msgid "union"
msgstr "unión"

#. [dummy]: id=union
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/macros/union.cfg:12
msgid "This unit wields the ancient power of the Union of Light and Darkness."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad empuña el antiguo poder de la Unión de la Luz y la Oscuridad."

#. [dummy]: id=union
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/macros/union.cfg:44
msgid ""
"This attack is only available on offense and requires a supporting unit with "
"the same weapon special adjacent to both participants. If this attack is "
"used during a turn, the supporting unit will not be able to perform any "
"additional actions for the current playing side’s turn.\n"
"\n"
"Additionally, the following special properties apply:\n"
"\n"
"• This attack always has an 80% chance to hit regardless of the defensive "
"ability of the unit being attacked.\n"
"• All damage dealt by this attack is considered <b>union</b> damage, to "
"which no units have resistance.\n"
"• Opponents have the <b>mark</b> status applied to them on hit, which "
"decreases all their resistances by 20% (down to a minimum of -50%) until "
"their own turn ends.\n"
"• Lower-level opponents have their number of retaliating strikes reduced by "
"1."
msgstr ""
"Este ataque solo está disponible en ofensiva y requiere una unidad de apoyo "
"con la misma especialidad de arma adyacente a ambos participantes. Si se usa "
"este ataque durante un turno, la unidad de apoyo no podrá realizar ninguna "
"acción adicional durante el turno del bando actual.\n"
"\n"
"Además, se aplican las siguientes propiedades especiales:\n"
"\n"
"• Este ataque siempre tiene un 80 % de probabilidad de acertar, "
"independientemente de la capacidad defensiva de la unidad atacada.\n"
"• Todo el daño infligido por este ataque se considera daño <b>unión</b>, al "
"que ninguna unidad tiene resistencia.\n"
"• Los oponentes reciben el estado <b>marcado</b> al ser golpeados, lo que "
"reduce todas sus resistencias en un 20 % (hasta un mínimo de -50 %) hasta "
"que termine su propio turno.\n"
"• Los oponentes de nivel inferior tienen su número de contraataques reducido "
"en 1."

