msgid "petrichor"
msgstr "petricor"

#. [petrifies]: id=petrichor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/macros/weapon-specials.cfg:21
msgid ""
"When this attack hits a lower-level opponent during offense, the target "
"becomes petrified for one turn. Once the petrification effect expires, the "
"target gains the mark status effect."
msgstr ""
"Cuando este ataque acierta a un oponente de nivel inferior durante la "
"ofensiva, el objetivo queda petrificado durante un turno. Una vez que el "
"efecto de petrificación expire, el objetivo obtiene el estado marcado."

#. [dummy]: id=shrapnel
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/macros/weapon-specials.cfg:133
msgid "shrapnel"
msgstr "metralla"

#. [dummy]: id=shrapnel
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/macros/weapon-specials.cfg:134
msgid ""
"The unit immediately behind the target takes 80% of the base damage of this "
"attack, regardless of its allegiance. This value is subject to the usual "
"damage calculation, taking the attacker’s alignment and the second target’s "
"resistances into account.\n"
"\n"
"This attack is only available on offense against living targets, and always "
"has a 100% chance to hit regardless of the defense attributes of the target."
msgstr ""
"La unidad situada inmediatamente detrás del objetivo recibe un 80% del daño "
"base de este ataque, independientemente de su lealtad. Este valor está "
"sujeto al cálculo habitual de daño, teniendo en cuenta la alineación del "
"atacante y las resistencias del segundo objetivo.\n"
"\n"
"Este ataque solo está disponible a la ofensiva contra objetivos vivos y "
"siempre tiene un 100% de probabilidad de impactar, sin importar los "
"atributos defensivos del objetivo."

