#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/01_Border_Patrol.cfg:159
msgid "It is advised you start recruiting units in advance as a precaution"
msgstr ""
"Se recomienda que comiences a reclutar unidades con anticipación como "
"precaución"

#. [message]: speaker=Grumnyr
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/01_Border_Patrol.cfg:170
msgid "Move on, you sluggards. Let’s claim these lands for the Master!"
msgstr "¡Avancen, holgazanes! ¡Reclamemos estas tierras para el Maestro!"

#. [message]: speaker=Surhan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/01_Border_Patrol.cfg:175
msgid "Be careful. We were warned that there are still elves in this valley."
msgstr "Tengan cuidado. Nos advirtieron que aún quedan elfos en este valle."

#. [message]: speaker=Grumnyr
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/01_Border_Patrol.cfg:180
msgid "No matter. We’ll tear them to pieces if they dare oppose us!"
msgstr "No importa. ¡Los haremos pedazos si se atreven a oponerse a nosotros!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/01_Border_Patrol.cfg:185
msgid ""
"A host of humans in the southern dunes... It has been quite a long time "
"since any of them have wandered here in such numbers."
msgstr ""
"Un grupo de humanos en las dunas del sur... Ha pasado mucho tiempo desde que "
"alguno de ellos vagara por aquí en tal cantidad."

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/01_Border_Patrol.cfg:193
msgid "What should we do?"
msgstr "¿Qué deberíamos hacer?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/01_Border_Patrol.cfg:198
msgid ""
"According to our laws, we should always grant refuge to wanderers — but I "
"sense hostility from this group. It would be wise to observe them for a "
"while, but let us be prepared for the worst nonetheless."
msgstr ""
"De acuerdo con nuestras leyes, siempre deberíamos conceder refugio a los "
"viajeros — pero percibo hostilidad en este grupo. Sería prudente observarlos "
"un tiempo, aunque debemos estar preparados para lo peor."

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/01_Border_Patrol.cfg:206
msgid "Very well."
msgstr "Muy bien."

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/01_Border_Patrol.cfg:268
msgid "Attack! Leave no one alive!"
msgstr "¡Ataquen! ¡No dejen a nadie con vida!"

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/01_Border_Patrol.cfg:276
msgid "They are attacking us!"
msgstr "¡Nos están atacando!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/01_Border_Patrol.cfg:281
msgid ""
"Our laws are very clear and strict on this matter. We shall not let hostile "
"outsiders enter our valley. Repel them!"
msgstr ""
"Nuestras leyes son muy claras y estrictas en este asunto. No permitiremos "
"que forasteros hostiles entren en nuestro valle. ¡Rechacenlos!"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/01_Border_Patrol.cfg:285
msgid "Defeat both enemy leaders"
msgstr "Derrote a ambos líderes enemigos"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/01_Border_Patrol.cfg:306
msgid "Argh! I have been... defeated..."
msgstr "¡Argh! He sido... derrotado..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/01_Border_Patrol.cfg:324
msgid ""
"They have summoned reinforcements! Our group is not strong enough to defend "
"the valley against a full-sized army!"
msgstr ""
"¡Han llamado refuerzos! ¡Nuestro grupo no es lo bastante fuerte para "
"defender el valle contra un ejército completo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/01_Border_Patrol.cfg:339
msgid ""
"We defeated them in time. But... that raiding party was quite large and well-"
"organized for a tribe of humans, and their metalwork seems beyond the "
"capabilities of regular sand-dwellers. This does not bode well..."
msgstr ""
"Los hemos derrotado a tiempo. Pero... esa partida de incursión era bastante "
"grande y bien organizada para ser una tribu de humanos, y su trabajo en "
"metal parece superar las capacidades de los habitantes comunes del desierto. "
"Esto no augura nada bueno..."

