#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:317
msgid "Death of Anlindë"
msgstr "Muerte de Anlindë"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:256
msgid ""
"Fewer than five elven villages under your or Lédinor’s control remain "
"standing"
msgstr "Quedan menos de cinco aldeas élficas bajo tu control o el de Lédinor"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:257
msgid ""
"Fewer than eight elven villages under your or Lédinor’s control remain "
"standing"
msgstr "Quedan menos de ocho aldeas élficas bajo tu control o el de Lédinor"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:258
msgid ""
"Fewer than nine elven villages under your or Lédinor’s control remain "
"standing"
msgstr "Quedan menos de nueve aldeas élficas bajo tu control o el de Lédinor"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:318
msgid ""
"The patrol group that was sent to replace yours in the southern zone should "
"have arrived this morning. I begin to worry about them."
msgstr ""
"El grupo de patrulla que fue enviado para reemplazar al tuyo en la zona sur "
"debería haber llegado esta mañana. Empiezo a preocuparme por ellos."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:332
msgid "Fire! Fire on the horizon! Call out the fighters, invaders draw near!"
msgstr ""
"¡Fuego! ¡Fuego en el horizonte! ¡Reunid a los combatientes, los invasores se "
"acercan!"

#. [unit]: type=Elvish Scout, type=Elvish Rider, id=Vólrand
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:359
msgid "Vólrand"
msgstr "Vólrand"

#. [message]: speaker=Vólrand
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:377
msgid ""
"Indeed, sir! It’s an entire human army burning forests and pillaging "
"villages in the border hills! They have even impaled the skulls of our "
"fallen kin on their banners!"
msgstr ""
"¡Así es, señor! ¡Es un ejército humano entero quemando bosques y saqueando "
"aldeas en las colinas fronterizas! ¡Incluso han empalado los cráneos de "
"nuestros caídos en sus estandartes!"

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:382
msgid ""
"An entire army? That’s impossible — humans are not capable of raising troops "
"in such numbers!"
msgstr ""
"¿Un ejército entero? ¡Eso es imposible! Los humanos no son capaces de reunir "
"tropas en tales números."

#. [message]: role=supporter
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:387
msgid "So that is what befell them... Those invaders will not go unpunished!"
msgstr "Así que eso les ocurrió… ¡Esos invasores no quedarán sin castigo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:392
msgid ""
"We must prepare to fight. We will not allow even an army to dispossess us. "
"Men, to arms!"
msgstr ""
"Debemos prepararnos para luchar. No permitiremos que ni siquiera un ejército "
"nos despoje. ¡Hombres, a las armas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:399
msgid ""
"But my lord, if these invaders could trap our best patrollers, how can we "
"prevail against them while so short of recruits and supplies?"
msgstr ""
"Pero mi señor, si estos invasores pudieron atrapar a nuestros mejores "
"patrulleros, ¿cómo podremos prevalecer contra ellos con tan pocos reclutas y "
"suministros?"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:404
msgid ""
"Young Galas, I understand your worries. But it is time for you to learn the "
"first duty of a commander, which is to not be defeated in mind before you "
"engage in battle."
msgstr ""
"Joven Galas, entiendo tus preocupaciones. Pero ha llegado el momento de que "
"aprendas el primer deber de un comandante: no ser derrotado en la mente "
"antes de entrar en batalla."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:409
msgid "I accept your instruction."
msgstr "Acepto su enseñanza."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:413
msgid ""
"In an emergency, even the valley’s citizens are ready to take up arms! "
"Although physically frail and not very adept at fighting outside of the "
"forests, their basic training in the use of the sword and the bow should "
"allow them to support your troops against low-level enemy units in a pinch. "
"But most importantly, <span color='#bcb088'>they will not charge you for "
"their services</span> at their initial level."
msgstr ""
"¡En una emergencia, incluso los ciudadanos del valle están listos para tomar "
"las armas! Aunque son físicamente frágiles y no muy hábiles luchando fuera "
"de los bosques, su entrenamiento básico con la espada y el arco debería "
"permitirles apoyar a tus tropas contra unidades enemigas de bajo nivel en "
"caso de necesidad. Pero lo más importante: <span color='#bcb088'>no te "
"cobrarán por sus servicios</span> en su nivel inicial."

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:435
msgid "Bright Gods... what is that thing?"
msgstr "Dioses luminosos… ¿qué es esa cosa?"

#. [message]: role=scared_one
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:456
msgid "I don’t think we can resist them!"
msgstr "¡No creo que podamos resistirlos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:461
msgid ""
"So, there is yet human civilization on this continent. I wonder why we have "
"not encountered them before?"
msgstr ""
"Así que aún existe una civilización humana en este continente. Me pregunto "
"por qué no los habíamos encontrado antes."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:466
msgid ""
"It must be that they are a new tribe, only recently come into its power... "
"an evil power that is not from our world. Look!"
msgstr ""
"Debe ser que son una nueva tribu que ha adquirido poder recientemente… un "
"poder maligno que no es de nuestro mundo. ¡Mira!"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:469
msgid "Garya"
msgstr "Garya"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:470
msgid "Quiryn"
msgstr "Quiryn"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:472
msgid "Nolok"
msgstr "Nolok"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:487
msgid "Would that my fears had proven false..."
msgstr "Ojalá mis temores hubieran sido infundados…"

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:516
msgid "Galas, are you— Are you purposely sending civilians to their deaths?!"
msgstr ""
"Galas, ¿acaso estás… estás enviando a propósito a los civiles a la muerte?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:521
msgid ""
"Er... No! They are supposed to deliver supplies to the front line and tend "
"to injured soldiers, not engage in combat! Somebody must have misunderstood "
"my orders — I will ask our officials to put a halt to this egregious waste "
"of precious elf lives immediately."
msgstr ""
"Eh… ¡No! Se suponía que debían llevar suministros a la línea del frente y "
"atender a los soldados heridos, no entrar en combate. Alguien debe haber "
"malinterpretado mis órdenes; pediré a nuestros oficiales que detengan de "
"inmediato este terrible desperdicio de valiosas vidas élficas."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:526
msgid "(<i>suspicious</i>) Very... well..."
msgstr "(<i>sospechosa</i>) Muy… bien…"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:559
msgid "The humans are retreating, after having almost defeated us?"
msgstr "¿Los humanos están retirándose… después de habernos casi derrotado?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:565
msgid "Their remaining forces are retreating. It seems we have won, for now."
msgstr ""
"Sus fuerzas restantes se están retirando. Parece que hemos ganado… por ahora."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:575
msgid ""
"Would that it had not taken the lives of so many civilians that had no need "
"to join the battle in the first place, huh, Galas?"
msgstr ""
"Ojalá no hubiera costado la vida a tantos civiles que no tenían necesidad de "
"unirse a la batalla, ¿eh, Galas?"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:584
msgid ""
"I hate to be the bearer of bad news, but some of the other patrol leaders "
"claim that the invaders are merely regrouping and preparing to strike again "
"with greater numbers. Many of your peers abandoned their posts, and Adel and "
"his hunters have not returned from their expedition yet... This is no mere "
"skirmish, Galas. I do not think we shall be able to hold against them."
msgstr ""
"Odio ser portador de malas noticias, pero algunos de los otros líderes de "
"patrulla afirman que los invasores solo se están reagrupando y preparando "
"para atacar de nuevo con más fuerzas. Muchos de tus compañeros abandonaron "
"sus puestos, y Adel y sus cazadores aún no han regresado de su expedición… "
"Esto no es una simple escaramuza, Galas. No creo que podamos resistirlos."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:589
msgid ""
"Would it be possible to obstruct the valley entrances and repel them? How "
"many more of those winged creatures could they have at their disposal?"
msgstr ""
"¿Sería posible obstruir las entradas del valle y rechazarlos? ¿Cuántas de "
"esas criaturas aladas podrían tener a su disposición?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:594
msgid ""
"If we trust the scouts’ word, they could be hundreds. Perhaps thousands. "
"Their own sorcerers would be able to bring down or bypass any sort of "
"obstacle we might raise within the scarce time we have before their next "
"assault. I would be inclined to suggest fleeing."
msgstr ""
"Si confiamos en la palabra de los exploradores, podrían ser cientos. Quizás "
"miles. Sus propios hechiceros serían capaces de derribar o eludir cualquier "
"obstáculo que pudiéramos levantar en el escaso tiempo que tenemos antes de "
"su próximo asalto. Me inclinaría a sugerir que huyamos."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:599
msgid ""
"Do you say we should abandon our home? Where would we go? Our people are not "
"as adept as those humans to surviving the desert’s perils!"
msgstr ""
"¿Dices que deberíamos abandonar nuestro hogar? ¿A dónde iríamos? ¡Nuestro "
"pueblo no es tan hábil como esos humanos para sobrevivir a los peligros del "
"desierto!"

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:604
msgid ""
"We would certainly not survive the desert from whence the humans came, "
"especially since we don’t know how many more warriors follow their back "
"trail. However, we have no reports of enemies approaching from the north — "
"we have not been menaced by anything from that direction in centuries. It "
"may be that any possibility of escaping the imminent slaughter lies there. "
"If our historical records are correct, the caverns should take us far from "
"this valley. It is my hope that the humans and their fell allies are not "
"informed of any of this."
msgstr ""
"Sin duda no sobreviviríamos al desierto de donde vinieron los humanos, "
"especialmente porque no sabemos cuántos guerreros más podrían seguir su "
"rastro. Sin embargo, no tenemos informes de enemigos acercándose desde el "
"norte; no hemos sido amenazados por nada desde esa dirección en siglos. "
"Puede que cualquier posibilidad de escapar de la inminente masacre esté "
"allí. Si nuestros registros históricos son correctos, las cavernas deberían "
"llevarnos lejos de este valle. Espero que los humanos y sus oscuros aliados "
"no sepan nada de esto."

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:609
msgid ""
"North, you say... It is true that it has seemed more tranquil in my "
"lifetime. Is it your intention to destroy any evidence of there being this "
"underground escape route in the northern pass? Even if that worked... it "
"would be a harsh, irrevocable choice."
msgstr ""
"¿Hacia el norte, dices…? Es cierto que ha parecido más tranquilo en mi vida. "
"¿Es tu intención destruir toda evidencia de la existencia de esta ruta de "
"escape subterránea en el paso del norte? Incluso si eso funcionara… sería "
"una elección dura e irrevocable."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:614
msgid ""
"The ancestors of our people spent much of their lives hiding beneath the "
"surface when this valley was just barely apt for sustaining them. If we "
"manage to survive, we might in time be fortunate enough to find a new home "
"to settle in. If we fail, at least we will die with our heads held high."
msgstr ""
"Los ancestros de nuestro pueblo pasaron gran parte de sus vidas ocultos bajo "
"la superficie cuando este valle apenas era apto para sustentarlos. Si "
"logramos sobrevivir, quizá con el tiempo tengamos la fortuna de encontrar un "
"nuevo hogar donde asentarnos. Si fallamos, al menos moriremos con la cabeza "
"en alto."

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:619
msgid "You bring hard counsel, but I see its wisdom."
msgstr "Traes un consejo duro, pero veo su sabiduría."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:624
msgid ""
"We are between a rock and a hard place — either death by the hands of the "
"invaders, or the perils of the underground tunnels."
msgstr ""
"Estamos entre la espada y la pared: o la muerte a manos de los invasores, o "
"los peligros de los túneles subterráneos."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:629
msgid ""
"Most of our people lack experience traveling at night, let alone under the "
"earth!"
msgstr ""
"¡La mayoría de nuestro pueblo carece de experiencia viajando de noche, y "
"mucho menos bajo tierra!"

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:634
msgid ""
"I fear we have no other alternatives left. Unless the civilians think it a "
"better course to stand and fight to our death and be expunged from the green "
"world without trace."
msgstr ""
"Temo que no nos quedan más alternativas. A menos que los civiles consideren "
"mejor quedarse y luchar hasta la muerte para ser borrados del mundo verde "
"sin dejar rastro."

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:639
msgid ""
"It will be necessary, however, to provide a distraction until we evacuate "
"all of our people to the caves. Have you thought on that, my lady?"
msgstr ""
"Será necesario, sin embargo, proporcionar una distracción hasta que "
"evacuemos a todo nuestro pueblo hacia las cavernas. ¿Ha pensado en eso, mi "
"señora?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:644
msgid "I have, indeed. But..."
msgstr "Sí, lo he hecho… pero…"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:649
msgid "Some of us must stay here to spoil their attack. We shall do it."
msgstr ""
"Algunos de nosotros debemos quedarnos aquí para frustrar su ataque. Lo "
"haremos."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:654
msgid "But— my lord?"
msgstr "Pero… ¿mi señor?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:659
msgid "My lord... Why?"
msgstr "Mi señor… ¿por qué?"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:664
msgid ""
"Because it is all I can do for our future. Many of us are too old to long "
"survive the desert wastes, including myself — but here we can die well. "
"Galas, you are a brave warrior, albeit unseasoned — and more to the point, "
"you have the intelligence to lead brave warriors. I pass to you the war-"
"leadership of the elves of the Valley of Elynia."
msgstr ""
"Porque es todo lo que puedo hacer por nuestro futuro. Muchos de nosotros "
"somos demasiado viejos para sobrevivir mucho tiempo a las tierras áridas del "
"desierto, yo incluido… pero aquí podemos morir con honor. Galas, eres un "
"guerrero valiente, aunque inexperto, y lo que es más importante: tienes la "
"inteligencia para liderar a valientes guerreros. Te transfiero el mando de "
"guerra de los elfos del Valle de Elynia."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:669
msgid ""
"But I am simply a patrol leader! I ... I am not ready for such a "
"responsibility!"
msgstr ""
"¡Pero solo soy un líder de patrulla! Yo… yo no estoy preparado para una "
"responsabilidad así."

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:674
msgid ""
"None of us are ever ready for such a burden, but we must bear it "
"nevertheless. Now, go! May fate reunite us in time, young Galas."
msgstr ""
"Ninguno de nosotros está jamás preparado para una carga así, pero debemos "
"soportarla igualmente. ¡Ahora, ve! Que el destino nos reúna a tiempo, joven "
"Galas."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:692
msgid "Ugh. I am finished..."
msgstr "Ugh. Estoy acabado…"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:704
msgid "Anlindë! No! We need you! Who will guide us with wisdom now?!"
msgstr "¡Anlindë! ¡No! ¡Te necesitamos! ¿Quién nos guiará ahora con sabiduría?"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:718
msgid "It is my end..."
msgstr "Es mi final…"

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:723
msgid "Galas? Galas, no!"
msgstr "¿Galas? ¡Galas, no!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:744
msgid ""
"I have fallen this day. But, young Galas, you are the brightest of our "
"young. Lead our people in my place!"
msgstr ""
"Hoy he caído. Pero, joven Galas, eres el más brillante de los nuestros. "
"¡Lidera a nuestro pueblo en mi lugar!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:756
msgid "Lédinor, no!"
msgstr "¡Lédinor, no!"

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:785
msgid "Leave nothing standing! Burn them alive with their villages!"
msgstr "¡No dejen nada en pie! ¡Quemen vivos a ellos y a sus aldeas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:842
msgid ""
"We could not protect enough of our civilians. They have been burned alive "
"with their villages!"
msgstr ""
"No pudimos proteger a suficientes civiles. ¡Han sido quemados vivos junto "
"con sus aldeas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/02_A_Real_Confrontation.cfg:847
msgid ""
"We have failed to protect our people and the legacy of our civilization."
msgstr ""
"Hemos fallado en proteger a nuestro pueblo y el legado de nuestra "
"civilización."

