#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:405
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1128
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1589
msgid "Straying too far from the road is probably not the best thing to do"
msgstr "Alejarse demasiado del camino probablemente no sea lo mejor"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:406
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:884
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1129
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1590
msgid ""
"Sources of income are very rare in the desert; choose your recruits and "
"recalls carefully"
msgstr ""
"Las fuentes de ingresos son muy escasas en el desierto; elige con cuidado a "
"tus reclutas y a las unidades que llames."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:418
msgid ""
"Ah, the surface! And the sunlight! Scorching hot sand everywhere as usual — "
"how unpleasant."
msgstr ""
"¡Ah, la superficie! ¡Y la luz del sol! Arena abrasadora por todas partes, "
"como de costumbre... qué desagradable."

#. [message]: role=supporter
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:423
msgid ""
"This environment is even more unfavorable for us than the caves. My lord, "
"there is an oasis north from here. If we want to advance across the sands we "
"will need to make sure our people can rest and replenish supplies there. The "
"problem is..."
msgstr ""
"Este entorno es aún más desfavorable para nosotros que las cuevas. Mi señor, "
"hay un oasis al norte de aquí. Si queremos avanzar a través de las arenas, "
"necesitaremos asegurarnos de que nuestra gente pueda descansar y reponer "
"suministros allí. El problema es…"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:433
msgid ""
"I heard the rumors already. The oasis appears to be controlled by orcs. Is "
"there any other way through?"
msgstr ""
"Ya he oído los rumores. Parece que el oasis está controlado por orcos. ¿Hay "
"alguna otra forma de pasar?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:440
msgid ""
"Definitely not, unless your intention is to retrace your steps across the "
"surface... and risk facing the demons again without the tactical advantage "
"of your towers and forests. Small orcish tribes like the one ahead generally "
"lack any proper military discipline. Your forest-loving kin should be able "
"to crush them with ease."
msgstr ""
"Definitivamente no, a menos que tu intención sea desandar tus pasos por la "
"superficie… y arriesgarte a enfrentarte a los demonios otra vez sin la "
"ventaja táctica de tus torres y bosques. Las pequeñas tribus orcas como la "
"que hay adelante suelen carecer de disciplina militar adecuada. Tus "
"parientes amantes de los bosques deberían ser capaces de aplastarlos con "
"facilidad."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:445
msgid ""
"That isn’t exactly motivating. They have lived in these sands for an epoch "
"or more. They are not the intruders."
msgstr ""
"Eso no es exactamente motivador. Ellos han vivido en estas arenas por una "
"época o más. No son los intrusos."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:450
msgid ""
"Galas, if you want to lead our people... you will need to become accustomed "
"to making hard decisions like this. There is much at stake — either the "
"lives of a few orcs who would have no qualms about murdering us in our "
"sleep, or the lives of our civilians and children, and our hope of "
"protecting and rebuilding our civilization."
msgstr ""
"Galas, si deseas liderar a nuestra gente... necesitarás acostumbrarte a "
"tomar decisiones difíciles como esta. Hay mucho en juego: la vida de unos "
"pocos orcos que no dudarían en asesinarnos mientras dormimos, o la vida de "
"nuestros civiles y niños, y nuestra esperanza de proteger y reconstruir "
"nuestra civilización."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:459
msgid ""
"I would never choose the orcs’ lives over ours... Let us prepare for the "
"assault, then."
msgstr ""
"Jamás elegiría la vida de los orcos por encima de la nuestra... Preparemos "
"el asalto, entonces."

#. [message]: role=supporter
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:464
msgid ""
"It is only going to become increasingly difficult and expensive to sustain "
"our mounts in this hostile environment. Would that we could replace them "
"with desert beasts."
msgstr ""
"Solo se hará cada vez más difícil y costoso mantener a nuestros montajes en "
"este entorno hostil. Ojalá pudiéramos reemplazarlos con bestias del desierto."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:469
msgid ""
"If it is your wish to ride sand lions, so be it. I’m sure you won’t mind if "
"I dispatch a few bats and possibly one or two skeletal riders to scout ahead."
msgstr ""
"Si tu deseo es montar leones de arena, que así sea. Estoy seguro de que no "
"te importará si envío algunos murciélagos y posiblemente uno o dos jinetes "
"esqueléticos para explorar adelante."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:474
msgid ""
"Our agreement did not include allowing you to make use of your foul sorcery "
"in our presence."
msgstr ""
"Nuestro acuerdo no incluía permitirte hacer uso de tu foul hechicería en "
"nuestra presencia."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:479
msgid "Did it include <i>forbidding</i> me from doing so, though?"
msgstr "¿Incluía acaso <i>prohibirme</i> hacerlo?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:484
msgid "Let him do as he wishes."
msgstr "Déjalo hacer lo que desee."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:490
msgid ""
"You can now recruit <b>undead units</b>!\n"
"\n"
"Elvish units become gradually more expensive to recruit (but not recall) as "
"you progress through the campaign. Because of this, you may find yourself "
"favoring undead recruits more as time goes on."
msgstr ""
"¡Ahora puedes reclutar <b>unidades no muertas</b>!\n"
"\n"
"Las unidades élficas se vuelven gradualmente más caras de reclutar (pero no "
"de reincorporar) a medida que avanzas en la campaña. Por eso, es probable "
"que termines prefiriendo reclutar más unidades no muertas conforme pase el "
"tiempo."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:512
msgid ""
"Galas, it’s not even midday — has the heat atrophied your senses already?"
msgstr "Galas, aún no es mediodía. ¿Ya el calor ha atrofiado tus sentidos?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:517
msgid ""
"You defeated him once. Surely you could do it again if worst comes to worst. "
"I need to know to what extent we can trust him."
msgstr ""
"Lo derrotaste una vez. Seguro podrías hacerlo de nuevo si lo peor llega a "
"pasar. Necesito saber hasta qué punto podemos confiar en él."

#. [message]: role=supporter
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:522
msgid ""
"My lord, if you allow me to say so... he is a damned soul, a <i>necromancer</"
"i>! You absolutely <i>cannot</i> place any trust in his words!"
msgstr ""
"Mi señor, si me permites decirlo... ¡es un alma maldita, un <i>necromántico</"
"i>! ¡No puedes <i>absolutamente</i> confiar en sus palabras!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:527
msgid ""
"I need to know his motives for offering us his help. If his intention is to "
"strike us down and raise an army with our corpses, I would rather find out "
"sooner than later."
msgstr ""
"Necesito saber sus motivos para ofrecernos su ayuda. Si su intención es "
"matarnos y levantar un ejército con nuestros cadáveres, prefiero descubrirlo "
"antes que después."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:537
msgid ""
"Aaaand, the suns continue their journey through the skies! Hopefully your "
"elves will withstand it long enough to reach the oasis, young leader!"
msgstr ""
"Y así, los soles continúan su viaje por los cielos. ¡Esperemos que tus elfos "
"resistan el calor lo suficiente para llegar al oasis, joven líder!"

#. [message]: role=supporter
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:544
msgid "Will he ever stop mocking us?"
msgstr "¿Alguna vez dejará de burlarse de nosotros?"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:566
msgid ""
"female^Ahhh, the refreshing feeling of my feet in the water... I miss our "
"peaceful valley..."
msgstr ""
"¡Ahhh, la refrescante sensación de mis pies en el agua... Extraño nuestro "
"valle pacífico..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:591
msgid "Those hostile spirits... Is this a trick of yours, Mal Keshar?"
msgstr "Esos espíritus hostiles... ¿Es esto un truco tuyo, Mal Keshar?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:596
msgid ""
"No. They are corrupted souls who have haunted the desert for an eternity, "
"victims of the destruction that turned Irdya into an endless desert. "
"Physical weapons are of little use against them and they always find a way "
"back — unless, of course, they are banished from our world by spellcasters "
"capable of wielding the arcane fire... or possibly, a necromancer and his "
"minions."
msgstr ""
"No. Son almas corrompidas que han acechado el desierto durante una "
"eternidad, víctimas de la destrucción que convirtió Irdya en un desierto "
"interminable. Las armas físicas son de poca utilidad contra ellas y siempre "
"encuentran la forma de regresar, a menos que, por supuesto, sean desterradas "
"de nuestro mundo por hechiceros capaces de controlar el fuego arcano... o, "
"posiblemente, un necromántico y sus secuaces."

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:619
msgid "Return to the darkness from whence you came!"
msgstr "¡Vuelvan a la oscuridad de donde vinieron!"

#. [floating_text]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:644
msgid "banished"
msgstr "desterrado"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:667
msgid ""
"Hah, the scouts weren’t hallucinating after all! It’s a party of bold little "
"elves heading for our precious oasis. Go get them!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ja! ¡Así que los exploradores no estaban alucinando! Es un grupo de "
"pequeños elfos audaces que se dirigen a nuestro preciado oasis. ¡A por ellos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:686
msgid "Yes, yes, this is more like old times!"
msgstr "¡Sí, sí, esto se parece más a los viejos tiempos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Karun Baghar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:723
msgid ""
"Elves in <i>my</i> oasis... And you brought a <i>necromancer</i> with you, "
"no less! Begone!"
msgstr ""
"Elfos en <i>mi</i> oasis... ¡Y además trajeron a un <i>necromántico</i> con "
"ustedes! ¡Largo de aquí!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:738
msgid "Any last words, <i>orc</i>?"
msgstr "¿Alguna última palabra, <i>orco</i>?"

#. [message]: speaker=Karun Baghar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:743
msgid "Damn... you—"
msgstr "Malditos... se—"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:766
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:772
msgid ""
"The chieftain kept a small hoard of gold in his tent. We shall surely find a "
"use for it."
msgstr ""
"El jefe guardaba un pequeño botín de oro en su tienda. Seguramente "
"encontraremos un buen uso para él."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:799
msgid "Aetheran"
msgstr "Aetheran"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:800
msgid "Mur"
msgstr "Mur"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:801
msgid "Gaether"
msgstr "Gaether"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:802
msgid "Merghyn"
msgstr "Merghyn"

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:830
msgid ""
"The oasis is ours now, but we may not tarry long. Our people can replenish "
"supplies and grab anything of value left behind by the orcs, but it is "
"imperative that we continue scouting ahead and clearing the path."
msgstr ""
"El oasis es nuestro ahora, pero no podemos demorarnos mucho. Nuestra gente "
"puede reponer suministros y tomar cualquier cosa de valor que hayan dejado "
"los orcos, pero es imperativo que sigamos explorando y despejando el camino."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:835
msgid "Is this what we have been reduced to? Looters and scavengers?"
msgstr "¿Es esto en lo que nos hemos convertido? ¿Saqueadores y carroñeros?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:840
msgid "Mal Keshar, where should we head now?"
msgstr "Mal Keshar, ¿hacia dónde debemos dirigirnos ahora?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:845
msgid "West."
msgstr "Al oeste."

#. [message]: race=elf
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:853
msgid "I thought we were supposed to head northwest!"
msgstr "¡Pensé que se suponía que íbamos hacia el noroeste!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:858
msgid ""
"First west, then we can resume traveling northwest. The sands north of here "
"are especially unpleasant, with absolutely no sources of water or food for "
"your troops for miles and miles. Your people would surely starve and perish. "
"On the other hand, the sands and mountains to the west are all that stands "
"between us and a river, and then a green valley leading to the very heart of "
"Irdya."
msgstr ""
"Primero hacia el oeste, y luego podremos retomar el rumbo hacia el noroeste. "
"Las arenas al norte de aquí son especialmente desagradables, sin fuentes de "
"agua ni comida para tus tropas en millas y millas. Tu gente seguramente "
"moriría de hambre. En cambio, las arenas y montañas al oeste son lo único "
"que nos separa de un río y luego de un valle verde que lleva directo al "
"corazón de Irdya."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:863
msgid ""
"The sooner we find land that isn’t completely covered in sand and infested "
"with orcs..."
msgstr ""
"Cuanto antes encontremos tierras que no estén completamente cubiertas de "
"arena y plagadas de orcos..."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:873
msgid "Proceed with Galas to the mountain range on the western side of the map"
msgstr "Avanza con Galas hasta la cordillera en el lado occidental del mapa"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:883
msgid "Straying too far from the road is probably inadvisable"
msgstr "Alejarse demasiado del camino probablemente no sea buena idea"

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:905
msgid ""
"Hmm, some unusual energy emanates from this inscription... “Here lies █████, "
"the Last Petrichor Sorcerer of Eisenstone. May the sacred instrument of his "
"might lie unperturbed forevermore — woe betide whosoever foolishly attempts "
"to extricate the relic from his earthen abode, for the secrets of the lithic "
"realm can only bring ruination upon the unenlightened!”\n"
"\n"
"Sounds like this tomb conceals some kind of mythical artifact. Perhaps one "
"of our more learned magic users may want to have a look at it?"
msgstr ""
"Hmm, de esta inscripción emana una energía poco común... «Aquí yace █████, "
"el Último Hechicero de Petricor de Eisenstone. Que el instrumento sagrado de "
"su poder repose inalterado por siempre — ¡ay de quien intente neciamente "
"extraer la reliquia de su morada terrenal, pues los secretos del reino "
"lítico solo pueden traer ruina a los ignorantes!»\n"
"\n"
"Parece que esta tumba oculta algún tipo de artefacto mítico. Tal vez alguno "
"de nuestros usuarios de magia más instruidos quiera echarle un vistazo."

#. [option]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:909
msgid "Defile the tomb."
msgstr "Profanar la tumba."

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:981
msgid "Oopsy-daisy! We should probably take care of that first..."
msgstr "¡Uy, uy! Probablemente deberíamos encargarnos de eso primero..."

#. [option]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:986
msgid ""
"On second thought, we do not need to add more things to our list of crimes "
"against the natural order..."
msgstr ""
"Pensándolo mejor, no necesitamos añadir más cosas a nuestra lista de "
"crímenes contra el orden natural..."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1076
msgid "Humans ahead. They appear to be bandits— Oh, damn it, they spotted us!"
msgstr ""
"Humanos adelante. Parece que son bandidos... ¡Oh, maldición, nos han visto!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1082
msgid "There are bandits ahead—"
msgstr "Hay bandidos adelante—"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1089
msgid "What is this? Are those... elves? Like in the stories?"
msgstr "¿Qué es esto? ¿Son... elfos? ¿Como en las historias?"

#. [message]: speaker=Aetheran
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1094
msgid "Undead! They have brought the damned spawns of darkness with them!"
msgstr ""
"¡No-muertos! ¡Han traído a las malditas criaturas de la oscuridad con ellos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Merghyn
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1099
msgid "Come on, men, it’s time to smash some bones!"
msgstr "¡Vamos, hombres, es hora de romper algunos huesos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1108
msgid ""
"I don’t suppose we would make a much better impression without the "
"necromancer’s minions marching amongst us, would we?"
msgstr ""
"Supongo que no causaríamos una mejor impresión sin los esbirros del "
"nigromante marchando entre nosotros, ¿verdad?"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1118
msgid "Defeat the leader of the barbarians controlling the mountain pass"
msgstr "Derrota al líder de los bárbaros que controlan el paso montañoso"

#. [message]: speaker=Garren
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1145
msgid "Damn you... pointy-eared demons... ack—"
msgstr "Malditos... demonios de orejas puntiagudas... argh—"

#. [message]: speaker=Garren
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1162
msgid "(<i>spits blood</i>) Go to hell, necromancer... ack—"
msgstr "(<i>escupe sangre</i>) Vete al infierno, nigromante... argh—"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1174
msgid ""
"Now, don’t make this more difficult than it needs to be. You are a strong "
"man — I would hate to waste your useful build tearing you to pieces before "
"dealing the killing blow."
msgstr ""
"Ahora no lo hagas más difícil de lo necesario. Eres un hombre fuerte; "
"odiaría desperdiciar tu cuerpo útil destrozándote antes de dar el golpe "
"final."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1179
msgid ""
"Mal Keshar, stop it. You are not allowed to torture our opponents... or... "
"raise them as undead, for that matter."
msgstr ""
"Mal Keshar, basta. No tienes permitido torturar a nuestros oponentes... ni "
"tampoco alzarlos como no-muertos, en ese caso."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1184
msgid ""
"What does it matter? These are merely barbarians. They know no laws and no "
"honor."
msgstr "¿Qué importa? Son simplemente bárbaros. No conocen leyes ni honor."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1189
msgid "Allow him to die in peace."
msgstr "Permite que muera en paz."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1202
msgid "Pah, let one of your own finish the job instead. Such a waste."
msgstr ""
"Pah, que uno de los tuyos termine el trabajo entonces. Qué desperdicio."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1236
msgid "Eisenstone Clan — South Arhaghen Hills Fortress"
msgstr "Clan Eisenstone — Fortaleza de las Colinas del Sur de Arhaghen"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1275
msgid ""
"(<i>sighs</i>) Orcs, humans... Would that we weren’t forced to kill "
"everything in our way."
msgstr ""
"(<i>suspira</i>) Orcos, humanos... Ojalá no nos viéramos obligados a matar "
"todo lo que se cruza en nuestro camino."

#. [message]: speaker=Neryan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1280
msgid "Hey, elves."
msgstr "Eh, elfos."

#. [message]: speaker=Neryan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1333
msgid ""
"Ha, ha... Great job, disposing of those invaders was taking us a bit too "
"long. Ahhhh... How may we repay you? Where is your leader?"
msgstr ""
"Ja, ja... Buen trabajo, deshacerse de esos invasores nos estaba tomando "
"demasiado tiempo. Ahhhh... ¿Cómo podemos agradecerles? ¿Dónde está su líder?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1338
msgid ""
"That would be me, lord Galas of the elves of the Valley of Elynia. Your men "
"control this pass, I presume?"
msgstr ""
"Yo soy ese, lord Galas de los elfos del Valle de Elynia. Sus hombres "
"controlan este paso, ¿cierto?"

#. [message]: speaker=Neryan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1343
msgid ""
"Yes... yes, we do. These lands belong to my people, the Eisenstone clan. We "
"do not normally allow visitors in our territory because of... reasons... but "
"perhaps we could make an exception for you and your advisor."
msgstr ""
"Sí... sí, así es. Estas tierras pertenecen a mi gente, el clan Eisenstone. "
"Normalmente no permitimos visitantes en nuestro territorio por... razones... "
"pero quizás podríamos hacer una excepción para usted y su consejero."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1348
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:596
msgid "(<i>coughs</i>)"
msgstr "(<i>tose</i>)"

#. [message]: speaker=Neryan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1353
msgid ""
"... And the necromancer too, of course. We can provide you with food and "
"water for your soldiers at affordable prices... if you are interested, that "
"is!"
msgstr ""
"... Y también al nigromante, por supuesto. Podemos proveerles de comida y "
"agua para sus soldados a precios razonables... ¡si están interesados, claro!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1358
msgid ""
"Thanks for the offer, but we will need supplies and safe passage for a much "
"larger number of people... through your lands, if you don’t mind."
msgstr ""
"Gracias por la oferta, pero necesitaremos suministros y un paso seguro para "
"un número mucho mayor de personas... a través de sus tierras, si no les "
"importa."

#. [message]: speaker=Neryan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1367
msgid ""
"... Lord Galas of the elves! Yes, yes, well... we have heard the rumors. "
"Your people hunt down every human who approaches your sacred valley seeking "
"shelter from the demons... You hunt our species like animals, yes, you do. "
"What makes you think we will allow your <i>army</i> to take our lands and "
"lives now, huh? Isn’t that what you came here for?"
msgstr ""
"... ¡Lord Galas de los elfos! Sí, sí, bueno... hemos oído los rumores. Tu "
"gente caza a todo humano que se acerca a su sagrado valle buscando refugio "
"de los demonios... Persiguen a nuestra especie como animales, sí, así es. "
"¿Qué te hace pensar que permitiremos que tu <i>ejército</i> tome nuestras "
"tierras y vidas ahora, eh? ¿No es para eso que viniste?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1376
msgid "Our intentions are not..."
msgstr "Nuestras intenciones no son..."

#. [message]: speaker=Neryan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1388
msgid ""
"<b>Enough!</b> If you know what’s good for you and your kind, you will turn "
"back <i>now</i> or leave through the southwestern pass. Come on, men."
msgstr ""
"<b>¡Basta!</b> Si sabes lo que te conviene a ti y a los tuyos, darán la "
"vuelta <i>ahora</i> o se marcharán por el paso del suroeste. Vamos, hombres."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1418
msgid ""
"Their intentions are more transparent than they realize — of course they "
"were trying to set a trap for us. Well... Although they have a few "
"necromancers on their side, getting rid of them should be relatively easy."
msgstr ""
"Sus intenciones son más obvias de lo que creen; por supuesto que estaban "
"intentando tendernos una trampa. Bueno... Aunque tienen algunos nigromantes "
"de su lado, deshacernos de ellos debería ser relativamente fácil."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1423
msgid "What other options do we have, Mal Keshar?"
msgstr "¿Qué otras opciones tenemos, Mal Keshar?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1449
msgid ""
"The southwestern pass they mentioned, well, it leads to a completely "
"uninhabited plateau, so it is a valid alternative if you want to avoid "
"fighting the humans. Just note that there are barely any sources of water in "
"that direction — your people would only be able to march at night."
msgstr ""
"El paso suroeste del que hablaron lleva a una meseta completamente "
"deshabitada, así que es una alternativa válida si quieres evitar luchar "
"contra los humanos. Solo ten en cuenta que hay muy pocas fuentes de agua en "
"esa dirección: tu gente solo podría marchar de noche."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1454
msgid ""
"Choosing that option would do little good for your popularity after "
"accepting my offer, he, he."
msgstr ""
"Elegir esa opción no haría mucho bien a tu popularidad después de aceptar mi "
"oferta, je, je."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1463
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/16_Dawn_of_War.cfg:1513
msgid "Well..."
msgstr "Bueno..."

#. [option]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1466
msgid "Let us confront the humans."
msgstr "Enfrentémonos a los humanos."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1470
msgid ""
"Ha ha ha ha ha! I knew you wouldn’t turn down the possibility of a good "
"fight, boy!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ja, ja, ja, ja! Sabía que no rechazarías la posibilidad de una buena pelea, "
"muchacho."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1475
msgid ""
"We shall do this on my terms, though. That means: no killing unless strictly "
"necessary, no torturing captured enemies, and no raising corpses. In "
"particular, no harm must come to the clan leader. We may only assume control "
"of their lands temporarily in order to allow our people through."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, lo haremos en mis términos. Eso significa: no matar a menos que "
"sea estrictamente necesario, no torturar a los enemigos capturados y no "
"levantar cadáveres. En particular, no debe hacerse daño a la líder del clan. "
"Solo asumiremos el control de sus tierras temporalmente para permitir que "
"nuestra gente pase."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1480
msgid ""
"A sound plan, young leader, but... proving a point to those barbarians, is "
"it really worth it?"
msgstr ""
"Un plan sensato, joven líder, pero... ¿realmente vale la pena demostrarle "
"algo a esos bárbaros?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1485
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1508
msgid "Only time will tell for sure."
msgstr "Sólo el tiempo lo dirá con certeza."

#. [option]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1499
msgid ""
"All this fighting is leading us nowhere. Let us proceed through the "
"southwestern pass."
msgstr ""
"Toda esta lucha no nos lleva a ninguna parte. Sigamos por el paso suroeste."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1503
msgid ""
"That is an ill-advised choice, Galas. Proving a point to those barbarians "
"isn’t really worth it."
msgstr ""
"Esa es una elección poco aconsejable, Galas. No vale la pena intentar "
"demostrarles algo a esos bárbaros."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1578
msgid ""
"Capture the leader of the Eisenstone clan by reducing her to 0 hitpoints or "
"lower"
msgstr ""
"Captura a la líder del clan Eisenstone reduciéndola a 0 puntos de vida o "
"menos"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1588
msgid ""
"Plague and drain weapon specials have no effect on the Eisenstone clan "
"humans for the remainder of this scenario"
msgstr ""
"Las habilidades especiales de plaga y drenaje no tienen efecto sobre los "
"humanos del clan Eisenstone durante el resto de este escenario"

#. [message]: speaker=Neryan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1612
msgid ""
"All right, elf lord! You got me and my people... Go ahead and serve us to "
"your starving subjects, what do I care."
msgstr ""
"Está bien, ¡señor elfo! Nos tienes a mí y a mi gente... Adelante, sírvenos a "
"tus súbditos hambrientos, ¿qué me importa?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1617
msgid ""
"Of course... It didn’t occur to me that we could deal with our food shortage "
"by feeding upon our prisoners. Sadly, I had a different fate in mind for you "
"and your people, and honestly, I have to wonder where the absurd notion of "
"elves hunting humans for food originated in the first place. Unarye, take "
"this woman and the local necromancers to our camp."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto... No se me ocurrió que podríamos solucionar la escasez de "
"alimentos alimentándonos de nuestros prisioneros. Por desgracia, tenía un "
"destino diferente en mente para ti y tu gente. Y, sinceramente, me pregunto "
"de dónde surgió la absurda idea de que los elfos cazan humanos para "
"comerlos. Unarye, lleva a esta mujer y a los nigromantes locales a nuestro "
"campamento."

#. [message]: speaker=Unarye
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1622
msgid "Yes, my lord."
msgstr "Sí, mi señor."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1627
msgid "Let us prepare things for the arrival of our main host."
msgstr "Preparémonos para la llegada de nuestro contingente principal."

