#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:246
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/15_Shadows_of_Time.cfg:272
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/16_Dawn_of_War.cfg:628
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/17_Voice_of_the_Armageddon.cfg:238
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/18_Ashes_of_Wesmere.cfg:373
