#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:590
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:321
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:873
