#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1608
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:596
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:901
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:872
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1189
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1707
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:229
msgid "Death of Elynia"
msgstr "Muerte de Elynia"

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:376
msgid ""
"Just as I feared, they managed to take down Herthgar’s defenses and surround "
"the capital."
msgstr ""
"Tal como temía, lograron derribar las defensas de Herthgar y rodear la "
"capital."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:381
msgid ""
"It matters little. We shall drive them out of the caves regardless of their "
"numbers! Maybe we could even manage to turn them to our side in death, he he."
msgstr ""
"Poco importa. ¡Los echaremos de las cavernas sin importar su número! Tal vez "
"hasta consigamos ponerlos de nuestro lado en la muerte, je, je."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:386
msgid ""
"So those are the demons you have fought? They are not as impressive as I "
"expected."
msgstr ""
"¿Así que esos son los demonios contra los que han luchado? No son tan "
"impresionantes como esperaba."

#. [message]: speaker=Althurin
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:391
msgid ""
"They shall pay with their accursed blood if our good king was captured or "
"murdered!"
msgstr ""
"¡Pagarán con su maldita sangre si han capturado o asesinado a nuestro buen "
"rey!"

#. [message]: speaker=King Asthorgar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:400
msgid "Ye ha’ nae reason to fear, Althurin! Well, at least I am still alive!"
msgstr "¡No hay razón para temer, Althurin! Bueno, ¡al menos sigo vivo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:405
msgid "Your Highness, what is the situation?"
msgstr "Su Alteza, ¿cuál es la situación?"

#. [message]: speaker=King Asthorgar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:410
msgid ""
"Our main defenses ha’ fallen and if we are to ha’ any hope o’ fending off "
"these demented barbarians and their ever-increasing numbers, we’ll need all "
"the help we can muster!"
msgstr ""
"¡Nuestras defensas principales han caído, y si queremos tener alguna "
"esperanza de rechazar a estos bárbaros dementes y sus crecientes números, "
"necesitaremos toda la ayuda que podamos reunir!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:415
msgid "We will help you, and we shall die fighting if it is necessary."
msgstr "Le ayudaremos, y moriremos luchando si es necesario."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:420
msgid ""
"Galas, this is suicidal! Just look at their numbers — if the dwarves did not "
"manage to hold out on their own, the odds our small group will be of any "
"help are unreasonably low. Look — they are already closing in on us from "
"behind!"
msgstr ""
"¡Galas, esto es un suicidio! Mira su número: si los enanos no lograron "
"resistir por sí solos, las probabilidades de que nuestro pequeño grupo pueda "
"ayudar son irrazonablemente bajas. ¡Mira, ya nos están cerrando el paso por "
"detrás!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:425
msgid ""
"We cannot leave the dwarves to perish alone! We are indebted to Althurin for "
"helping us find Elynia, and his people <i>need us now</i>! Besides, if "
"Herthgar is to fall, what obstacles shall be left to impede their advance "
"towards the northlands?"
msgstr ""
"¡No podemos dejar que los enanos perezcan solos! Estamos en deuda con "
"Althurin por ayudarnos a encontrar a Elynia, y su pueblo <i>nos necesita "
"ahora</i>. Además, si Herthgar cae, ¿qué obstáculos quedarán para frenar su "
"avance hacia las tierras del norte?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:430
msgid "Lord Galas is right — we must fight."
msgstr "Lord Galas tiene razón: debemos luchar."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:435
msgid "My lady? But our numbers are small, and we are still weak!"
msgstr "¿Mi señora? ¡Pero somos pocos y aún estamos débiles!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:440
msgid ""
"Hah! You elves might be weak, but my minions are as strong as ever. Let the "
"slaughter commence!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ja! Tal vez ustedes los elfos sean débiles, pero mis esbirros están tan "
"fuertes como siempre. ¡Que comience la carnicería!"

#. [message]: speaker=Alazar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:453
msgid ""
"Your doom is at hand, dwarf king! If you surrender now, the Warlord might "
"show some mercy and spare the lives of your underlings."
msgstr ""
"¡Tu perdición está cerca, rey enano! Si te rindes ahora, el Señor de la "
"Guerra podría mostrar algo de misericordia y perdonar la vida de tus "
"súbditos."

#. [message]: speaker=Wygerm
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:458
msgid "We’ll rip you to pieces if you don’t accept the offer!"
msgstr "¡Te haremos pedazos si no aceptas la oferta!"

#. [message]: speaker=King Asthorgar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:463
msgid ""
"We’ll never surrender to ye and yer loathsome vermin! We shallna’ give our "
"domain to those who kill everything in sight, dabble in the darkest of arts, "
"and nae ken any diplomacy other than that done wi’ fire and swords! May "
"Herthgar be destroyed and forgotten, but it shallna’ be remembered as a "
"kingdom of cowards!"
msgstr ""
"¡Nunca nos rendiremos ante ustedes y sus asquerosas alimañas! ¡Jamás "
"entregaremos nuestro dominio a quienes matan todo a su paso, juegan con las "
"artes más oscuras y no conocen otra diplomacia que la que se hace con fuego "
"y espadas! ¡Que Herthgar sea destruido y olvidado, pero no será recordado "
"como un reino de cobardes!"

#. [message]: speaker=Alazar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:468
msgid ""
"So be it! Your pride and arrogance has sealed your fate! Attack! Wipe these "
"bearded children out of this place! For Uria! For the Empire!"
msgstr ""
"¡Así sea! ¡Tu orgullo y arrogancia han sellado tu destino! ¡Al ataque! "
"¡Borrad a estos niños barbudos de este lugar! ¡Por Uria! ¡Por el Imperio!"

#. [message]: speaker=Oddis
#. The 'Blessed One' is Elynia.
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:474
msgid ""
"Hey, it’s the pointy-eared rats of the forest! And they made it back with "
"the Blessed One!"
msgstr ""
"¡Eh, son las ratas orejudas del bosque! ¡Y han regresado con la Bendecida!"

#. [message]: speaker=Gythrn
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:479
msgid ""
"It matters not. We shall flood the caverns with the elves’ blood, and bring "
"that creature to the Warlord."
msgstr ""
"No importa. ¡Inundaremos las cavernas con la sangre de los elfos y "
"llevaremos a esa criatura ante el Señor de la Guerra!"

#. [message]: speaker=Oddis
#. [message]: speaker=Alazar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:484
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:489
msgid "Aye."
msgstr "Si."

#. [message]: speaker=Armiza'ar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:494
msgid "Aye!"
msgstr "¡Si!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:499
msgid "So annoying."
msgstr "Qué fastidio."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:508
msgid ""
"If I might make a suggestion — using the corpses of the fallen as a barrier "
"could delay our enemies enough to let our best warriors do their duty from "
"safe positions."
msgstr ""
"Si me permitís una sugerencia: usar los cadáveres de los caídos como barrera "
"podría retrasar a nuestros enemigos lo suficiente para que nuestros mejores "
"guerreros cumplan su deber desde posiciones seguras."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:513
msgid ""
"The idea sickens me; many of the corpses will be those of our kinsmen. "
"But... I have to admit it’s an option."
msgstr ""
"La idea me enferma; muchos de esos cadáveres serán de nuestros propios "
"familiares. Pero... debo admitir que es una opción."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:548
msgid ""
"Why are you even fighting alongside us, lich? Are the struggles of my people "
"entertaining to you?"
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué luchas siquiera a nuestro lado, lich? ¿Acaso te entretienen las "
"luchas de mi pueblo?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:556
msgid "Or perhaps you seek redemption? But I find that unlikely."
msgstr "¿O acaso buscas redención? Pero me parece poco probable."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:561
msgid "Why do you want to know?"
msgstr "¿Por qué quieres saberlo?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:566
msgid ""
"Lord Galas and Anlindë seem to consider you an equal, but in truth you are a "
"menace to our lifestyle. Your mere existence would not have been tolerated "
"in the past — and surely you remember that I was once charged with the task "
"of destroying you..."
msgstr ""
"Lord Galas y Anlindë parecen considerarte un igual, pero en realidad eres "
"una amenaza para nuestra forma de vida. Tu mera existencia no habría sido "
"tolerada en el pasado... y seguramente recuerdas que una vez se me encomendó "
"la tarea de destruirte..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:571
msgid ""
"The angry assailants over there seem really interested in chopping off your "
"head, you know. Shouldn’t you focus on the mission at hand instead of "
"blabbering about your precious past like an elderly lady?"
msgstr ""
"Los furiosos atacantes de allí parecen realmente interesados en cortarte la "
"cabeza, ¿sabías? ¿No deberías concentrarte en la misión en lugar de "
"parlotear sobre tu precioso pasado como una anciana?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:607
msgid "What is it with these demons and their endless numbers?"
msgstr "¿Qué pasa con estos demonios y sus números interminables?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:627
msgid "We must persevere. We cannot lose this battle!"
msgstr "Debemos perseverar. ¡No podemos perder esta batalla!"

#. [message]: speaker=Denathor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:639
msgid "Forgive me, my King..."
msgstr "Perdóneme, mi rey..."

#. [message]: speaker=Furin
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:651
msgid "Y’may take me down, but me’ brethren’s hearts still stand!"
msgstr "¡Podéis derribarme, pero los corazones de mis hermanos aún resisten!"

#. [message]: speaker=Armiza'ar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:663
msgid "A curse upon you, heretics!"
msgstr "¡Una maldición sobre ustedes, herejes!"

#. [message]: speaker=Oddis
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:675
msgid "May Yechnagoth swallow your souls!"
msgstr "¡Que Yechnagoth devore sus almas!"

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:689
msgid "Yechnagoth is long gone, you fool!"
msgstr "¡Yechnagoth se ha ido hace mucho, idiota!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:701
msgid "I shall be avenged!"
msgstr "¡Seré vengado!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:713
msgid "Today, you might win the battle, but you will never win the war!"
msgstr "Hoy pueden ganar la batalla, ¡pero jamás ganarán la guerra!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:725
msgid ""
"<i>Ack!</i> Your efforts are in vain — you’re just delaying the inevitable!"
msgstr ""
"<i>¡Ack!</i> Sus esfuerzos son en vano: ¡solo están retrasando lo inevitable!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:734
msgid "At last, we have defeated them! They are retreating!"
msgstr "¡Por fin los hemos derrotado! ¡Se están retirando!"

#. [message]: speaker=Althurin
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:739
msgid ""
"No, lad — I reckon they are preparin’ to retaliate. The way they fight, I "
"doubt we’ve even seen a hair o’ their assault force."
msgstr ""
"No, muchacho. Sospecho que se están preparando para contraatacar. Por cómo "
"luchan, dudo que hayamos visto siquiera un cabello de su fuerza de asalto."

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:755
msgid ""
"These persistent earthworms won’t forfeit as easily as the other clans did, "
"it seems. Time to execute the backup plan, everyone! Retreat!"
msgstr ""
"Estos persistentes gusanos no se rendirán tan fácilmente como lo hicieron "
"los otros clanes, al parecer. ¡Hora de ejecutar el plan de respaldo, todos! "
"¡Retirada!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:760
msgid "The enemy troops are retreating!"
msgstr "¡Las tropas enemigas se están retirando!"

#. [message]: speaker=Althurin
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:765
msgid ""
"’Tis doesn’t sound good, lad. They must be preparin’ to retaliate. The way "
"they fight, I doubt we’ve even seen a hair o’ their assault force."
msgstr ""
"No suena bien, muchacho. Deben estarse preparando para contraatacar. Por "
"cómo luchan, dudo que hayamos visto siquiera un cabello de su fuerza de "
"asalto."

#. [message]: speaker=King Asthorgar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:776
msgid ""
"I ha’ to admit that we gravely underestimated the threat posed by the Chaos "
"Empire. Our losses ha’ been too great... <i>(sighs)</i> At this point, I say "
"we must leave. Mayhap our kin to the northwest would allow us to regroup "
"there."
msgstr ""
"Debo admitir que subestimamos gravemente la amenaza del Imperio del Caos. "
"Nuestras pérdidas han sido demasiado grandes... <i>(suspira)</i> En este "
"punto, digo que debemos partir. Tal vez nuestros parientes del noroeste nos "
"permitan reagruparnos allí."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:781
msgid "So, Herthgar has fallen."
msgstr "Entonces, Herthgar ha caído."

#. [message]: speaker=King Asthorgar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:786
msgid ""
"Dinnae say that! Sure, our home ha’ fallen, but Herthgar is more than just "
"stone and marble. We’ll figure out something later. And as much as it "
"troubles me to think about it, the northern humans will ha’ to deal with "
"these bloodthirsty barbarians somehow. I ken that will be their next move, "
"aye."
msgstr ""
"¡No digas eso! Sí, nuestro hogar ha caído, pero Herthgar es más que piedra y "
"mármol. Ya encontraremos una solución más adelante. Y por mucho que me "
"preocupe pensarlo, los humanos del norte tendrán que arreglárselas con estos "
"sedientos de sangre de alguna forma. Sé que ese será su próximo movimiento, "
"sí."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:791
msgid ""
"Most of our people went north. It is worrying that we haven’t heard anything "
"of them ever since we parted ways, but assuming that nothing bad has "
"occurred to them, we need to warn them of this development, quickly."
msgstr ""
"La mayoría de nuestro pueblo fue hacia el norte. Es preocupante que no "
"hayamos oído nada de ellos desde que nos separamos, pero suponiendo que nada "
"malo les haya ocurrido, debemos advertirles de esta situación rápidamente."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:796
msgid ""
"How prepared are the northerners to deal with an invasion from the Chaos "
"Empire, King Asthorgar? Do you think they would be able to defend the Far "
"North with the elves’ and dwarves’ aid?"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué tan preparados están los norteños para hacer frente a una invasión del "
"Imperio del Caos, rey Asthorgar? ¿Cree que podrían defender el Lejano Norte "
"con la ayuda de elfos y enanos?"

#. [message]: speaker=King Asthorgar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:801
msgid ""
"Dwarves, elves, and humans united under a single banner? I find that highly "
"improbable, lass! I ken it ha’ been thousands o’ years since the last "
"alliance, and it didna’ turn out very well in the end. And in any case, we "
"ha’ our own battles to fight here. I ken the humans will do well on their "
"own as long as they arena’ caught unprepared, but... <i>(shrugs)</i>"
msgstr ""
"¿Enanos, elfos y humanos unidos bajo un mismo estandarte? ¡Lo encuentro muy "
"improbable, muchacha! Sé que han pasado miles de años desde la última "
"alianza, y no terminó muy bien que digamos. Y en cualquier caso, tenemos "
"nuestras propias batallas que librar aquí. Creo que los humanos se las "
"arreglarán por su cuenta mientras no los tomen desprevenidos, pero... <i>(se "
"encoge de hombros)</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:806
msgid ""
"We will warn them and seek their help regardless. We can’t keep running away "
"from the enemy like rats; there <i>has</i> to be some way to stop them "
"before there is no more land left on the continent for us."
msgstr ""
"Los advertiremos y buscaremos su ayuda de todos modos. No podemos seguir "
"huyendo del enemigo como ratas; tiene que haber alguna forma de detenerlos "
"antes de que no quede tierra en el continente para nosotros."

#. [message]: speaker=Althurin
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:811
msgid ""
"My king, d’ye really think we can vacate Herthgar before the demons return?"
msgstr ""
"Mi rey, ¿cree de verdad que podemos evacuar Herthgar antes de que los "
"demonios regresen?"

#. [message]: speaker=King Asthorgar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:816
msgid "We must at least try — I fear we dinna’ have a choice at this point."
msgstr ""
"Debemos al menos intentarlo; temo que no tenemos otra opción en este punto."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:821
msgid ""
"King, if you attempt to evacuate, it is quite likely that the enemy forces "
"will manage to sneak up on your people from behind and perpetrate yet "
"another slaughter. But there is a simple solution to this quandary — I "
"believe Mal Keshar could lend me his minions to aid in setting up an ambush "
"to keep the enemy from advancing."
msgstr ""
"Rey, si intenta evacuar, es muy probable que las fuerzas enemigas logren "
"acercarse a su gente por detrás y perpetren otra masacre. Pero hay una "
"solución sencilla a este dilema: creo que Mal Keshar podría prestarme sus "
"esbirros para ayudar a preparar una emboscada que impida el avance del "
"enemigo."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:828
msgid ""
"What? But... Anlindë, you can’t possibly fend off those fiends alone! Odds "
"are... you won’t be able to get back to us. Don’t do the same as Lord "
"Lédinor... please..."
msgstr ""
"¿Qué? Pero... ¡Anlindë, no puedes enfrentarte sola a esos demonios! Lo más "
"probable es que... no puedas regresar con nosotros. No hagas lo mismo que "
"Lord Lédinor... por favor..."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:833
msgid ""
"Our Lady of Light once said that there things more important in this world "
"than the lives of the few. For me, the safety of our people is far more "
"important than my own, and as you already know, I have a debt to repay. Our "
"past will never cease to haunt me, and I certainly will never be able to "
"repair the great damage we caused back then; but if I am going to die, I "
"would prefer it to be for your sake."
msgstr ""
"Nuestra Señora de la Luz dijo una vez que hay cosas más importantes en este "
"mundo que la vida de unos pocos. Para mí, la seguridad de nuestro pueblo es "
"mucho más importante que la mía, y como ya sabes, tengo una deuda que "
"saldar. Nuestro pasado nunca dejará de atormentarme, y ciertamente nunca "
"podré reparar el gran daño que causamos entonces; pero si he de morir, "
"preferiría que fuera por ustedes."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:838
msgid ""
"If the circumstances hadn’t conspired against it, I would have done it back "
"in the Valley instead of Lédinor, but you were too young, and I first had to "
"make sure you were ready. Since then, you have proven yourself to be a "
"fierce warrior and a capable leader, Galas; I’m proud of you."
msgstr ""
"Si las circunstancias no se hubieran confabulado en contra, lo habría hecho "
"en el Valle en lugar de Lédinor, pero eras demasiado joven, y primero tenía "
"que asegurarme de que estuvieras preparado. Desde entonces, has demostrado "
"ser un guerrero feroz y un líder capaz, Galas; estoy orgullosa de ti."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:843
msgid ""
"This is insane! What purpose does it serve to throw your life away like "
"this?! Let Mal Keshar dispatch his minions; there is absolutely no need for "
"you to get involved—"
msgstr ""
"¡Esto es una locura! ¿Qué propósito tiene arrojar tu vida así?! Deja que Mal "
"Keshar envíe a sus esbirros; no hay absolutamente ninguna necesidad de que "
"tú te involucres—"

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:848
msgid ""
"And leave them to be quickly disposed of by the enemy? We cannot afford such "
"a risk right now, Galas! Your survival... you are far more important! There "
"is a much greater foe hiding in these caves, and sooner or later he will "
"catch up with us, and Elynia is in no condition to fight anyone."
msgstr ""
"¿Y dejarlos para que el enemigo los aniquile rápidamente? ¡No podemos "
"permitirnos tal riesgo ahora, Galas! Tu supervivencia... ¡tú eres mucho más "
"importante! Hay un enemigo mucho mayor escondido en estas cavernas, y tarde "
"o temprano nos alcanzará, y Elynia no está en condiciones de luchar contra "
"nadie."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:853
msgid "What? But I—"
msgstr "¿Qué? Pero yo—"

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:858
msgid ""
"I have seen your performance in this battle, my lady, and I regret saying "
"this but... I saw you do far better in Wesmere. It’s plainly evident that "
"you have been dormant for too long."
msgstr ""
"He visto su desempeño en esta batalla, mi señora, y lamento decir esto "
"pero... la vi actuar mucho mejor en Wesmere. Es evidente que ha permanecido "
"demasiado tiempo inactiva."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:867
msgid ""
"About my words... it is not necessary to take them to heart. Anlindë, we "
"will need all available spellcasters on the front line if our plans come to "
"fruition. The ill-gotten power you wield is far superior than the norm for "
"our kin, and combined with the might of the undead, it could offer us an "
"unprecedented tactical advantage. How may I persuade you to reconsider?"
msgstr ""
"Sobre mis palabras... no es necesario que las tome a pecho. Anlindë, "
"necesitaremos a todos los hechiceros disponibles en la primera línea si "
"nuestros planes se cumplen. El poder ilícito que usted maneja es muy "
"superior al de la norma entre los nuestros, y combinado con la fuerza de los "
"no muertos, podría brindarnos una ventaja táctica sin precedentes. ¿Cómo "
"podría persuadirla de que lo reconsidere?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:872
msgid ""
"You cannot. I feel that my mission and my fate lies here, in the very heart "
"of Irdya. Allow me to protect elvenkind a last time, my lady; I shall "
"obliterate every demon, every cultist, and every dark soldier who dares to "
"approach this keep; and even if it is to be with my dying breath, I shall "
"vanquish their Warlord, and turn fate in our favor."
msgstr ""
"No puede. Siento que mi misión y mi destino están aquí, en el mismo corazón "
"de Irdya. Permítame proteger a los elfos por última vez, mi señora; "
"aniquilaré a cada demonio, cada sectario y cada soldado oscuro que se atreva "
"a acercarse a este castillo; y aun si ha de ser con mi último aliento, "
"derrotaré a su caudillo y haré que el destino se incline a nuestro favor."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:881
msgid ""
"You have lived for so long, and you have seen so much, so many things that "
"were never even recorded in books... I don’t understand why... why do you "
"want it to end like this?"
msgstr ""
"Has vivido tanto tiempo, y has visto tantas cosas, tantas que ni siquiera "
"fueron registradas en libros... No entiendo por qué... ¿por qué quieres que "
"termine así?"

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:886
msgid ""
"Picture living for thousands of years knowing it was only made possible by "
"the suffering and death of millions of innocent souls. Eternal life becomes "
"a disillusioning burden as time passes by and you see... you see everything "
"turn to dust. And then your memories begin to fade away as well... You "
"eventually forget all positive experiences and can only recall the horrors "
"that haunt you in your sleep."
msgstr ""
"Imagina vivir miles de años sabiendo que solo fue posible gracias al "
"sufrimiento y la muerte de millones de almas inocentes. La vida eterna se "
"convierte en una carga desilusionante a medida que pasa el tiempo y ves... "
"ves cómo todo se convierte en polvo. Y luego tus recuerdos también empiezan "
"a desvanecerse... Con el tiempo olvidas todas las experiencias positivas y "
"solo puedes recordar los horrores que te atormentan en tus sueños."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:891
msgid ""
"At least none of you will have to live with the knowledge that you were "
"accomplices of the evil that brought elvenkind to its knees."
msgstr ""
"Al menos ninguno de ustedes tendrá que vivir con el conocimiento de que "
"fueron cómplices del mal que puso a los elfos de rodillas."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/11_Strike_on_Herthgar.cfg:900
msgid ""
"So be it. Your sacrifice won’t be forgotten, and I swear that I will not "
"rest until the last of our enemies is reduced to cinders on the ground. May "
"the Lords of Light guide you in your last mission."
msgstr ""
"Así sea. Tu sacrificio no será olvidado, y juro que no descansaré hasta que "
"el último de nuestros enemigos haya sido reducido a cenizas sobre la tierra. "
"Que los Señores de la Luz te guíen en tu última misión."

#. [side]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:35
msgid "team_name^Elves and Dwarves"
msgstr "Elfos y Enanos"

#. [set_variables]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:292
msgid "Locate and eliminate the rearguard captain"
msgstr "Localiza y elimina al capitán de la retaguardia"

#. [set_variables]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:294
msgid "Defeat the Goliath"
msgstr "Derrota al Goliath"

#. [set_variables]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:296
msgid "Defeat Yreul"
msgstr "Derrota a Yreul"

#. [literal]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:349
msgid ""
"In this scenario, you may only recall or recruit units during the first turn"
msgstr ""
"En este escenario, solo puedes recuperar o reclutar unidades durante el "
"primer turno."

#. [literal]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:351
msgid ""
"Because Mal Keshar has granted control of most of his undead minions to "
"Anlindë, any undead veterans you do not recall in this scenario will be "
"permanently lost."
msgstr ""
"Como Mal Keshar ha cedido el control de la mayoría de sus esbirros no-"
"muertos a Anlindë, cualquier veterano no-muerto que no recuperes en este "
"escenario se perderá de forma permanente."

#. [literal]
#. [scenario]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:353
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:439
msgid "You may not recall or recruit units"
msgstr "No puedes recuperar ni reclutar unidades"

#. [value]: condition=win
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:408
msgid "Galas, Elynia, or Mal Keshar must reach the exit to the northlands"
msgstr ""
"Galas, Elynia o Mal Keshar deben alcanzar la salida hacia las tierras del "
"norte"

#. [message]: speaker=King Asthorgar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:429
msgid ""
"The exit’s to the north. But before we proceed, I must warn ye: it ha’ been "
"long since we last walked these caves, so we should be prepared to deal with "
"anything that might be awaitin’ down the road."
msgstr ""
"La salida está al norte. Pero antes de seguir, debo advertirles: hace mucho "
"que no caminamos por estas cavernas, así que debemos estar preparados para "
"cualquier cosa que pueda esperarnos en el camino."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:434
msgid ""
"Such as an unexpected encounter with Chaos troops? We are accustomed to that "
"kind of thing after our quest underground."
msgstr ""
"¿Como un encuentro inesperado con tropas del Caos? Ya estamos acostumbrados "
"a ese tipo de cosas tras nuestra travesía bajo tierra."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:439
msgid ""
"We must make haste, though. We don’t know for how long Anlindë’s strategy is "
"going to work and provide us with safe passage."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, debemos darnos prisa. No sabemos cuánto tiempo más funcionará "
"la estrategia de Anlindë ni cuánto nos asegurará un paso seguro."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:444
msgid ""
"Indeed... I would be unable to bear the thought of her sacrifice turning out "
"to be in vain after so much."
msgstr ""
"En efecto... No podría soportar la idea de que su sacrificio resulte en vano "
"después de todo."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:449
msgid ""
"Hmph, I sure hope she has put my minions to good use. I had grown fond of "
"some of them. Ah well, there will be plenty of opportunities to raise more "
"later."
msgstr ""
"Hmph, espero que haya dado un buen uso a mis esbirros. Le había tomado "
"cariño a algunos de ellos. Bah, ya habrá muchas oportunidades para levantar "
"más después."

#. [message]: type=Fire Ant Queen
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:494
msgid "<i>Screeeeeech!</i>"
msgstr "<i>¡Scriiiiiii!</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:500
msgid ""
"Ugh, great, just what we needed. I hate those things so much... I can’t wait "
"to leave these caves so we never have to deal with swarms of giant insects "
"again."
msgstr ""
"Ugh, genial, justo lo que necesitábamos. Odio tanto esas cosas... No puedo "
"esperar a salir de estas cuevas para no tener que lidiar nunca más con "
"enjambres de insectos gigantes."

#. [event]: id=Yreul, type=Chaos Soulhunter, id=Karshas, type=Troll Warrior
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:539
msgid "Yreul"
msgstr "Yreul"

#. [event]: id=Yreul, type=Chaos Soulhunter, id=Karshas, type=Troll Warrior
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:566
msgid "Karshas"
msgstr "Karshas"

#. [unit]: type=Troll Rocklobber, id=Burg
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:579
msgid "Burg"
msgstr "Burg"

#. [message]: speaker=Karshas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:596
msgid "Damned creatures! You kill our children! You pay with your blood!"
msgstr "¡Malditas criaturas! ¡Mataron a nuestros hijos! ¡Paguen con su sangre!"

#. [message]: speaker=Yreul
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:601
msgid ""
"Fat chance, dimwit. Get out of the way this instant, unless you would rather "
"be ground into dust!"
msgstr ""
"Ja, ni lo sueñes, idiota. ¡Quítate del camino ahora mismo, a menos que "
"quieras ser reducido a polvo!"

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:606
msgid ""
"Hey, hey, what do we have here? The elfses and dwarfses are tryin’ to escape "
"thru the backdoor!"
msgstr ""
"¡Eh, eh! ¿Qué tenemos aquí? ¡Los elfitos y enanitos están intentando escapar "
"por la puerta trasera!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:612
msgid "Uh..."
msgstr "Oh..."

#. [message]: speaker=Yreul
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:617
msgid ""
"Hah! So they are coming to us now! What’s your clever plan, rats? I am "
"certain the captain will be very pleased to see your impaled heads topping "
"our banners!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ja! ¡Así que ahora vienen hacia nosotros! ¿Cuál es su brillante plan, "
"ratas? Estoy seguro de que el capitán se alegrará mucho de ver sus cabezas "
"empaladas ondeando en nuestras banderas."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:622
msgid ""
"We’ll have to deal with this scum first, lest they bring news of us to their "
"superiors."
msgstr ""
"Primero tendremos que ocuparnos de esta escoria, antes de que lleven "
"noticias sobre nosotros a sus superiores."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:634
msgid "Defeated... by rats!"
msgstr "¡Derrotado... por ratas!"

#. [message]: type=Goliath
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:694
msgid "The vermin must die! Affirmative!"
msgstr "¡Las sabandijas deben morir! ¡Afirmativo!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:702
msgid "Aaah! Another one of these metallic beasts!"
msgstr "¡Aaah! ¡Otra de esas bestias metálicas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:707
msgid "This is turning out to be harder than we expected."
msgstr "Esto está resultando ser más difícil de lo que esperábamos."

#. [event]: gender=female
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:746
msgid "Lilith"
msgstr "Lilith"

#. [message]: speaker=Lilith
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:769
msgid "There they are! Don’t let them cross the bridge!"
msgstr "¡Ahí están! ¡No los dejen cruzar el puente!"

#. [message]: type=Hellhound
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:774
msgid "Grrrrrr..."
msgstr "Grrrrrr..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:779
msgid ""
"Hm, I see — they are the rearguard of our ‘friends’. Their blockade would be "
"far more effective if they just demolished the bridge, so surely their "
"captain is right across."
msgstr ""
"Hm, ya veo: son la retaguardia de nuestros ‘amigos’. Su bloqueo sería mucho "
"más efectivo si simplemente destruyeran el puente, así que seguramente su "
"capitán está justo al otro lado."

#. [event]: id=Lagonus, type=Gutwrencher Imp
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:797
msgid "Lagonus"
msgstr "Lagonus"

#. [message]: speaker=Lagonus
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:822
msgid ""
"I swear to Uria, this is the end of the road for you, insolent maggots! "
"Prepare to die!"
msgstr ""
"¡Juro por Uria que este es el fin del camino para ustedes, larvas "
"insolentes! ¡Prepárense para morir!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:827
msgid "Wishful thinking, filth!"
msgstr "¡Sueños inútiles, basura!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:839
msgid "How could I fail like this? Forgive me, Master... <i>(gurgle)</i>"
msgstr "¿Cómo pude fallar así? Perdóname, maestro... <i>(gluglú)</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:853
msgid "The imp’s body is dissolving into slime!"
msgstr "¡El cuerpo del diablillo se está disolviendo en lodo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:911
msgid "This is truly disgusting."
msgstr "Esto es verdaderamente repugnante."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:958
msgid "female^The exit, at last! Follow me!"
msgstr "¡La salida, por fin! ¡Síganme!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:959
msgid "The exit, at last! Follow me!"
msgstr "¡La salida, por fin! ¡Síganme!"

#. [message]: role=complainer
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:986
msgid ""
"Wait a moment, we cannot leave yet! If we don’t dispose of our pursuers, "
"they may report our position to their leaders!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esperen un momento, no podemos irnos todavía! Si no nos deshacemos de "
"nuestros perseguidores, podrían informar de nuestra posición a sus líderes."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12_The_Escape.cfg:999
msgid ""
"I can hear their main assault force approaching from behind. Oh, forgive me, "
"Anlindë..."
msgstr ""
"Puedo oír que su fuerza de asalto principal se acerca por detrás. Oh, "
"perdóname, Anlindë..."

#. [scenario]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12x_Outside.cfg:4
msgid "Outside"
msgstr "Exterior"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12x_Outside.cfg:144
msgid "We made it! And there are no signs of demons."
msgstr "¡Lo logramos! Y no hay señales de demonios."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12x_Outside.cfg:149
msgid ""
"Ah, I can feel the wind in my hair again... It is cold, but it’s a "
"refreshing change from the stale air of the deep caverns."
msgstr ""
"Ah… puedo sentir el viento en mi cabello otra vez… Hace frío, pero es un "
"cambio refrescante después del aire viciado de las cavernas profundas."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12x_Outside.cfg:154
msgid ""
"You know, returning to the surface doesn’t seem all that great to me, but at "
"least it’s not the desert."
msgstr ""
"Sabes, volver a la superficie no me parece tan maravilloso… pero al menos no "
"es el desierto."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12x_Outside.cfg:159
msgid ""
"I wish Anlindë was here with us to breathe the fresh air and contemplate the "
"beautiful landscape."
msgstr ""
"Ojalá Anlindë estuviera aquí con nosotros para respirar el aire fresco y "
"contemplar el hermoso paisaje."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12x_Outside.cfg:168
msgid "So do I."
msgstr "Yo también."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12x_Outside.cfg:197
msgid ""
"And so, Galas and his band left the dark caves beneath the Heart Mountains "
"for the northern lands. After making sure that there were no foes in sight, "
"they signaled the rest of their group to emerge from the caverns.\n"
"\n"
"The fate of Anlindë was to remain uncertain to all of them. But this did not "
"deter other elves and dwarves from telling legends of her last battle "
"against Chaos. Her courage and resolve would be remembered by many for "
"generations to come; and in time, the dwarves of Herthgar would build a "
"gleaming silver temple to pay tribute to her great sacrifice."
msgstr ""
"Y así, Galas y su grupo abandonaron las oscuras cavernas bajo las Montañas "
"Profundas para dirigirse a las tierras del norte. Tras asegurarse de que no "
"había enemigos a la vista, hicieron señales al resto del grupo para que "
"emergiera de las cavernas.\n"
"\n"
"El destino de Anlindë seguiría siendo incierto para todos ellos. Pero esto "
"no impidió que otros elfos y enanos contaran leyendas sobre su última "
"batalla contra el Caos. Su valor y determinación serían recordados por "
"muchos durante generaciones; y con el tiempo, los enanos de Herthgar "
"construirían un resplandeciente templo de plata para rendir homenaje a su "
"gran sacrificio."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/12x_Outside.cfg:208
msgid "May your soul find peace, Anlindë."
msgstr "Que tu alma encuentre la paz, Anlindë."

#. [side]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:50
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:47
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:44
msgid "team_name^Chaos Warlord"
msgstr "Señora de la Guerra del Caos"

#. [side]: type=Gutwrencher Imp, id=Laveri
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:94
msgid "Laveri"
msgstr "Laveri"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:298
msgid "Pelaes"
msgstr "Pelaes"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:299
msgid "Pelcatil"
msgstr "Pelcatil"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:301
msgid "Marlin"
msgstr "Marlin"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:302
msgid "Durcanos"
msgstr "Durcanos"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:306
msgid "Izkotep"
msgstr "Izkotep"

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:329
msgid "Shrieek!"
msgstr "Shirieek"

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:334
msgid "What in the world are those creatures doing?"
msgstr "¿Qué demonios están haciendo esas criaturas?"

#. [message]: speaker=Durcanos
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:339
msgid ""
"I’m na’ sure, they seem to be laying larvae on the flooded western keep."
msgstr ""
"No estoy seguro, parecen estar depositando larvas en la fortaleza occidental "
"inundada."

#. [message]: speaker=Marlin
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:344
msgid ""
"My lady, we swear we winna’ rest until either we ha’ spilled all the the "
"blood o’ those wretched freaks, or our dead bodies are all layin’ on the "
"floor. We’ll fight for ye. May the glorious ruins of Herthgar be our tomb!"
msgstr ""
"Mi señora, juramos que no descansaremos hasta haber derramado toda la sangre "
"de esos malditos engendros, o hasta que nuestros cadáveres queden tendidos "
"en el suelo. ¡Lucharemos por vos! ¡Que las gloriosas ruinas de Herthgar sean "
"nuestra tumba!"

#. [message]: speaker=Laveri
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:349
msgid ""
"Ah, the stench of death and decay that fills this place only intensifies my "
"hunger. Let us make haste and finish this once and for all so we can have "
"our well-deserved feast!"
msgstr ""
"Ah, el hedor a muerte y descomposición que llena este lugar solo intensifica "
"mi hambre. ¡Démonos prisa y acabemos con esto de una vez por todas para "
"disfrutar de nuestro bien merecido festín!"

#. [message]: speaker=Izkotep
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:354
msgid "Look, the elvish witch is on the dwarvish capital’s keep!"
msgstr "¡Miren, la bruja élfica está en la fortaleza de la capital enana!"

#. [message]: speaker=Laveri
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:361
msgid ""
"Graaargh, kill her, now! And the elf leader too! And find the filthy faerie "
"of the forests — but remember the Warlord’s orders: trap the creature, but "
"she must not come to harm! We need her alive and intact."
msgstr ""
"¡Graaargh, mátenla ahora! ¡Y también al líder élfico! Y encuentren a la "
"asquerosa hada de los bosques... pero recuerden las órdenes del Señor de la "
"Guerra: atrapen a la criatura, pero no debe sufrir daño alguno. ¡La "
"necesitamos viva e intacta!"

#. [message]: speaker=Izkotep
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:366
msgid "Attack now! You know what to do!"
msgstr "¡Atacad ahora! ¡Saben lo que deben hacer!"

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:371
msgid ""
"Their final assault begins. Hopefully we’ll manage to give Galas and the "
"rest enough time to escape unnoticed."
msgstr ""
"Su asalto final comienza. Esperemos poder dar a Galas y a los demás tiempo "
"suficiente para escapar sin ser vistos."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:401
msgid ""
"Aaargh!! It’s pointless! <i>(spits)</i> Killing me won’t do anything to "
"weaken our forces! We are unstoppable!"
msgstr ""
"¡¡Aaargh!! ¡Es inútil! <i>(escupe)</i> ¡Matarme no hará nada para debilitar "
"nuestras fuerzas! ¡Somos imparables!"

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:577
msgid ""
"Great. Nobody informed me that there was <i>another</i> alternate entrance "
"to this chamber in the west. We ought to seal that somehow."
msgstr ""
"Genial. Nadie me informó de que había <i>otra</i> entrada alternativa a esta "
"cámara por el oeste. Debemos sellarla de algún modo."

#. [unit]: type=Chaos Warlord, id=Chaos Warlord
#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:610
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:691
msgid "Chaos Warlord"
msgstr "Señor de la Guerra del Caos"

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:671
msgid ""
"Their commander, at last! Come and fight me, fiend! This place shall be your "
"grave!"
msgstr ""
"¡Su comandante, al fin! ¡Ven y enfréntame, engendro! ¡Este lugar será tu "
"tumba!"

#. [message]: speaker=Chaos Warlord
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:676
msgid ""
"<i>(muffled metallic voice)</i> You should do like your friends and run "
"away, little worm, unless you would prefer me to tear your frail body to "
"pieces and delight in your suffering."
msgstr ""
"<i>(voz metálica amortiguada)</i> Deberías hacer como tus amigos y huir, "
"gusano insignificante, a menos que prefieras que despedace tu frágil cuerpo "
"y me deleite con tu sufrimiento."

#. [message]: speaker=Chaos Warlord
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:681
msgid ""
"Trying to divert my attention is futile. I already know where your friends "
"are; it is all in your weak and permeable mind. Your pointless sacrifice "
"does not fool our Master either, and neither will it save the cowards from "
"his wrath. We’ll find them all in due time."
msgstr ""
"Intentar desviar mi atención es inútil. Ya sé dónde están tus amigos; todo "
"está en tu mente débil y vulnerable. Tu sacrificio inútil tampoco engaña a "
"nuestro Amo, y no salvará a esos cobardes de su ira. Los encontraremos a "
"todos a su debido tiempo."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:686
msgid "Not if I can stop you first!"
msgstr "¡No si puedo detenerte antes!"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:691
msgid "Leader of the Invading Forces"
msgstr "Líder de las Fuerzas Invasoras"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:698
msgid "Vanquish the Chaos Warlord"
msgstr "Señor de la Guerra del Caos"

#. [message]: speaker=Chaos Warlord
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:764
msgid ""
"You will never succeed in slaying me with such pitiful weapons and spells."
msgstr "Jamás lograrán matarme con armas y hechizos tan patéticos."

#. [message]: speaker=Chaos Warlord
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:769
msgid ""
"By the power you have bestowed upon me, Uria, may the spells conferring life "
"to the dead be canceled now!"
msgstr ""
"Por el poder otorgado a mí, Uria, ¡que los conjuros que animan a los no-"
"muertos sean cancelados ahora!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:813
msgid "I am... sorry, Galas... I... failed..."
msgstr "Lo siento... tanto... Galas... fallé..."

#. [message]: speaker=Chaos Warlord
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:859
msgid "You still draw breath? This is an infuriating waste of my time."
msgstr "¿Aún respiras? Esto es una irritante pérdida de mi tiempo."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:864
msgid "... Heh."
msgstr "... Eh."

#. [message]: speaker=Chaos Warlord
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:871
msgid "What is this?!"
msgstr "¡¿Qué es esto?!"

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:880
msgid "I’m not... leaving this world... without taking you with me..."
msgstr "No... dejaré este mundo... sin llevarte conmigo..."

#. [message]: race=demon,imps
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:885
msgid "Aiyeee!! Retreat, retreat!!"
msgstr "¡¡Aiyeee!! ¡¡Retirada, retirada!!"

#. [message]: speaker=Chaos Warlord
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:894
msgid ""
"Do you truly believe it will be all over just like this? How naïve of "
"someone like you, a past servant of Zhangor."
msgstr ""
"¿De verdad crees que todo terminará así de simple? Qué ingenuo de tu parte, "
"alguien que fue sirviente de Zhangor."

#. [message]: speaker=Anlindë
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/13_Face_your_Fate.cfg:899
msgid "Death will take us all now... None of that matters anymore."
msgstr "La muerte nos llevará a todos ahora... Nada de eso importa ya."

#. [scenario]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:4
msgid "Clearing the Road"
msgstr "Despejando el Camino"

#. [side]: type=Saurian Flanker, id=Grilock
#. [side]: type=Orcish Nightblade, id=Arghalon
#. [side]: type=Orcish Slurbow, id=Tan Zalfargat
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:38
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:82
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/15_Shadows_of_Time.cfg:145
msgid "team_name^Mercenaries"
msgstr "Mercenarios"

#. [side]: type=Saurian Flanker, id=Grilock
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:54
msgid "Grilock"
msgstr "Grilock"

#. [side]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:71
msgid "team_name^Aragwaithi"
msgstr "Aragwaithi"

#. [side]: type=Orcish Nightblade, id=Arghalon
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:98
msgid "Arghalon"
msgstr "Arghalon"

#. [message]: speaker=King Asthorgar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:289
msgid ""
"Our forefathers could never ha’ imagined their legacy would meet such a "
"shameful end. Shameful, I say! I canna’ wait to see the faces of our kin in "
"Valgran — surely they will be amused to see the King of Herthgar become the "
"head of a band of homeless beggars! PAH!"
msgstr ""
"Nuestros antepasados nunca habrían imaginado que su legado terminaría de "
"forma tan vergonzosa. ¡Vergonzosa, digo! ¡No puedo esperar para ver las "
"caras de nuestra gente en Valgran — seguro se divertirán al ver al Rey de "
"Herthgar convertirse en el líder de una banda de mendigos sin hogar! ¡Pah!"

#. [message]: speaker=Althurin
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:294
msgid "My king, you didn’t seem too bothered about the situation back in—"
msgstr "Mi rey, no parecías muy preocupado por la situación en—"

#. [message]: speaker=King Asthorgar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:299
msgid ""
"And what did ye expect me to do, Althurin? Act pessimistic in front of our "
"people right before leading them out o’ the caves on a suicide mission?! "
"’Course that was na’ option."
msgstr ""
"¿Y qué esperabas que hiciera, Althurin? ¿Actuar pesimista frente a nuestra "
"gente justo antes de sacarlos de las cuevas en una misión suicida? ¡Claro "
"que no era una opción!"

#. [message]: speaker=King Asthorgar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:310
msgid ""
"I apologize for venting like this, Galas, lady, I just couldna’ hold my "
"frustration any longer. (<i>sighs</i>)"
msgstr ""
"Disculpen que me desahogue así, Galas, dama, simplemente no pude contener "
"más mi frustración. (<i>suspira</i>)"

#. [message]: speaker=King Asthorgar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:321
msgid ""
"Though, mayhap there is a silver lining to all this. What d’ye think, Galas?"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, tal vez haya un lado positivo en todo esto. ¿Qué opinas, Galas?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:326
msgid ""
"It is our hope that the northerners will acknowledge the threat and help us "
"retaliate, Majesty. It would be highly unreasonable on their part to turn a "
"blind eye to the destruction that the Chaos Empire has and will continue to "
"wreak."
msgstr ""
"Esperamos que los del norte reconozcan la amenaza y nos ayuden a "
"represaliar, Majestad. Sería muy irracional de su parte hacer la vista gorda "
"ante la destrucción que el Imperio del Caos ha causado y seguirá causando."

#. [message]: speaker=King Asthorgar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:335
msgid ""
"Only a complete fool wouldna’ take ye and yer people seriously, Galas. Would "
"that we had the men and resources to aid ye in this crusade... Still, "
"Althurin would like to hand ye a gift as token of our gratitude. Use it "
"wisely."
msgstr ""
"Sólo un completo tonto no te tomaría a ti ni a tu gente en serio, Galas. "
"Ojalá tuviéramos los hombres y recursos para ayudarte en esta cruzada... Aun "
"así, Althurin quisiera entregarte un regalo como muestra de nuestra "
"gratitud. Úsalo sabiamente."

#. [message]: speaker=King Asthorgar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:342
msgid ""
"I wouldna’ be surprised if our children a few generations from now spoke "
"legends about the exploits of the Elves of the Valley of Elynia against the "
"dark Empire in the south. Farewell! May the Bright Gods let our paths cross "
"again!"
msgstr ""
"No me sorprendería si dentro de unas generaciones nuestros hijos hablaran "
"leyendas sobre las hazañas de los Elfos del Valle de Elynia contra el oscuro "
"Imperio del sur. ¡Adiós! ¡Que los Dioses Brillantes permitan que nuestros "
"caminos se crucen de nuevo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:347
msgid "Farewell, friends."
msgstr "Adiós, amigos."

#. [message]: speaker=Althurin
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:352
msgid ""
"Farewell, Elynia! I wish we had more time to exchange notes about our "
"cultures’ respective brands of magic."
msgstr ""
"Adiós, Elynia. Ojalá tuviéramos más tiempo para intercambiar ideas sobre las "
"formas de magia de nuestras culturas."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:357
msgid "Bye, Althurin. May we meet a second time."
msgstr "Adiós, Althurin. Que nos encontremos una segunda vez."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:386
msgid ""
"And thus, the dwarves of Herthgar and the elves of the Valley parted ways."
msgstr ""
"Y así, los enanos de Herthgar y los elfos del Valle tomaron caminos "
"separados."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:391
msgid "So, now we need to find the rest of the elves. Any ideas?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces, ahora necesitamos encontrar al resto de los elfos. ¿Alguna idea?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:396
msgid ""
"We should be able to find the northern country’s capital if we follow the "
"dwarves’ instructions. It’s supposed to be only about three days from here "
"if we avoid stopping to rest during daytime. I’m just unsure about walking "
"through human lands with a lich among us..."
msgstr ""
"Deberíamos poder encontrar la capital del país del norte si seguimos las "
"instrucciones de los enanos. Se supone que está a unas tres jornadas de aquí "
"si evitamos descansar durante el día. Solo que no me siento cómodo caminando "
"por tierras humanas con un lich entre nosotros..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:401
msgid "I am ready to banish him from this world if you wish, my lord."
msgstr "Estoy lista para desterrarlo de este mundo si así lo deseas, mi señor."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:406
msgid ""
"You... don’t need to call me ‘lord’. It doesn’t sit well with me, "
"considering how much older you... I mean, no offense my lady, but..."
msgstr ""
"No... no hace falta que me llames ‘señor’. No me sienta bien, considerando "
"que tú eres mucho mayor... No es por ofender, mi señora, pero..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:411
msgid ""
"Hahahaha! I did notice it makes you uncomfortable, young Galas. I have been "
"but a homeless wanderer for so long, I think it only proper for me to defer "
"to the last regent lord of my kin — but if you wish me to stop then I "
"will... (<i>moves closer</i>) on the condition that you call me Elynia like "
"I said before."
msgstr ""
"¡Jajaja! Me di cuenta de que te incomoda, joven Galas. He sido una errante "
"sin hogar por tanto tiempo que creo que es justo deferir al último señor "
"regente de mi pueblo — pero si quieres que pare, lo haré... (<i>se acerca</"
"i>) con la condición de que me llames Elynia, como dije antes."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:416
msgid "(<i>flustered</i>) I will... try."
msgstr "(<i>sonrojado</i>) Lo... intentaré."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:423
msgid ""
"Pffft, what is this? You both have fancy titles to flaunt around, and "
"instead opt for this trite fraternization thing? This is a waste of "
"everyone’s time."
msgstr ""
"Pf, ¿qué es esto? Ambos tienen títulos elegantes para presumir, y en vez de "
"eso optan por esta cursilería de fraternidad? Esto es una pérdida de tiempo "
"para todos."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:428
msgid "As if you ever cared about anyone’s titles or ranks, Mal Keshar."
msgstr "Como si alguna vez te importaran los títulos o rangos, Mal Keshar."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:437
msgid "Someone is observing us."
msgstr "Alguien nos está observando."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:465
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:793
msgid "Blynyr"
msgstr "Blynyr"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:474
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:802
msgid "Zednal"
msgstr "Zednal"

#. [message]: speaker=Erathan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:484
msgid "Outsiders! What brings you to Aragwaith territory?"
msgstr "¡Forasteros! ¿Qué los trae al territorio de Aragwaith?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:489
msgid ""
"You don’t need to point your bow at us, sir. We come in peace, as refugees!"
msgstr ""
"No necesita apuntarnos con su arco, señor. Venimos en paz, ¡somos refugiados!"

#. [message]: speaker=Erathan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:494
msgid ""
"Is that a lich behind you?! This is unexpected. But nothing we cannot handle!"
msgstr ""
"¿Ese es un lich detrás de ustedes? Esto es inesperado. ¡Pero nada que no "
"podamos manejar!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:499
msgid "Someone ought to teach you to pick your fights more cautiously, whelp—"
msgstr ""
"Alguien debería enseñarte a escoger tus peleas con más cuidado, cachorro—"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:504
msgid ""
"No! Please, listen to us. We are elves! You may have heard of a large number "
"of us coming to this country seeking refuge from a war in the southern lands."
msgstr ""
"¡No! Por favor, escúchenos. ¡Somos elfos! Quizás hayan oído que un gran "
"número de nosotros llegó a este país buscando refugio de una guerra en las "
"tierras del sur."

#. [message]: speaker=Erathan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:509
msgid ""
"... Elves? Refugees, you say? Hah! Elves, indeed — those pointy-eared "
"creatures that don’t exist but in tall tales of a past age."
msgstr ""
"... ¿Elfos? ¿Refugiados, dices? ¡Ja! Elfos, sí — esas criaturas de orejas "
"puntiagudas que sólo existen en cuentos de otra época."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:514
msgid ""
"Galas, allow me to do the talking. I could seduce him into cooperating with "
"us."
msgstr "Galas, déjame hablar. Podría seducirlo para que coopere con nosotros."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:519
msgid "Galas, boy, I am ready to strike down this nuisance if you wish."
msgstr "Galas, muchacho, estoy listo para eliminar esta molestia si quieres."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:524
msgid "Sssht, quiet you two!"
msgstr "¡Sssht, silencio los dos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Zednal
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:529
msgid ""
"Erathan, they must be the creatures we were searching for. Maybe we should "
"take them to the Grand Council before those fiends return."
msgstr ""
"Erathan, deben ser las criaturas que buscábamos. Quizás deberíamos llevarlos "
"al Gran Consejo antes de que esos demonios regresen."

#. [message]: speaker=Erathan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:538
msgid ""
"Elves, with a subservient lich and a faerie of the forest walking among "
"them. This is quite the odd picture — it’s almost entertaining. You, faerie, "
"what do you have to say in defense of you and your friends?"
msgstr ""
"Elfos, con un lich sumiso y un hada del bosque entre ellos. Es una imagen "
"bastante extraña — casi entretenida. Tú, hada, ¿qué tienes que decir en "
"defensa de ti y tus amigos?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:543
msgid ""
"Perhaps we can make a deal. These seem to be difficult times for your "
"country. I can tell from your worn attire that you were involved in some "
"sort of skirmish recently. Was it against human invaders from the south? Our "
"people are well acquainted with their tactics and weapons, as they lost "
"their home to none other than those barbarians and their demon allies. "
"Perhaps there is some task we could assist you with in exchange for "
"guaranteeing us safe passage through the northern marchlands?"
msgstr ""
"Quizás podamos hacer un trato. Parece que son tiempos difíciles para su "
"país. Puedo notar por su ropa desgastada que estuvieron involucrados en "
"algún enfrentamiento reciente. ¿Fue contra invasores humanos del sur? "
"Nuestra gente conoce bien sus tácticas y armas, pues ellos perdieron su "
"hogar a manos de esos bárbaros y sus aliados demoníacos. Tal vez haya alguna "
"tarea con la que podamos ayudar a cambio de garantizar nuestro paso seguro "
"por las tierras fronterizas del norte."

#. [message]: speaker=Erathan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:552
msgid ""
"Hah! You read me well, faerie. To tell you the truth, we were sent by the "
"Grand Council of the Northern Peoples to Herthgar, to escort your leader "
"back to the Council for an audience. But it seems you came to us instead. I "
"take it that something bad happened back there. Lord Galas, right?"
msgstr ""
"¡Ja! Me conoces bien, hada. A decir verdad, fuimos enviados por el Gran "
"Consejo de los Pueblos del Norte a Herthgar, para escoltar a su líder de "
"vuelta al Consejo para una audiencia. Pero parece que vinieron a nosotros en "
"su lugar. Supongo que algo malo pasó allá atrás. Lord Galas, ¿verdad?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:557
msgid "Yes, sir. The kingdom of Herthgar has fallen to the Chaos Empire."
msgstr "Sí, señor. El reino de Herthgar ha caído ante el Imperio del Caos."

#. [message]: speaker=Erathan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:562
msgid ""
"Huh. So that’s how dire the situation is. Very well, then, elf lord — we can "
"escort you to our capital, Raelthyn, but we cannot guarantee your safety "
"right now. You see, a group of orcish mercenaries allied with these ‘Chaos’ "
"fiends set up camp north of the river. Just as we managed to cross, their "
"saurian allies arrived and seized control of the bridge. There is a mountain "
"pass we can use but... none of you seem adequately equipped for an "
"expedition like that. So, my proposal is as follows: you repel the invaders, "
"and we’ll take you to Raelthyn."
msgstr ""
"Ajá. Así que la situación es tan grave. Muy bien, entonces, señor elfo — "
"podemos escoltarlos a nuestra capital, Raelthyn, pero no podemos garantizar "
"su seguridad por ahora. Verá, un grupo de mercenarios orcos aliados con "
"estos demonios del ‘Caos’ han acampado al norte del río. Justo cuando "
"logramos cruzar, sus aliados saurios llegaron y tomaron control del puente. "
"Hay un paso montañoso que podemos usar, pero... ninguno de ustedes parece "
"estar adecuadamente equipado para una expedición así. Entonces, mi propuesta "
"es la siguiente: ustedes repelen a los invasores, y nosotros los llevaremos "
"a Raelthyn."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:567
msgid "Seems like a sound plan to me."
msgstr "Me parece un plan sensato."

#. [message]: speaker=Erathan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:572
msgid ""
"I thought so. Here, you can have our intel so you don’t get lost in this "
"region and know exactly what you are up against."
msgstr ""
"Eso pensé. Toma, puedes quedarte con nuestra información para que no te "
"pierdas en esta región y sepas exactamente contra qué te enfrentas."

#. [message]: speaker=Erathan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:619
msgid "We’ll be watching you closely."
msgstr "Los estaremos vigilando de cerca."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:652
msgid "They do not seem to trust us much, do they?"
msgstr "No parecen confiar mucho en nosotros, ¿verdad?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:657
msgid ""
"Would <i>you</i> trust people who consort with necromancers, Galas? We "
"should be thankful they didn’t decide to kill us on sight."
msgstr ""
"¿Confías <i>tú</i> en gente que se junta con nigromantes, Galas? Deberíamos "
"estar agradecidos de que no hayan decidido matarnos en cuanto nos vieron."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:662
msgid ""
"Hey, don’t be so sure of yourself, girl. He seemed to take offense at your "
"presence as well."
msgstr ""
"Oye, no te creas tanto, chica. Él también pareció ofenderse con tu presencia."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:667
msgid ""
"It sounds like forest faeries have become a more common sight in the "
"northern forests for some reason. I understand that these humans might not "
"trust them, but... we might be able to enlist their help somehow."
msgstr ""
"Parece que por alguna razón los duendecillos del bosque se han vuelto una "
"vista más común en los bosques del norte. Entiendo que estos humanos quizás "
"no confíen en ellos, pero... podríamos lograr que nos ayuden de alguna forma."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:678
msgid ""
"It’s interesting that he did not pay any attention to our goblin friend."
msgstr "Es curioso que no haya prestado atención a nuestro amigo goblin."

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:683
msgid "I feared for my life for a moment there... <i>phew</i>."
msgstr "Temí por mi vida por un momento... <i>uf</i>."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:690
msgid ""
"Well, now... This mission will be pleasant to accomplish — for me at least."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, ahora... Esta misión será agradable de cumplir — para mí al menos."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:695
msgid "What are those creatures he mentioned, the ‘saurians’?"
msgstr "¿Qué son esas criaturas que mencionó, los ‘saurios’?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:700
msgid ""
"Treacherous scaled pests that frolic in swampy waters and impale you with "
"their rusty spears from beneath the surface. They rarely pose a threat on "
"their own, until they swarm you in numbers."
msgstr ""
"Esas son plagas traicioneras cubiertas de escamas que retozan en aguas "
"pantanosas y te empalan con sus lanzas oxidadas desde debajo de la "
"superficie. Rara vez representan una amenaza por sí solas, hasta que te "
"atacan en manada."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:705
msgid "Well, let’s be about it, then."
msgstr "Bueno, pongámonos manos a la obra, entonces."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:711
msgid ""
"Elynia’s affinity with the faerie realm allows you to control forest "
"sprites. They have both a melee and a ranged attack which inflict fire "
"damage to foes. The drawback, however, is that they are very fragile "
"creatures and can be easily slain by enemies in a one-on-one fight; "
"furthermore, they are costlier to recruit than most other units. Never send "
"them against your adversaries without protection!"
msgstr ""
"La afinidad de Elynia con el reino feérico te permite controlar duendecillos "
"del bosque. Tienen ataque cuerpo a cuerpo y a distancia que infligen daño de "
"fuego a los enemigos. Sin embargo, son criaturas muy frágiles y pueden ser "
"fácilmente derrotados en un duelo uno a uno; además, su reclutamiento es más "
"costoso que el de la mayoría de las unidades. ¡Nunca los envíes contra tus "
"adversarios sin protección!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:748
msgid "We did it. Now what?"
msgstr "Lo hicimos. ¿Ahora qué?"

#. [message]: role=doubtful_elf
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:753
msgid ""
"That was not too difficult. But why make us do the dirty work for them, I "
"wonder? They could have sent a real escort to Herthgar rather than those "
"three individuals alone. It’s the sensible thing to do."
msgstr ""
"No fue tan difícil. Pero, ¿por qué hacernos a nosotros el trabajo sucio? Me "
"pregunto. Podrían haber enviado una escolta de verdad a Herthgar en vez de "
"esos tres individuos solos. Es lo sensato."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:758
msgid ""
"I assume their military is preoccupied dealing with the Chaos Empire’s "
"forces elsewhere."
msgstr ""
"Supongo que su ejército está ocupado enfrentando a las fuerzas del Imperio "
"del Caos en otra parte."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:764
msgid ""
"That was not too difficult. But why did they set things up so we’d have to "
"do the dirty work for them, I wonder? They could have sent a real escort to "
"Herthgar rather than those three individuals alone. Perhaps their military "
"is preoccupied dealing with the Chaos Empire’s forces elsewhere."
msgstr ""
"No fue tan difícil. Pero, ¿por qué arreglaron las cosas para que nosotros "
"tengamos que hacerles el trabajo sucio? Me pregunto. Podrían haber enviado "
"una escolta de verdad a Herthgar en vez de esos tres individuos solos. "
"Quizás su ejército esté ocupado enfrentando a las fuerzas del Imperio del "
"Caos en otra parte."

#. [message]: speaker=Erathan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:806
msgid ""
"I must admit, I’m pleasantly surprised by your performance in battle, lord "
"Galas. Very well, then, let us proceed to Raelthyn."
msgstr ""
"Debo admitir que estoy gratamente sorprendido por tu desempeño en batalla, "
"lord Galas. Muy bien, entonces, procedamos a Raelthyn."

#. [message]: speaker=Erathan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:824
msgid ""
"Zednal? Just for safety, I want you to keep an eye on the forest faeries, "
"especially the lavender-haired one. The last thing we want is creatures like "
"her flirting with our men in the capital."
msgstr ""
"¿Zednal? Por precaución, quiero que vigiles a los duendecillos del bosque, "
"especialmente a la de cabello lavanda. Lo último que queremos es que "
"criaturas como ella coqueteen con nuestros hombres en la capital."

#. [message]: speaker=Erathan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:830
msgid ""
"Zednal? Just for safety, I want you to keep an eye on that lavender-haired "
"forest faerie. The last thing we want is creatures like her flirting with "
"our men in the capital."
msgstr ""
"¿Zednal? Por precaución, quiero que vigiles a esa duendecilla del bosque de "
"cabello lavanda. Lo último que queremos es que criaturas como ella coqueteen "
"con nuestros hombres en la capital."

#. [message]: speaker=Zednal
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:837
msgid "Yes, as you command, sir."
msgstr "Sí, como ordene, señor."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:842
msgid "You heard that?"
msgstr "¿Oíste eso?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:847
msgid "Yes. (</i>sighs<i>) Oh well, their love problems are not our business."
msgstr ""
"Sí. (</i>suspira<i>) Bueno, sus problemas amorosos no son asunto nuestro."

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:865
msgid ""
"What the hell? Are those elves? And undead at their command? This is most "
"unusual!"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué demonios? ¿Esos son elfos? ¿Y muertos vivientes a su mando? ¡Esto es "
"muy inusual!"

#. [message]: speaker=Arghalon
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:870
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The lich wants to see their leader’s head on a stake! Go get them, you "
"useless scum!"
msgstr ""
"¡El lich quiere ver la cabeza de nuestro líder en una pica! ¡Vayan por "
"ellos, escoria inútil!"

#. [message]: speaker=Grilock
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:875
msgid "Already working on it, boss!"
msgstr "¡Ya estoy en eso, jefe!"

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:890
msgid "This feels so wrong..."
msgstr "Esto se siente tan mal..."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:904
msgid "Gaaargh... How could this happen to me!"
msgstr "¡Gaaaargh...! ¡¿Cómo pudo pasarme esto?!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:916
msgid ""
"You wose-born fiends may take me down, but at the end of the day, the Chaos "
"Empire will prevail! It’s not too late for your people yet... join them and "
"perhaps they’ll spare your miserable lives!"
msgstr ""
"¡Malditos demonios de sangre podrida, pueden acabar conmigo, pero al final, "
"el Imperio del Caos prevalecerá! Aún no es tarde para tu gente... únete a "
"ellos y quizás perdonen sus miserables vidas."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:921
msgid ""
"Hah! Is this why you and your people chose to serve them? It’s appalling "
"that orcs would rather surrender to a band of bloodthirsty humans than fight "
"back. What has the world come to?"
msgstr ""
"¡Ja! ¿Por eso tú y tu gente eligieron servirles? Es indignante que los orcos "
"prefieran rendirse ante una banda de humanos sedientos de sangre en lugar de "
"luchar. ¿En qué se ha convertido el mundo?"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:926
msgid ""
"You... clearly haven’t seen the full extent of their power. The followers of "
"Uria... they are not a threat to be taken lightly, elf. You’ll rue the day "
"you decided to cross them."
msgstr ""
"Tú... claramente no has visto todo su poder. Los seguidores de Uria... no "
"son una amenaza para tomar a la ligera, elfo. Lamentarás el día que "
"decidiste enfrentarlos."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:949
msgid ""
"Danger: Abandoned bridge!\n"
"\n"
"Use at your own peril!"
msgstr ""
"¡Peligro: Puente abandonado!\n"
"\n"
"¡Úsalo bajo tu propio riesgo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:971
msgid ""
"Awww, look it’s a bunny! It’s nice to see that these cute little fur balls "
"still exist."
msgstr ""
"¡Awww, mira, es un conejito! Es agradable ver que estas pequeñas bolas de "
"pelo tan adorables aún existen."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:986
msgid ""
"Why would you ask me to murder such an adorable creature! Have someone else "
"do it."
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué me pedirías que mate a una criatura tan adorable? Que alguien más "
"lo haga."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:1016
msgid "What... Why? What possessed me to do such a horrible thing?"
msgstr "¿Qué... por qué? ¿Qué me poseyó para hacer algo tan horrible?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:1022
msgid "That was surprisingly cruel of you, Elynia. (<i>snickers</i>)"
msgstr "Eso fue sorprendentemente cruel de tu parte, Elynia. (<i>risitas</i>)"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:1037
msgid "Blargh, get that thing out of my sight!"
msgstr "¡Blargh, quita esa cosa de mi vista!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:1052
msgid "Yes! YES!"
msgstr "¡Sí! ¡SÍ!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/14_Clearing_the_Road.cfg:1058
msgid "You are such a disgusting creature, Malin Keshar."
msgstr "Eres una criatura tan repugnante, Malin Keshar."

