msgid "Redbart"
msgstr "Redbart"

#. [unit]: type=Dwarvish Berserker, id=Turin
#. [unit]: id=Zombie Turin, type=Soulless
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:595
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:1284
msgid "Turin"
msgstr "Turin"

#. [event]: id=Galas}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:640
msgid "Move Galas, Elynia, or Mal Keshar into the dark keep"
msgstr "Mueve a Galas, Elynia o Mal Keshar dentro del bastión oscuro"

#. [event]: id=Galas}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:656
msgid ""
"Distract the enemy while Galas, Elynia, or Mal Keshar enter the dark keep"
msgstr ""
"Distráe al enemigo mientras Galas, Elynia o Mal Keshar entran al bastión "
"oscuro"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:672
msgid "There it is, the Heart of the Chaos Empire."
msgstr "Ahí está, el Corazón del Imperio del Caos."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:677
msgid ""
"I figured the rumors weren’t too far from the truth, but this is ridiculous. "
"How can these people afford such a ludicrous construction in the middle of "
"the desert? Perhaps they only ever enlisted Uria’s demons in the first place "
"as cheap work force..."
msgstr ""
"Me imaginaba que los rumores no estaban muy lejos de la verdad, pero esto es "
"ridículo. ¿Cómo pudieron costear una construcción tan absurda en medio del "
"desierto? Quizá siempre reclutaron a los demonios de Uria en primer lugar "
"como mano de obra barata…"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:682
msgid ""
"The dwarven scouts report that another large battalion departed for the "
"northwest just a few hours ago. So... I believe the time has come."
msgstr ""
"Los exploradores enanos informan que otro gran batallón partió hacia el "
"noroeste hace apenas unas horas. Así que… creo que ha llegado el momento."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:687
msgid ""
"Looking at it in hindsight, there really was no way our infiltration mission "
"wouldn’t turn into a full-fledged assault on the enemy capital. Perhaps it’s "
"better this way, after all. Now, Galas, will you do the honors?"
msgstr ""
"Viéndolo en retrospectiva, realmente no había manera de que nuestra misión "
"de infiltración no se convirtiera en un asalto total a la capital enemiga. "
"Quizá sea mejor así, después de todo. Ahora, Galas, ¿harás los honores?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:692
msgid "Eh..."
msgstr "Eh…"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:697
msgid ""
"You know, ask us whether we are ready and then give us an overly dramatic "
"discourse about the importance of this battle for the future of Irdya. It’s "
"the kind of thing a good leader is expected to do."
msgstr ""
"Ya sabes, pregúntanos si estamos listos y luego suelta un discurso "
"excesivamente dramático sobre la importancia de esta batalla para el futuro "
"de Irdya. Es el tipo de cosas que se espera de un buen líder."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:702
msgid "Right. Are we all ready for the battle ahead?"
msgstr "Bien. ¿Estamos todos listos para la batalla que nos espera?"

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:707
msgid "Yes! I’m ready, master Galas!"
msgstr "¡Sí! ¡Estoy listo, maestro Galas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Erathan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:712
msgid "My bow obediently awaits your orders, Lord Galas."
msgstr "Mi arco espera obediente sus órdenes, Lord Galas."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:717
msgid "Let’s get this over with!"
msgstr "¡Terminemos con esto!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:722
msgid "(<i>nods</i>)"
msgstr "(<i>asiente</i>)"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:727
msgid "Then the battle for Irdya begins now. <b>Charge!!!</b>"
msgstr "Entonces la batalla por Irdya comienza ahora. <b>¡A la carga!</b>"

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:732
msgid "Wait, and what about the dramatic discourse the lady mentioned?"
msgstr "Espera, ¿y qué hay del discurso dramático que mencionó la dama?"

#. [message]: speaker=Althurin
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:737
msgid ""
"It appears Lord Galas has just given the order, lads. Ye know what to do! "
"Don’t hold back! Kill every single one of these fiends! Avenge our fallen "
"brethren! For the King! For Herthgar! <b>Charge!!!</b>"
msgstr ""
"Parece que Lord Galas acaba de dar la orden, muchachos. ¡Ya saben lo que "
"deben hacer! ¡No se contengan! ¡Maten a cada uno de estos demonios! ¡Venguen "
"a nuestros hermanos caídos! ¡Por el Rey! ¡Por Herthgar! <b>¡A la carga!</b>"

#. [message]: speaker=Ilrymaea
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:747
msgid "The elf lord and his consorts approach from the northeast, sir!"
msgstr "¡El señor élfico y sus consortes se aproximan desde el noreste, señor!"

#. [message]: speaker=Limzer
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:752
msgid "Dwarves! Dwarves on the northwestern hills! We are under attack!"
msgstr "¡Enanos! ¡Enanos en las colinas del noroeste! ¡Estamos bajo ataque!"

#. [message]: speaker=General Erval
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:757
msgid ""
"Oh, ha ha! Are they truly this naïve? Do they believe we were not prepared "
"for this contingency? Prepare for battle! Crush all these vermin to the "
"ground! For Yechnagoth! For the glory of Uria and the Chaos Empire!"
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, ja ja! ¿De verdad son tan ingenuos? ¿Creen que no estábamos preparados "
"para esta contingencia? ¡Prepárense para la batalla! ¡Aplasten a todas estas "
"alimañas contra el sueldo! ¡Por Yechnagoth! ¡Por la gloria de Uria y el "
"Imperio del Caos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:770
msgid ""
"(<i>bitterly</i>) And so my time has come again to serve as the elves’ "
"living weapon. Even if I can hardly stand this much death and destruction..."
msgstr ""
"(<i>con amargura</i>) Y así ha llegado de nuevo mi momento de servir como el "
"arma viviente de los elfos. Aunque apenas puedo soportar tanta muerte y "
"destrucción…"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:775
msgid "I hope you can forgive me for bringing you here."
msgstr "Espero que puedas perdonarme por traerte aquí."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:780
msgid ""
"Oh, Galas, don’t fret about it — by now this almost feels like daily "
"routine. Besides, I told you before, I would have come on my own anyway."
msgstr ""
"Oh, Galas, no te preocupes por eso; a estas alturas esto casi parece una "
"rutina diaria. Además, ya te lo dije antes, habría venido por mi cuenta de "
"todos modos."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:795
msgid "<b>For Herthgar!!!</b>"
msgstr "<b>¡Por Herthgar!</b>"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:810
msgid "For Lord Lédinor and our fallen comrades!"
msgstr "¡Por Lord Lédinor y nuestros camaradas caídos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:822
msgid ""
"He, he, he, he... It’s about time this place got a do-over befitting of gods "
"who relish in death and destruction, don’t you think?"
msgstr ""
"He, he, he, he… Ya era hora de que este lugar recibiera un buen repaso digno "
"de dioses que se deleitan en la muerte y la destrucción, ¿no te parece?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:834
msgid "For Anlindë!"
msgstr "¡Por Anlindë!"

#. [message]: speaker=General Erval
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:843
msgid "Let us show these non-believers the real might of the Empire!"
msgstr "¡Mostremos a estos incrédulos el verdadero poder del Imperio!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:848
msgid "Galas, enemy troops are coming from behind!"
msgstr "¡Galas, tropas enemigas vienen por detrás!"

#. [unit]: type=Demon Warrior, id=Umlayla, gender=female
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:877
msgid "Umlayla"
msgstr "Umlayla"

#. [unit]: type=Chaos Magus, id=Ellerian
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:917
msgid "Ellerian"
msgstr "Ellerian"

#. [unit]: type=Chaos Lorekeeper, id=Mal Cyriath
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:932
msgid "Mal Cyriath"
msgstr "Mal Cyriath"

#. [message]: speaker=Umlayla
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:951
msgid "Surprise, Irdyan maggots!"
msgstr "¡Sorpresa, gusanos irdyanos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Althurin
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:965
msgid ""
"Brace yourselves, boys! The Long Dark is upon our heels and ready to liven "
"up this hell of a battle!"
msgstr ""
"¡Prepárense, muchachos! ¡La Gran Oscuridad nos pisa los talones y está lista "
"para animar esta condenada batalla!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:974
msgid ""
"Even though it’s taking us much longer than expected, the Chaos Emperor has "
"yet to make an appearance. What if our information is incorrect and he is "
"not even in the capital?"
msgstr ""
"Aunque nos está llevando mucho más tiempo de lo esperado, el Emperador del "
"Caos aún no ha hecho acto de presencia. ¿Y si nuestra información es "
"incorrecta y ni siquiera está en la capital?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:979
msgid ""
"Nah, he’s probably in his chamber running in circles and flailing his arms "
"like a lunatic while begging the goddesses for forgiveness! (<i>cackles</i>) "
"He knows we’ve won this fight."
msgstr ""
"Bah, probablemente está en su cámara corriendo en círculos y agitando los "
"brazos como un lunático mientras suplica perdón a las diosas. (<i>carcajea</"
"i>) Sabe que ya hemos ganado esta batalla."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:984
msgid ""
"Hm, yes. He is most certainly down there. He... and something else whose "
"nature I cannot ascertain yet. Mal Keshar, you can feel it too, right?"
msgstr ""
"Hm, sí. Con toda certeza está allá abajo. Él… y algo más cuya naturaleza aún "
"no puedo determinar. Mal Keshar, tú también lo sientes, ¿verdad?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:989
msgid ""
"I try not to worry too much about these things, girl. Besides, what power "
"could possibly stop two walking legends like us?"
msgstr ""
"Procuro no preocuparme demasiado por esas cosas, muchacha. Además, ¿qué "
"poder podría detener a dos leyendas vivientes como nosotros?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:1007
msgid ""
"Do you see how this dark fortress crumbles down already? Tell your goddess "
"that <b>this</b> is the fate that awaits those who dare cross the peoples of "
"Irdya!"
msgstr ""
"¿Ves cómo esta oscura fortaleza ya se desmorona? ¡Dile a tu diosa que "
"<b>este</b> es el destino que aguarda a quienes se atreven a desafiar a los "
"pueblos de Irdya!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:1025
msgid ""
"If you meet your demon gods on the other side, tell them I will not stop "
"until I have erased the very last trace of their influence on Irdya! Begone, "
"filth!"
msgstr ""
"¡Si te encuentras con tus dioses demoníacos al otro lado, diles que no me "
"detendré hasta borrar el último rastro de su influencia en Irdya! "
"¡Desaparece, escoria!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:1043
msgid "We’ve failed the Master... How can this be... No... no!"
msgstr "Hemos fallado al Amo… ¿Cómo puede ser esto…? ¡No… no!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:1048
msgid "Yes, <b>yes</b>, <b>YES! AhahahahahahahaHAHAHAHAHA!!!</b>"
msgstr "¡Sí, <b>sí</b>, <b>¡SÍ! ¡AhahahahahahahaHAHAHAHAHA!</b>"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:1255
msgid "RIP-N’ TEAAAAAAR!!!"
msgstr "¡DESGARRAR Y DESTROZAAAR!!!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:1269
msgid "At long last... ah’ meet me doom..."
msgstr "Por fin... encuentro mi destino..."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:1325
msgid "Quickly! We have no time to waste."
msgstr "¡Rápido! No tenemos tiempo que perder."

#. [message]: speaker=Althurin
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:1369
msgid ""
"Alas, if Galas and the Lady are to succeed in their mission we must stay "
"here and fend off the enemy reinforcements. I can’t help but wonder what "
"kind of foe awaits that courageous bunch in there..."
msgstr ""
"En fin, si Galas y la Dama quieren tener éxito en su misión, debemos "
"quedarnos aquí y repeler a los refuerzos enemigos. No puedo evitar "
"preguntarme qué clase de enemigo aguarda a ese valiente grupo allá dentro…"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/20_The_Heart.cfg:1380
msgid ""
"This is hopeless, Galas. We took too long, and now enemy reinforcements are "
"approaching from all directions!"
msgstr ""
"Esto es inútil, Galas. Nos hemos demorado demasiado, y ahora los refuerzos "
"enemigos se acercan desde todas direcciones."

#. [side]: type=Armageddon Imp, id=Cragworg
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:65
msgid "Cragworg"
msgstr "Cragworg"

#. [unit]: type=Demon Grunt, id=Aelyriun-Balal, gender=female
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:91
msgid "Aelyriun-Balal"
msgstr "Aelyriun-Balal"

#. [side]: type=Ancient Lich, id=Mal Vritra, gender=female
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:120
msgid "Mal Vritra"
msgstr "Mal Vritra"

#. [side]: type=Shaxthal Sentry Drone, id=Nemaara
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:178
msgid "Nemaara"
msgstr "Nemaara"

#. [side]: type=Chaos Arbalestier, id=Ra'aldir
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:250
msgid "Ra’aldir"
msgstr "Ra’aldir"

#. [unit]: type=Lich, id=Mal Abbadur
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:282
msgid "Mal Abbadur"
msgstr "Mal Abbadur"

#. [scenario]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:417
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:418
msgid "Dungeon"
msgstr "Mazmorra"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:587
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:318
msgid ""
"Explore and descend deeper underground with Galas, Elynia, or Mal Keshar"
msgstr ""
"Explora y desciende más profundamente bajo tierra con Galas, Elynia o Mal "
"Keshar"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:597
msgid ""
"In this scenario, you may only recall or recruit units during the first "
"turn, in your starting area"
msgstr ""
"En este escenario, solo puedes rememorar o reclutar unidades durante el "
"primer turno, en tu área inicial."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:599
msgid ""
"Only those units you recall or recruit during the first turn will be "
"available for the remainder of the campaign"
msgstr ""
"Solo las unidades que rememores o reclutes en el primer turno estarán "
"disponibles para el resto de la campaña."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:643
msgid ""
"A presence... A strong, dark presence fills this whole place, as if the "
"floor and walls had a life of their own. I don’t like this."
msgstr ""
"Una presencia… Una presencia oscura y poderosa llena todo este lugar, como "
"si el suelo y las paredes tuvieran vida propia. No me gusta esto."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:646
msgid "Thus you dare enter my stronghold. You truly are a foolish hero, Galas."
msgstr ""
"Así que te atreves a entrar en mi fortaleza. Realmente eres un héroe necio, "
"Galas."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:650
msgid "... It’s that voice again."
msgstr "... Es esa voz otra vez."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:655
msgid ""
"Reveal yourself, coward who hides in the darkness! We have come here to put "
"an end to your reign of chaos and suffering!"
msgstr ""
"¡Muéstrate, cobarde que se oculta en las sombras! ¡Hemos venido para poner "
"fin a tu reinado de caos y sufrimiento!"

#. [message]: speaker=Erathan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:666
msgid "That metallic laughter sure sounded real to me."
msgstr "Esa risa metálica me ha parecido muy real."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:671
msgid ""
"He seems to want us to move forward, so let us be on the look out for traps. "
"And... we need to find a way to open this gate."
msgstr ""
"Parece que quiere que sigamos avanzando, así que estemos atentos a las "
"trampas. Y… debemos encontrar la forma de abrir esta puerta."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:676
msgid ""
"Oh, please, courtesy is wasted in a place like this. Just blast them down or "
"something."
msgstr ""
"Oh, por favor, la cortesía es un desperdicio en un lugar como este. Solo "
"derríbalos o algo así."

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:737
msgid ""
"Drop your weapons this instant, elf, and the Master may yet show you and "
"your friends mercy!"
msgstr ""
"¡Deja caer tus armas ahora mismo, elfo, y el Amo quizá aún tenga piedad de "
"ti y tus amigos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:742
msgid "Never! Onwards, everyone!"
msgstr "¡Nunca! ¡Adelante, todos!"

#. [transient_message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:746
msgid ""
"Choose your recruits and recalls carefully. They will not require upkeep, "
"but you should try to keep them alive for as long as possible; no other "
"units will be available to you for the remainder of the campaign."
msgstr ""
"Elige con cuidado a tus reclutas y rememorados. No requerirán mantenimiento, "
"pero deberías intentar mantenerlos con vida el mayor tiempo posible; no "
"tendrás otras unidades disponibles para el resto de la campaña."

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:818
msgid ""
"The crate is full of metal parts. I guess they are meant for some kind of "
"machine."
msgstr ""
"La caja está llena de piezas metálicas. Supongo que son para algún tipo de "
"máquina."

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:835
msgid "Books? What business do these fiends have reading <i>books</i>?"
msgstr "¿Libros? ¿Qué demonios hacen estas criaturas leyendo <i>libros</i>?"

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:852
msgid "It’s an empty crate."
msgstr "Es una caja vacía."

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:869
msgid "It’s full of bread. Very stale bread."
msgstr "Está llena de pan. Pan muy duro."

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:886
msgid "It’s an empty barrel."
msgstr "Es un barril vacío."

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:903
msgid ""
"Oh gods... It’s full of fish! Argh! But we are in the middle of a desert, so "
"where did they get them from?"
msgstr ""
"Oh, dioses… ¡Está lleno de pescado! ¡Argh! Pero estamos en medio de un "
"desierto, ¿de dónde los sacaron?"

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:920
msgid "There seems to be nothing but coal in here."
msgstr "Parece que no hay nada aquí aparte de carbón."

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:937
msgid ""
"It gives off such a foul smell I don’t think I want to see the contents. "
"Let’s leave it alone, shall we?"
msgstr ""
"Desprende un hedor tan repugnante que no creo querer ver su contenido. "
"Dejémoslo como está, ¿de acuerdo?"

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:954
msgid "... Eyes. It’s full of eyes."
msgstr "... Ojos. Está lleno de ojos."

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:971
msgid ""
"Hmph, why would anyone craft armor out of pure gold? Everyone knows it’s one "
"of the softest materials on Irdya. These ostentatious fiends..."
msgstr ""
"Hmph, ¿por qué alguien fabricaría armaduras de oro puro? Todo el mundo sabe "
"que es uno de los materiales más blandos de Irdya. Estos ostentosos demonios…"

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1009
msgid "Yep, nothing to see here."
msgstr "Sip, aquí no hay nada que ver."

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1042
msgid ""
"It’s not like we will need the gold any time soon, but there is nothing "
"wrong with a little plundering, right?"
msgstr ""
"No es que vayamos a necesitar el oro pronto, pero no hay nada de malo en un "
"poco de saqueo, ¿verdad?"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1065
msgid "Invisibility Tonic"
msgstr "Tónico de Invisibilidad"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1066
msgid ""
" • 1× clipped faerie wing\n"
" • 1× eye of blood bat\n"
" • 2× sprig of alvorian shade flower\n"
" • 1× lancespade powder\n"
" • 3× blue moon wisps\n"
"\n"
"Combine faerie wings with blood bat eye. Mix well and boil in iron cauldron "
"for two hours. Add rest of ingredients, stirring. Makes 5 beakers of "
"invisibility tonic."
msgstr ""
" • 1× ala de hada recortada\n"
" • 1× ojo de murciélago de sangre\n"
" • 2× ramitas de flor de sombra alvoriana\n"
" • 1× polvo de lanzapica\n"
" • 3× brumas de luna azul\n"
"\n"
"Combina las alas de hada con el ojo de murciélago de sangre. Mezcla bien y "
"hierve en un caldero de hierro durante dos horas. Añade el resto de los "
"ingredientes, removiendo. Rinde 5 frascos de tónico de invisibilidad."

#. [unit]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1220
msgid "Rurhló"
msgstr "Rurhló"

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1226
msgid "Graurgh... Argh gaaaaa... (<i>roars</i>)"
msgstr "Graurgh… ¡Argh gaaaaa…! (<i>ruge</i>)"

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1232
msgid "It’s hostile! Kill it!"
msgstr "¡Es hostil! ¡Mátalo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1250
msgid "Lord Lédinor! Is that really you? What have these beasts done to you?!"
msgstr "¡Lord Lédinor! ¿Realmente eres tú? ¡¿Qué te han hecho estas bestias?!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1261
msgid ""
"He seems extremely unwell — no doubt he has been constantly tortured by his "
"captors during all this time. I will have to treat him before he’ll be able "
"to stand on his own again."
msgstr ""
"Parece estar extremadamente mal — sin duda lo han torturado sin cesar sus "
"captores durante todo este tiempo. Tendré que tratarlo antes de que pueda "
"volver a sostenerse por sí mismo."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1266
msgid "If only we could take him back outside... Damn it!"
msgstr "Si tan solo pudiéramos llevarlo de vuelta afuera… ¡Maldita sea!"

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1380
msgid "Oh, just... great."
msgstr "Oh, esto es… genial."

#. [message]: speaker=Ra'aldir
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1385
msgid "Seize the Lady of Light and kill the intruders!"
msgstr "¡Capturen a la Dama de la Luz y maten a los intrusos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Ra'aldir
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1401
msgid "You... you will not succeed... You can’t kill... the Emperor..."
msgstr "Ustedes… no lo lograrán… No pueden matar… al Emperador…"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1413
msgid "I don’t suspect anyone has actually tried before."
msgstr "No creo que nadie lo haya intentado antes."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1432
msgid "Touchgem triggered. A gate opens."
msgstr "Piedra de toque activada. Una puerta se abre."

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1454
msgid "Ah, that ought to do the trick."
msgstr "Ah, eso debería bastar."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1460
msgid "Onwards!"
msgstr "¡Adelante!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Vritra
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1535
msgid ""
"Ah, every story has to come to an end someday... even yours, Lady of Light..."
msgstr ""
"Ah, toda historia debe llegar a su fin algún día… incluso la tuya, Dama de "
"la Luz…"

#. [message]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1570
msgid "Oh no... Uria be damned!"
msgstr "Oh no… ¡Maldita sea Uria!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1596
msgid "Not this again..."
msgstr "No otra vez…"

#. [message]: speaker=Cragworg
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1601
msgid ""
"Your foolishness ends here with your death, enemies of Uria! Her Voice "
"requests that we prevent your advance towards the Gate of Inferno at all "
"costs!"
msgstr ""
"¡Su necedad termina aquí con su muerte, enemigos de Uria! Su Voz exige que "
"impidamos su avance hacia la Puerta del Infierno a toda costa."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1606
msgid ""
"You mean the Chaos Emperor, right? I can’t believe your kind lets a lesser "
"monster like him order you around like dogs."
msgstr ""
"¿Te refieres al Emperador del Caos, verdad? No puedo creer que los de tu "
"clase dejen que un monstruo menor como él los mande como a perros."

#. [message]: speaker=Aelyriun-Balal
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1611
msgid ""
"Don’t you dare speak ill of the Voice of Uria, elf scum! Cragworg, crush "
"these disgusting vermin!"
msgstr ""
"¡No te atrevas a hablar mal de la Voz de Uria, escoria élfica! ¡Cragworg, "
"aplasta a estas asquerosas alimañas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Aelyriun-Balal
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1626
msgid "Not the Lady of Light, you worthless idiot!"
msgstr "¡No a la Dama de la Luz, idiota inútil!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1641
msgid ""
"Is this our curse? To fight countless big shot enemies with death wishes?"
msgstr ""
"¿Es esta nuestra maldición? ¿Pelear contra interminables enemigos "
"importantes con deseos de morir?"

#. [message]: speaker=Aelyriun-Balal
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1653
msgid "Oh, Uria, I... have... failed..."
msgstr "Oh, Uria… yo… he… fallado…"

#. [message]: speaker=Cragworg
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1669
msgid ""
"(<i>spits blood</i>) You have not seen the last of me! I am not... dying... "
"today... (<i>collapses</i>)"
msgstr ""
"(<i>escupe sangre</i>) ¡No han visto lo último de mí! No… voy a… morir… hoy… "
"(<i>se desploma</i>)"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1684
msgid ""
"Ugh. Hopefully that’s the last time we will need to fight one of these "
"drooling imps. Now, where do we go from here?"
msgstr ""
"Ugh. Espero que sea la última vez que tengamos que pelear contra uno de "
"estos demonios babeantes. Ahora, ¿hacia dónde vamos desde aquí?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1689
msgid ""
"They seemed determined not just to prevent our progress towards the ‘Gate’, "
"but also to impede our access to the dungeon on this level. May I suggest we "
"investigate and possibly release any prisoners kept captive?"
msgstr ""
"Parecían decididos no solo a impedir nuestro avance hacia la ‘Puerta’, sino "
"también a obstaculizar nuestro acceso a la mazmorra en este nivel. ¿Puedo "
"sugerir que investiguemos y quizás liberemos a cualquier prisionero cautivo?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1694
msgid "Yes, sounds good to me."
msgstr "Sí, me parece bien."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1715
msgid "I think I just heard a voice calling for help."
msgstr "Creo que acabo de oír una voz pidiendo ayuda."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1720
msgid ""
"Galas, do you really want us to explore the whole place? We do not have all "
"the time in the world, you know. Besides, I doubt the prisoners can be of "
"much help. <small>Not alive, at least...</small>"
msgstr ""
"Galas, ¿de verdad quieres que exploremos todo el lugar? No tenemos todo el "
"tiempo del mundo, ¿sabes? Además, dudo que los prisioneros puedan ser de "
"mucha ayuda. <small>No vivos, al menos…</small>"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1725
msgid ""
"It would be highly inhumane for us to leave them abandoned to their own luck!"
msgstr ""
"¡Sería sumamente inhumano de nuestra parte dejarlos abandonados a su suerte!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1730
msgid ""
"Very well, boy, do as you wish. I don’t really care! Should we lose precious "
"time due to your insistence on helping all living things, that shall be "
"<i>your</i> problem to deal with, not mine."
msgstr ""
"Muy bien, chico, haz lo que quieras. ¡Me da igual! Si perdemos un tiempo "
"valioso por tu insistencia en ayudar a todos los seres vivos, ese será "
"<i>tu</i> problema, no el mío."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1746
msgid ""
"I wonder if that’s all of them... It seems odd that the dungeon is almost "
"completely empty. Perhaps they saw us coming and moved all of their "
"prisoners elsewhere?"
msgstr ""
"Me pregunto si esos eran todos… Parece extraño que la mazmorra esté casi "
"completamente vacía. ¿Quizá nos vieron venir y trasladaron a todos sus "
"prisioneros a otro sitio?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1751
msgid ""
"Why would they bother? They have never seemed to be the kind who would take "
"prisoners in the first place; Lord Lédinor’s presence here is highly unusual."
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué se molestarían? Nunca han parecido ser del tipo que toma "
"prisioneros; la presencia de Lord Lédinor aquí es sumamente inusual."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1756
msgid "Yes, and that is... Hold on, I hear movement."
msgstr "Sí, y eso es… Espera, oigo movimiento."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1790
msgid "So I guess we don’t need to find a way to open that gate after all!"
msgstr ""
"¡Así que supongo que no necesitamos buscar la manera de abrir esa puerta "
"después de todo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1833
msgid ""
"And deeper underground we go. (<i>sighs</i>) Perhaps we should focus on "
"finding that ‘Gate’ and close it off somehow before confronting the Emperor. "
"Elynia, would you be able to do that?"
msgstr ""
"Y seguimos más profundo bajo tierra. (<i>suspira</i>) Quizá deberíamos "
"centrarnos en encontrar esa ‘Puerta’ y sellarla de algún modo antes de "
"enfrentar al Emperador. Elynia, ¿podrías hacer eso?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1842
msgid "... Elynia?"
msgstr "… ¿Elynia?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#. She is supposed to sound as though she's distracted with/by something else.
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1848
msgid ""
"Huh? Oh, sorry. You are asking about the portal to Inferno, right. I fear it "
"might be a much more severe fissure in our reality than I originally "
"suspected. I can’t even begin to fathom the amount of power that was "
"required to create it, let alone how to heal it."
msgstr ""
"¿Eh? Oh, lo siento. Preguntabas por el portal al Infierno, ¿verdad? Temo que "
"pueda ser una fisura mucho más grave en nuestra realidad de lo que "
"sospechaba al principio. No puedo ni empezar a imaginar la cantidad de poder "
"que se necesitó para crearla, y mucho menos cómo repararla."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1853
msgid "So, you mean..."
msgstr "Entonces, quieres decir…"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/21_Innuendo.cfg:1858
msgid "This whole city is the Gate."
msgstr "Toda esta ciudad es la Puerta."

#. [unit]: id=Urunur, type=Iron Mauler
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:91
msgid "Urunur"
msgstr "Urunur"

#. [side]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:132
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:122
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:61
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:147
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:182
msgid "team_name^Dark Hive"
msgstr "Colmena Oscura"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:338
msgid ""
"It has been a while since we last encountered an enemy other than those "
"mindless hive creatures, and the stench of decay is only getting worse. Are "
"we sure we are going in the right direction?"
msgstr ""
"Ha pasado un tiempo desde la última vez que encontramos un enemigo que no "
"fueran esas criaturas sin mente de la colmena, y el hedor a descomposición "
"no hace más que empeorar. ¿Estamos seguros de que vamos en la dirección "
"correcta?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:343
msgid ""
"Oh, we certainly are heading towards a powerful dark presence. Whether it is "
"the Chaos Emperor himself or not—"
msgstr ""
"Oh, sin duda nos dirigimos hacia una poderosa presencia oscura. Sea o no el "
"mismo Emperador del Caos—"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:348
msgid "Galas, Lord Lédinor seems to be regaining consciousness."
msgstr "Galas, parece que Lord Lédinor está recuperando la conciencia."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:357
msgid "My lord! Are you all right?"
msgstr "¡Mi señor! ¿Está bien?"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:362
msgid ""
"Oh, young Galas, that is a... silly question to ask... (<i>coughs</i>) To "
"say that I have felt better in my life would be quite an understatement. "
"But... I am alive at least. I never expected to see you here, and... I hear "
"this radiant lady is the Lady of Light, the savior of elf-kind? How can this "
"be? I... I always thought..."
msgstr ""
"Oh, joven Galas, esa es una... pregunta tonta que hacer... (<i>tos</i>) "
"Decir que me he sentido mejor en mi vida sería quedarse corto. Pero... al "
"menos sigo con vida. Nunca esperé verte aquí, y... escucho que esta radiante "
"dama es la Dama de la Luz, ¿la salvadora de la raza élfica? ¿Cómo puede ser "
"esto? Yo... siempre pensé..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:367
msgid ""
"Oh, my lord, it is a long and sorrowful story. I suppose it rests on me to "
"bring you up to speed. Do you think you will be able to walk on your own, "
"sir?"
msgstr ""
"Oh, mi señor, es una historia larga y triste. Supongo que me corresponde "
"ponerte al tanto. ¿Cree que podrá caminar por su cuenta, señor?"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:372
msgid ""
"I am old and tortured, but not useless yet. Yes, I can walk, and perhaps I "
"may still be of help."
msgstr ""
"Estoy viejo y torturado, pero aún no soy inútil. Sí, puedo caminar, y quizá "
"todavía pueda ser de ayuda."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:377
msgid "Let us get moving then."
msgstr "Entonces sigamos adelante."

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:386
msgid ""
"So that is why Anlindë is not here... Oh, Galas, would that I had foreseen "
"this. It’s not fair. I should have died in her place, making a last stand "
"against our enemies! Instead, I was captured and brought to this living hell."
msgstr ""
"Así que por eso Anlindë no está aquí... Oh, Galas, ojalá hubiera previsto "
"esto. No es justo. Yo debería haber muerto en su lugar, haciendo una última "
"resistencia contra nuestros enemigos. En cambio, fui capturado y traído a "
"este infierno viviente."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:391
msgid ""
"Why would they do this? Were any other elves captured? Did the demons want "
"anything specific from you, perhaps to make an example for the rest of our "
"people?"
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué harían esto? ¿Capturaron a otros elfos? ¿Querían los demonios algo "
"en específico de usted, quizás para dar un ejemplo al resto de nuestro "
"pueblo?"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:396
msgid ""
"Oh, I fear I was never allowed to see or be seen by any other prisoners back "
"in the Valley, my fair lady. Then I was brought here tied and blindfolded. "
"Although there certainly used to be other people in the dungeon, not a "
"single one of them sounded like one of our own. As for why they kept me "
"alive... Ugh... (<i>holds head</i>)"
msgstr ""
"Oh, temo que nunca se me permitió ver ni ser visto por otros prisioneros en "
"el Valle, mi noble señora. Luego me trajeron aquí atado y con los ojos "
"vendados. Aunque sin duda había otras personas en la mazmorra, ninguna de "
"ellas sonaba como uno de los nuestros. En cuanto a por qué me mantuvieron "
"con vida... Ugh... (<i>se lleva la mano a la cabeza</i>)"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:401
msgid ""
"These fiends, they have no compassion for any living creature, not even "
"those from their own ranks. You don’t want to hear of the atrocities they do "
"to their prisoners... I am sure you recall the stories we tell about orcs "
"mutilating their enemies and boiling them alive? Compared to the things they "
"do to you in here — the things they <i>make</i> you do — I assure you, "
"becoming an orc’s dinner... would be a far preferable fate to even "
"witnessing all this..."
msgstr ""
"Esos demonios no tienen compasión por ninguna criatura viviente, ni siquiera "
"por los de sus propias filas. No querrás oír las atrocidades que hacen a sus "
"prisioneros... Estoy seguro de que recuerdas las historias que contamos "
"sobre orcos mutilando a sus enemigos y hirviéndolos vivos. Comparado con las "
"cosas que te hacen aquí —las cosas que te <i>obligan</i> a hacer— te aseguro "
"que acabar como la cena de un orco... sería un destino mucho más preferible "
"que tan solo presenciar todo esto..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:406
msgid "I... Lord Lédinor, pardon me. I should not have asked."
msgstr "Yo... Lord Lédinor, discúlpeme. No debería haber preguntado."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:415
msgid "Galas, I need to speak to you in private for a moment."
msgstr "Galas, necesito hablar contigo en privado un momento."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:420
msgid "All right. What is it?"
msgstr "Está bien. ¿Qué pasa?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:425
msgid ""
"Lord Lédinor. While treating him, I could not help but notice... Remember I "
"told you back then about how the Emperor’s magic on you seemed to have been "
"amplified by some sort of infection?"
msgstr ""
"Lord Lédinor. Mientras lo atendía, no pude evitar notar... ¿Recuerdas que te "
"conté en aquel entonces que la magia del Emperador en ti parecía haber sido "
"amplificada por algún tipo de infección?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:430
msgid "Oh Bright Gods... Are you saying that..."
msgstr "Oh Dioses Luminosos... ¿Estás diciendo que...?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:435
msgid ""
"He was evidently subjected to all manner of torture and experimentation. I "
"cannot tell for sure what they did to him, but I do sense a similar "
"infection cursing through his veins. For now he seems fully in control of "
"his own body, but I fear he will be used by the Emperor against us... I "
"considered suggesting leaving him behind, but that also seems... I don’t "
"know what we should do. I feel you would not want to abandon your senior "
"like that either. Still, I wanted to make sure you are ready to make the "
"right decision should things go awry."
msgstr ""
"Evidentemente fue sometido a toda clase de torturas y experimentos. No puedo "
"saber con certeza qué le hicieron, pero sí percibo una infección similar "
"recorriendo sus venas. Por ahora parece tener pleno control de su cuerpo, "
"pero temo que el Emperador lo use en nuestra contra... Consideré sugerir "
"dejarlo atrás, pero eso también parece... No sé qué deberíamos hacer. Siento "
"que tú tampoco querrías abandonar a tu superior de esa manera. Aun así, "
"quería asegurarme de que estés preparado para tomar la decisión correcta si "
"las cosas salen mal."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:444
msgid ""
"I hate how you have to be the bearer of bad news in this situation. Would "
"that you could figure out a way to excise that influence off his body "
"instead."
msgstr ""
"Odio que tengas que ser la portadora de malas noticias en esta situación. "
"Ojalá pudieras encontrar una forma de extirpar esa influencia de su cuerpo "
"en su lugar."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:449
msgid ""
"After all he has gone through, us experimenting on him as well seems like "
"the cruelest of fates. The best we can hope for now is that he manages to "
"reject any attempts to control his body like you did."
msgstr ""
"Después de todo lo que ha pasado, que nosotros también experimentemos con él "
"parece el destino más cruel. Lo mejor que podemos esperar ahora es que logre "
"rechazar cualquier intento de controlar su cuerpo como tú lo hiciste."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:454
msgid ""
"I will... do what needs to be done if I have to, as much as it pains me. I "
"do not wish to speak of this matter any further. I am sure you understand."
msgstr ""
"Haré... lo que haya que hacer si es necesario, por mucho que me duela. No "
"quiero hablar más de este asunto. Estoy seguro de que lo entiendes."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#. She understands Galas's quandary much better than she lets on because she
#. came here under the assumption that Argan may have turned evil and become
#. the Chaos Emperor.
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:462
msgid "I do, Galas. I am sorry. I won’t trouble you further about this."
msgstr "Lo entiendo, Galas. Lo siento. No te molestaré más con esto."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:523
msgid "Do they seriously expect these two to prevent our advance somehow?"
msgstr ""
"¿De verdad esperan que estos dos detengan de algún modo nuestro avance?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:544
msgid "Ah, that’s much better!"
msgstr "¡Ah, eso está mucho mejor!"

#. [message]: speaker=Urunur
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:637
msgid "It’s the heathens! Keep them entertained!"
msgstr "¡Son los herejes! ¡Manténganlos entretenidos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:642
msgid "What is this now? Keep us entertained for what?"
msgstr "¿Y esto qué se supone que es? ¿Mantenernos entretenidos para qué?"

#. [message]: speaker=Erathan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:675
msgid "I suppose it’s too late to turn back now."
msgstr "Supongo que ya es demasiado tarde para volver atrás."

#. [message]: speaker=Erathan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:748
msgid "He is here!"
msgstr "¡Él está aquí!"

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:758
msgid "That’s..."
msgstr "Eso es..."

#. [message]: speaker=Erathan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:800
msgid "A woman? The warlord is actually a <i>woman</i>?"
msgstr "¿Una mujer? ¿El señor de la guerra es en realidad una <i>mujer</i>?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:805
msgid ""
"Huh? The warlord is actually a woman? Pah, not that it makes any difference."
msgstr ""
"¿Eh? ¿El señor de la guerra es en realidad una mujer? Bah, no es que eso "
"haga alguna diferencia."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:811
msgid ""
"Galas, the elf leader. You have no idea how long I’ve been waiting to meet "
"you. It’s too bad that the elven witch could not make it — she seemed too "
"infatuated with self-sacrifice for that, much like you."
msgstr ""
"Galas, el líder élfico. No tienes idea de cuánto tiempo he estado esperando "
"para conocerte. Es una lástima que la bruja élfica no pudiera venir: parecía "
"demasiado obsesionada con el autosacrificio para eso, al igual que tú."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:816
msgid ""
"So you are the monster who killed Anlindë. I shall make sure you meet your "
"due punishment, and I am <i>not</i> planning on dying tonight!"
msgstr ""
"Así que tú eres el monstruo que mató a Anlindë. Me aseguraré de que recibas "
"tu merecido castigo, ¡y <i>no</i> planeo morir esta noche!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:821
msgid ""
"Alas, lord of the elves, there is no weapon nor magical power left on this "
"ruined world able to destroy me. You will only waste the last minutes of "
"your life!"
msgstr ""
"Ay, señor de los elfos, no queda arma ni poder mágico en este mundo "
"arruinado capaz de destruirme. ¡Solo perderás los últimos minutos de tu vida!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:826
msgid ""
"No, we will prevail. No matter how many times your kind tries, you cannot "
"escape justice at our hands. You will be banished from Irdya all the same!"
msgstr ""
"No, prevaleceremos. No importa cuántas veces intente tu clase, no puedes "
"escapar de la justicia en nuestras manos. ¡Serás desterrada de Irdya de "
"todos modos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:831
msgid ""
"Ah, the formidable Lady of Light... I am truthfully disappointed to see you "
"are but a brash, ignorant creature, just like the rest. You should be taught "
"to not defy the power of Uria."
msgstr ""
"Ah, la formidable Dama de la Luz... Sinceramente me decepciona ver que no "
"eres más que una criatura temeraria e ignorante, igual que los demás. "
"Deberías aprender a no desafiar el poder de Uria."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:836
msgid ""
"You all appear to be under the misconception that your pitiful war will make "
"a difference; but to her, you are completely beneath notice. We have been "
"kept distracted by more important matters, but since you decided to come to "
"our domain in person, I suppose it falls upon me to put an end to this folly."
msgstr ""
"Todos parecen estar bajo la equivocación de que su patética guerra marcará "
"alguna diferencia; pero para ella ustedes son completamente insignificantes. "
"Hemos estado distraídos por asuntos más importantes, pero ya que decidieron "
"venir en persona a nuestro dominio, supongo que me corresponde a mí poner "
"fin a esta locura."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:842
msgid ""
"The demoness unsheathed her sword and held it to the fore, glancing at the "
"Lady of Light with murderous glee in her eyes. And just for one instant, "
"Galas could read a hint of outrage and anguish on Elynia’s face."
msgstr ""
"La demonio desenvainó su espada y la sostuvo al frente, mirando a la Dama de "
"la Luz con un brillo asesino en los ojos. Y por un instante, Galas pudo leer "
"un atisbo de indignación y angustia en el rostro de Elynia."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#. Yes, she doesn't spell out the Chaos Emperor's name or title
#. on this line, that's intentional.
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:849
msgid ""
"Although he and Uria had an interest in dealing with you personally, I fear "
"that will not be possible, my dear."
msgstr ""
"Aunque él y Uria tenían interés en ocuparse de ustedes personalmente, me "
"temo que eso no será posible, querida."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:862
msgid "No. It is time for <i>you</i> to meet your fate!"
msgstr "No. ¡Es hora de que <i>tú</i> enfrentes tu destino!"

#. [event]
#. [scenario]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:867
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1031
msgid "Elyssa, the Chaos Warlord"
msgstr "Elyssa, la Señora de la Guerra del Caos"

#. [event]
#. [scenario]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:867
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1031
msgid "Fire of Uria"
msgstr "Fuego de Uria"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:870
msgid "Defeat the Chaos Warlord"
msgstr "Derrota a la Señora de la guerra del Caos"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:932
msgid "I did warn you... You cannot destroy me."
msgstr "Te lo advertí... No puedes destruirme."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:937
msgid ""
"Galas, you know that normally I would approve of sticking around to enact "
"some form of revenge, but the harsh reality of the situation is..."
msgstr ""
"Galas, sabes que normalmente aprobaría quedarnos para cobrar venganza, pero "
"la dura realidad de la situación es..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:942
msgid "Everyone, cover your eyes!"
msgstr "¡Todos, cúbranse los ojos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:980
msgid ""
"What is this...? Do you really think such a cheap trick is going to stop "
"me!? (<i>holds her head</i>)"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué es esto...? ¿De verdad creen que un truco tan barato va a detenerme!? "
"(<i>se sujeta la cabeza</i>)"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:985
msgid ""
"She seems disoriented. Is this what we are doing now, Elynia? Fleeing from "
"the enemy like cowards?"
msgstr ""
"Parece desorientada. ¿Es esto lo que estamos haciendo ahora, Elynia? ¿Huir "
"del enemigo como cobardes?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:990
msgid ""
"We’re not fleeing from her — we are just advancing to a more tactically "
"advantageous position! Mal Keshar, take care of the enchantment shielding "
"the gate!"
msgstr ""
"¡No estamos huyendo de ella; solo avanzamos hacia una posición tácticamente "
"más ventajosa! ¡Mal Keshar, encárgate del encantamiento que protege la "
"puerta!"

#. [event]: id=boss_victory_progress_update
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:1028
msgid ""
"Destroy the exit gate using Mal Keshar before the Chaos Warlord regains her "
"sight ($boss_reactivate_turns turns remaining)"
msgstr ""
"Destruye la puerta de salida usando a Mal Keshar antes de que la Señora de "
"la Guerra del Caos recupere la vista (quedan $boss_reactivate_turns turnos)"

#. [event]: id=boss_victory_progress_update
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:1030
msgid ""
"Destroy the exit gate using Mal Keshar before the Chaos Warlord regains her "
"sight (1 turn remaining)"
msgstr ""
"Destruye la puerta de salida usando a Mal Keshar antes de que la Señora de "
"la Guerra del Caos recupere la vista (queda 1 turno)"

#. [event]: id=boss_victory_progress_update
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:1042
msgid ""
"Elyssa will be incapacitated only for a limited time ($boss_reactivate_turns "
"turns remaining)"
msgstr ""
"Elyssa estará incapacitada solo por un tiempo limitado (quedan "
"$boss_reactivate_turns turnos)"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:1083
msgid ""
"Enough! By the power you have bestowed upon me, Uria, may the spells "
"conferring life to the dead be canceled now!"
msgstr ""
"¡Basta! Por el poder que me has otorgado, Uria, ¡que los conjuros que "
"confieren vida a los muertos sean cancelados ahora!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:1088
msgid "Oh no..."
msgstr "Oh no..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:1094
msgid "Her power is too great! I... cannot..."
msgstr "¡Su poder es demasiado grande! Yo... no puedo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:1169
msgid "Time for us to leave!"
msgstr "¡Es hora de irnos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:1174
msgid ""
"What exactly do you intend to accomplish with this, Elynia? Could you at "
"least tell me what your plan is for once?"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué pretendes lograr con esto, Elynia? ¿Podrías al menos decirme cuál es tu "
"plan por una vez?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:1179
msgid ""
"Oh, you mean that as if you never did anything of the sort before? We have "
"no time to waste here, I will explain later!"
msgstr ""
"Oh, ¿lo dices como si tú nunca hubieras hecho algo así antes? ¡No tenemos "
"tiempo que perder aquí, te lo explicaré luego!"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:1183
msgid "Escape from the Chaos Warlord with Galas, Elynia, or Mal Keshar"
msgstr ""
"Escapa de la Señora de la Guerra del Caos con Galas, Elynia o Mal Keshar"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:1298
msgid "So <i>that</i> is your plan, Lady of Light. I see..."
msgstr "Así que <i>ese</i> es tu plan, Dama de la Luz. Ya veo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:1324
msgid "So will you explain your plan now?"
msgstr "¿Entonces vas a explicarnos tu plan ahora?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:1329
msgid ""
"I... am not completely sure yet if it is possible, but... even without "
"Argan’s assistance, I may be able to summon the Union again somehow, if we "
"can concentrate for a few minutes."
msgstr ""
"No... no estoy del todo segura todavía de si es posible, pero... incluso sin "
"la ayuda de Argan, tal vez pueda invocar la Unión de nuevo de algún modo, si "
"logramos concentrarnos durante unos minutos."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:1334
msgid "We? I don’t think I can..."
msgstr "¿Nosotros? No creo que yo pueda..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:1339
msgid "Not you! Malin and me."
msgstr "¡No tú! Malin y yo."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22A_Face_of_the_Enemy.cfg:1344
msgid "Wait, what?"
msgstr "Espera, ¿qué?"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:470
msgid "Proceed deeper underground with Galas, Elynia, or Mal Keshar"
msgstr "Avanza más profundo bajo tierra con Galas, Elynia o Mal Keshar"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:489
msgid ""
"Elynia, what you are saying is simply preposterous! How could I possibly "
"serve as a substitute for Argan’s powers! Unless..."
msgstr ""
"¡Elynia, lo que dices es simplemente absurdo! ¿Cómo podría yo servir como "
"sustituto de los poderes de Argan? A menos que…"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#. The ellipsis after 'darkness' is very much intentional.
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:495
msgid ""
"As we descend deeper into this fortress, we get ever closer to Inferno and "
"to the source of their power. You are one of the most powerful dark "
"sorcerers ever born from Irdya. My hope is that together we might be able to "
"channel the darkness... of the demons’ homeland. I cannot guarantee we will "
"survive the attempt, but at this point we have few alternatives left."
msgstr ""
"A medida que descendemos más profundo en esta fortaleza, nos acercamos cada "
"vez más a Inferno y a la fuente de su poder. Tú eres uno de los hechiceros "
"oscuros más poderosos que ha nacido en Irdya. Mi esperanza es que juntos "
"podamos canalizar la oscuridad... de la tierra natal de los demonios. No "
"puedo garantizar que sobrevivamos al intento, pero en este punto nos quedan "
"pocas alternativas."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:500
msgid ""
"I am not sure... if I even want to do this anymore. I am no hero! I should "
"kill you and take the prize to hell with me! Actually, I guess that’s "
"exactly where we are headed, so..."
msgstr ""
"No estoy seguro… ni siquiera sé si quiero hacer esto ya. ¡No soy un héroe! "
"¡Debería matarte y llevarme el premio conmigo al infierno! Aunque… supongo "
"que es precisamente hacia donde vamos, así que…"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:505
msgid ""
"You did many things in the past, most of them crimes against people and "
"life. But now, at the end of all things, you guided Galas and his loyal "
"followers to the depths of Irdya, awoke me from my long slumber, and fought "
"the hordes of Chaos alongside us all the while. Redeeming yourself will take "
"much more than this, but I can assure you that turning your back on us now "
"will only result in your destruction at the hands of Uria’s servants."
msgstr ""
"Hiciste muchas cosas en el pasado, la mayoría crímenes contra las personas y "
"la vida. Pero ahora, al final de todas las cosas, guiaste a Galas y a sus "
"leales seguidores hasta las profundidades de Irdya, me despertaste de mi "
"largo letargo y luchaste contra las hordas del Caos junto a nosotros todo "
"este tiempo. Redimirte llevará mucho más que esto, pero puedo asegurarte que "
"darnos la espalda ahora solo resultará en tu destrucción a manos de los "
"siervos de Uria."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:510
msgid "Would you prefer that fate over fighting a just cause one final time?"
msgstr ""
"¿Prefieres ese destino en lugar de luchar por una causa justa una última vez?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:584
msgid ""
"Pah! To the Dark Gods with you and your stupid and pretentious motivations! "
"I will help, but only because I am curious to see if I can really harness "
"this legendary power! <small>I can’t possibly refuse the offer of unlimited "
"power after all these eons...</small>"
msgstr ""
"¡Bah! ¡Que los Dioses Oscuros se lleven a ti y a tus estúpidas y "
"pretenciosas motivaciones! Ayudaré, pero solo porque tengo curiosidad de ver "
"si realmente puedo aprovechar este poder legendario. <small>No puedo "
"rechazar la oferta de poder ilimitado después de todos estos eones…</small>"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:589
msgid "(<i>smiles</i>) I knew you would listen to reason, Malin."
msgstr "(<i>sonríe</i>) Sabía que escucharías la razón, Malin."

#. [message]: speaker=Erathan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:595
msgid ""
"How can you people hand your lives to this lich on a silver platter like "
"that! It defies all logic!"
msgstr ""
"¡¿Cómo pueden entregar sus vidas a este liche en bandeja de plata así?! "
"¡Esto desafía toda lógica!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:600
msgid "Just like this mission, then?"
msgstr "¿Igual que esta misión, entonces?"

#. [message]: speaker=$tmp_speaker
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:751
msgid ""
"We should avoid those dark and windy passages. With such evil creatures "
"lurking around, we could get cornered and trapped."
msgstr ""
"Debemos evitar esos pasajes oscuros y ventosos. Con tantas criaturas "
"malignas al acecho, podríamos quedar acorralados y atrapados."

#. [scenario]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:763
msgid ""
"This dusty coffin contains the barely recognizable remains of what appears "
"to be a human noble of some sort. “Vikren the First of Wesnoth.” It says he "
"was some kind of important figure back in the old empire? Who knows what he "
"would be doing down here in this infernal complex... Wait a moment. His body "
"was placed here wearing some kind of magic ring. I sense a powerful magic "
"stirring within somehow, even an eternity after his death. Do you think we "
"should take it?"
msgstr ""
"Este polvoriento ataúd contiene los restos apenas reconocibles de lo que "
"parece ser un noble humano de algún tipo. «Vikren el Primero de Wesnoth». "
"Dice que fue una figura importante en el viejo imperio… ¿Quién sabe qué "
"estaría haciendo aquí, en este complejo infernal? Un momento… Su cuerpo fue "
"colocado aquí con una especie de anillo mágico. Siento un poder fuerte "
"agitándose dentro de él, incluso tras una eternidad después de su muerte. "
"¿Creen que deberíamos tomarlo?"

#. [scenario]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:764
msgid ""
"I have this distinct feeling that the magic in this ring would interact with "
"the undead in ways we cannot possibly predict. Let us not attempt anything "
"stupid while we are still on the run from that murderous woman, shall we?"
msgstr ""
"Tengo la sensación de que la magia de este anillo interactuaría con los no-"
"muertos de formas que no podemos predecir. No intentemos nada estúpido "
"mientras seguimos huyendo de esa mujer asesina, ¿de acuerdo?"

#. [object]: id=revenant_ring
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:779
msgid "Ring of the Revenant"
msgstr "Anillo del Regresado"

#. [dummy]: id=revenant_ring
#. [object]: id=revenant_ring
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:792
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:781
msgid ""
"Any living creature wearing this ring is granted the power to cheat death "
"once, after which the ring shall become inert for a thousand years."
msgstr ""
"Cualquier criatura viviente que lleve este anillo obtiene el poder de burlar "
"a la muerte una vez, tras lo cual el anillo quedará inerte durante mil años."

#. [dummy]: id=revenant_ring
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:791
msgid "ring of the revenant"
msgstr "anillo del regresado"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:807
msgid "Wait... does a forest spirit count as a dead or a living creature?"
msgstr ""
"Espera... ¿un espíritu del bosque cuenta como una criatura viva o muerta?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:812
msgid "Why not both? I reckon this could be be a worthwhile experiment, he he."
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué no ambas cosas? Creo que podría ser un experimento interesante, je "
"je."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:817
msgid ""
"I know not how this is possible, but the ring appears to have become firmly "
"intertwined with my existence in a way I cannot begin to comprehend. I "
"cannot remove it."
msgstr ""
"No sé cómo es posible, pero el anillo parece haberse entrelazado firmemente "
"con mi existencia de un modo que no alcanzo a comprender. No puedo "
"quitármelo."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:822
msgid "I hope this doesn’t turn out to be a grave mistake later..."
msgstr "Espero que esto no termine resultando un error fatal más adelante..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:827
msgid ""
"You did not just say “grave mistake” while stealing an object from a grave, "
"did you, Elynia?"
msgstr ""
"¿Acabas de decir «error fatal» mientras robas un objeto de una tumba, Elynia?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:842
msgid ""
"Did we just give the ring to one of Mal Keshar’s pets? Seriously? Do you "
"have any idea of the historical importance of this ring?"
msgstr ""
"¿Le acabamos de dar el anillo a una de las mascotas de Mal Keshar? ¿En "
"serio? ¿Tienes idea de la importancia histórica de este anillo?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:847
msgid ""
"Pah, it’s not like anyone else has a need for it right now. Why is it such a "
"big deal?"
msgstr ""
"Bah, no es como si alguien más lo necesitara ahora mismo. ¿Por qué tanto "
"alboroto?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:854
msgid ""
"Vikren of Wesnoth... I cannot seem to remember the details anymore, but I "
"was once sent by... somebody... to find this man in Parthyn, a border "
"stronghold. I was to convince him to start a revolt among the countryside’s "
"populace and put an end to the anarchy that fractured the kingdom of "
"Wesnoth. In time and with Argan’s help, we would take Weldyn back and found "
"the Second Wesnothian Empire."
msgstr ""
"Vikren de Wesnoth... No logro recordar los detalles, pero una vez fui "
"enviada por... alguien... para encontrar a este hombre en Parthyn, una "
"fortaleza fronteriza. Debía convencerlo de iniciar una revuelta entre la "
"población rural y poner fin a la anarquía que había fracturado el reino de "
"Wesnoth. Con el tiempo, y con la ayuda de Argan, recuperaríamos Weldyn y "
"fundaríamos el Segundo Imperio Wesnothiano."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:859
msgid ""
"Hold on a moment, are you saying that <i>this</i> guy was from my hometown "
"all along? What?? And <b>he</b> was responsible for that superfluous ball of "
"fire circling Irdya alongside our original sun?"
msgstr ""
"Un momento, ¿estás diciendo que <i>este</i> tipo era de mi ciudad natal todo "
"este tiempo? ¿¡Qué!? ¿Y <b>él</b> fue responsable de esa bola de fuego "
"superflua que orbita Irdya junto con nuestro sol original?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:864
msgid ""
"Naia was actually the creation of one of his descendants centuries later, "
"not Vikren himself. Although he did once tell his people that he envisioned "
"a monument to Wesnoth’s glory emblazoned on the vast night sky forever, so "
"the inspiration certainly did come from him."
msgstr ""
"Naia en realidad fue creación de uno de sus descendientes siglos más tarde, "
"no del propio Vikren. Aunque una vez dijo a su gente que imaginaba un "
"monumento a la gloria de Wesnoth grabado para siempre en el vasto cielo "
"nocturno, así que la inspiración sin duda provino de él."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:869
msgid ""
"And you were responsible for his rise to a position that enabled him to "
"inspire his progeny, huh?"
msgstr ""
"Y tú fuiste responsable de su ascenso a una posición que le permitió "
"inspirar a su progenie, ¿eh?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:874
msgid ""
"As you can probably imagine, I am not too proud of that accomplishment these "
"days. But we have tarried here for long enough — let us move on."
msgstr ""
"Como podrás imaginar, no me siento muy orgullosa de ese logro hoy en día. "
"Pero ya hemos perdido demasiado tiempo aquí; sigamos adelante."

#. [scenario]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:904
msgid "Moonfell Wastelands Lorekeeper ‘Aleph’ Report #108"
msgstr ""
"Informe #108 del Guardián de Conocimientos de los Yermos de Luna Caída "
"‘Aleph’"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1063
msgid ""
"Despite every obstacle placed just for you, you still believe you can "
"continue and kill the Chaos Emperor in his own lair. I sorely underestimated "
"your foolishness."
msgstr ""
"A pesar de todos los obstáculos puestos solo para ustedes, aún creen que "
"pueden seguir adelante y matar al Emperador del Caos en su propia guarida. "
"He subestimado gravemente su estupidez."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1070
msgid ""
"Elynia, are we close enough to Inferno already? There is absolutely no way "
"we will be able to advance with her in our way!"
msgstr ""
"Elynia, ¿estamos lo bastante cerca de Inferno ya? ¡No hay forma de que "
"podamos avanzar con ella bloqueando el camino!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1075
msgid ""
"We can try... but while we focus, you will need to protect us from the "
"Warlord’s forces."
msgstr ""
"Podemos intentarlo... pero mientras nos concentramos, necesitarás "
"protegernos de las fuerzas del Señor de la Guerra."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1080
msgid "You heard her — protect them at all costs!"
msgstr "Ya la escucharon: ¡protéjanlos a toda costa!"

#. [event]: id=union_trance_init
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1099
msgid "Move Elynia and Mal Keshar so they are on adjacent hexes"
msgstr "Mueve a Elynia y Mal Keshar para que estén en hexágonos adyacentes"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1165
msgid ""
"Very well, Elynia... let us hope that your theory is correct and will not "
"result in our destruction."
msgstr ""
"Muy bien, Elynia... esperemos que tu teoría sea correcta y no termine con "
"nuestra destrucción."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1170
msgid "... I hope so as well."
msgstr "... Yo también lo espero."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1176
msgid "Protect Elynia and Mal Keshar from harm for $trance_turns turns"
msgstr "Protege a Elynia y Mal Keshar del daño por $trance_turns turnos"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1178
msgid "Protect Elynia and Mal Keshar from harm for one more turn"
msgstr "Protege a Elynia y Mal Keshar del daño por un turno más"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1378
msgid "How... can this be? That power... the Union!"
msgstr "¿Cómo... es posible? ¡Ese poder... la Unión!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1383
msgid "It worked! Malin, it worked!"
msgstr "¡Funcionó! ¡Malin, funcionó!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1388
msgid ""
"Yes... <b>YES!</b> Tremble before us, pathetic worms, and prepare to meet "
"your gods!"
msgstr ""
"Sí... <b>¡SÍ!</b> ¡Tiembla ante nosotros, gusano patético, y prepárate para "
"conocer a tus dioses!"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1392
msgid "Use the Union to take down the Chaos Warlord"
msgstr "Usa la Unión para derribar a la Señora de la Guerra del Caos"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1471
msgid "Hah! Our attacks actually have an effect on her now!"
msgstr "¡Ja! ¡Nuestros ataques por fin le hacen efecto!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1490
msgid ""
"We should not be attacking her directly, it is pointless! Let Elynia and Mal "
"Keshar deal with her instead!"
msgstr ""
"¡No deberíamos atacarla directamente, es inútil! ¡Dejen que Elynia y Mal "
"Keshar se encarguen de ella!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1548
msgid "This is not over yet!"
msgstr "¡Esto aún no ha terminado!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1572
msgid "The coward is fleeing! We must not allow her to escape!"
msgstr "¡La cobarde está huyendo! ¡No debemos permitir que escape!"

#. [event]: id=Elyssa}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1605
msgid "Track down and vanquish the Chaos Warlord"
msgstr "Localiza y derrota al Señor de la Guerra del Caos"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1678
msgid "Uhhh... What is this?"
msgstr "Uhhh... ¿Qué es esto?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1702
msgid "What the...?! Look, this place is floating over an infinite void!"
msgstr "¡¿Qué caraj...?! ¡Mira, este lugar flota sobre un vacío infinito!"

#. [message]: speaker=Erathan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1707
msgid "Dear Lords of Light!"
msgstr "¡Queridos Señores de la Luz!"

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1712
msgid ""
"Wait, I can see stars in it! So... the sky is below us? Are we walking "
"upside-down then, or... Aaaargh, I’m so confused!!!"
msgstr ""
"¡Espera, puedo ver estrellas ahí! Entonces... ¿el cielo está debajo de "
"nosotros? ¿Estamos caminando al revés o...? ¡Aaaargh, estoy tan confundido!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1717
msgid ""
"So this is what the bridge between our worlds looks like. Mal Keshar, we "
"probably should avoid sending spirits across the void, lest they become "
"trapped in it."
msgstr ""
"Así que así es como se ve el puente entre nuestros mundos. Mal Keshar, "
"probablemente deberíamos evitar enviar espíritus a través del vacío, no sea "
"que queden atrapados en él."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1722
msgid "Hm, indeed, that is a risk we cannot afford right now."
msgstr "Hm, en efecto, es un riesgo que no podemos permitirnos ahora."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1741
msgid "Darkness unto the enemies of Uria!"
msgstr "¡Oscuridad sobre los enemigos de Uria!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1770
msgid "I doubt she will be able to keep this up for much longer."
msgstr "Dudo que pueda mantener esto por mucho más tiempo."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1802
msgid "You just don’t know when to give up."
msgstr "Simplemente no sabes cuándo rendirte."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1807
msgid ""
"Neither do you. By now you have surely seen that the power of the Union can "
"destroy you easily. Accept your fate and fight us instead of fleeing like a "
"lowly rat!"
msgstr ""
"Tampoco tú. A estas alturas ya habrás visto que el poder de la Unión puede "
"destruirte con facilidad. ¡Acepta tu destino y enfréntanos en lugar de huir "
"como una rata miserable!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1832
msgid ""
"By... (<i>clutching her face</i>) By the power you have bestowed upon me, "
"Uria, may... the spells conferring life to the dead... be canceled now!"
msgstr ""
"Por... (<i>agarrándose la cara</i>) Por el poder que me has otorgado...Uria, "
"¡que... los hechizos que dan vida a los muertos... sean cancelados ahora!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1858
msgid "My minion! You will pay for that, repulsive wench!"
msgstr "¡Mi sirviente! ¡Pagarás por eso, bruja repugnante!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1864
msgid "My minions! You will pay for that, repulsive wench!"
msgstr "¡Mis sirvientes! ¡Pagarás por eso, bruja repugnante!"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1910
msgid ""
"The combined power of Elynia and Mal Keshar hit the demoness one last time, "
"shattering into her magic defense shield and sending her flying across the "
"bridge. Unable to regain her footing, she desperately grabbed her sword and "
"prepared for the killing blow."
msgstr ""
"El poder combinado de Elynia y Mal Keshar golpeó a la demonio una última "
"vez, rompiendo su escudo mágico y lanzándola por el puente. Incapaz de "
"recuperar el equilibrio, tomó su espada con desesperación y se preparó para "
"el golpe final."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1950
msgid ""
"Go on, Elynia. Do what you must do. Now that I have failed, there’s no "
"purpose left for me..."
msgstr ""
"Vamos, Elynia. Haz lo que tengas que hacer. Ahora que he fallado, ya no me "
"queda ningún propósito..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1955
msgid "Who are you?"
msgstr "¿Quién eres?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1960
msgid "Why would I tell you?"
msgstr "¿Por qué debería decírtelo?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1965
msgid "I would feel much better about ending your miserable life if you did."
msgstr ""
"Me sentiría mucho mejor al acabar con tu miserable vida si lo hicieras."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#. Intentionally not mentioning the Chaos Emperor's name here.
#. Note that she's referring to him back when the empire did not
#. even exist!
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1977
msgid ""
"I am Elyssa. I dedicated my life to studying the ancient Empire’s history "
"from whatever remnants I could find amidst the sands. That is... before I "
"found him... and Uria.... Their great power and knowledge truly changed me, "
"and in time, they will change this world too."
msgstr ""
"Soy Elyssa. Dediqué mi vida a estudiar la historia del antiguo Imperio a "
"partir de los restos que pude encontrar entre las arenas. Eso fue... antes "
"de encontrarlo a él... y a Uria... Su gran poder y conocimiento realmente me "
"cambiaron, y con el tiempo, también cambiarán este mundo."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1986
msgid "Where is your master hiding?"
msgstr "¿Dónde se esconde tu maestro?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:1995
msgid "She’s not going to answer. Off with her head!"
msgstr "No va a responder. ¡Córtenle la cabeza!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:2000
msgid ""
"You are not going to do it, are you? I can give you an answer... but only if "
"you swear you will spare my life."
msgstr ""
"No vas a hacerlo, ¿verdad? Puedo darte una respuesta... pero solo si juras "
"que me perdonarás la vida."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:2005
msgid ""
"Don’t listen to her lies, Elynia! You know these creatures cannot be trusted!"
msgstr ""
"¡No escuches sus mentiras, Elynia! Sabes que no se puede confiar en estas "
"criaturas."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:2012
msgid ""
"Elynia stared directly into the demoness’ eyes, with a frightening "
"expression of suppressed rage. Time seemed to stop for the watchers, and no-"
"one dared break the uneasy silence."
msgstr ""
"Elynia miró directamente a los ojos de la demonio, con una expresión "
"aterradora de ira contenida. El tiempo pareció detenerse para los "
"observadores, y nadie se atrevió a romper el tenso silencio."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:2022
msgid "Finally, she spoke."
msgstr "Finalmente, habló."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:2027
msgid ""
"Tell me what you know and you can keep what little life you have left, as "
"long as you get out of my sight as quickly as you can. Now out with it."
msgstr ""
"Dime lo que sabes y podrás conservar lo poco de vida que te queda, siempre "
"que desaparezcas de mi vista lo más rápido posible. Vamos, habla."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:2032
msgid "But she..."
msgstr "Pero ella..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elyssa
#. If your language has singular/plural 'you' ambiguity like
#. English, try to use that for the "greatest fears" part of
#. this line; otherwise make it plural.
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:2044
msgid ""
"Do you see the passage ahead? Go through it, and you will be in Inferno. The "
"entrance to his icy fortress is just across the snow past the end the road. "
"There, you will find the heart of the hive, and his lair. But be warned: "
"once you enter, there will be no going back without first confronting your "
"greatest fears."
msgstr ""
"¿Ven el pasaje adelante? Atraviésenlo y estarán en Inferno. La entrada a su "
"fortaleza helada está justo al otro lado de la nieve, pasado el final del "
"camino. Allí encontrarán el corazón de la colmena y su guarida. Pero tengan "
"cuidado: una vez que entren, no habrá vuelta atrás sin antes enfrentar sus "
"mayores miedos."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:2049
msgid "Very well, then. Now, go."
msgstr "Muy bien, entonces. Ahora vete."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:2065
msgid "Why would you do this, Elynia? That woman is Anlindë’s murderer!"
msgstr "¿Por qué hiciste esto, Elynia? ¡Esa mujer es la asesina de Anlindë!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:2070
msgid ""
"I cannot bring myself to kill someone so much weaker than I. It would be "
"unfair... and cruel. You remember how the lich Mal Keshar came to be, do you "
"not? Let yourself succumb to wrath and you become as bad as the foul-minded "
"creatures you fight."
msgstr ""
"No puedo obligarme a matar a alguien tan inferior a mí. Sería injusto... y "
"cruel. ¿Recuerdas cómo llegó a ser el liche Mal Keshar, verdad? Si te dejas "
"consumir por la ira, te vuelves tan despreciable como las criaturas de mente "
"corrupta contra las que luchas."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/22B_Dark_Hive.cfg:2079
msgid ""
"Now, it’s time to go find the answers we seek. Let us see... if the Chaos "
"Emperor can be stopped before the madness of this place consumes us as well."
msgstr ""
"Ahora es momento de buscar las respuestas que necesitamos. Veamos... si el "
"Emperador del Caos puede ser detenido antes de que la locura de este lugar "
"nos consuma también."

#. [side]
#. [side]: type=Dead Shadow Master, id=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:49
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:176
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:297
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:53
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:37
msgid "team_name^Chaos Emperor"
msgstr "Señora de la Guerra del Caos"

#. [side]: type=Chaos Lorekeeper, id=Mal Murwiel
#. [side]: type=Chaos Lorekeeper, id=Mal Aravir
#. [side]: type=Hell Overlord, id=Yivril
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:111
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:143
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:131
msgid "team_name^Lair Guards"
msgstr "Guardias de la Guarida"

#. [side]: type=Chaos Lorekeeper, id=Mal Murwiel
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:130
msgid "Mal Murwiel"
msgstr "Mal Murwiel"

#. [side]: type=Chaos Lorekeeper, id=Mal Aravir
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:162
msgid "Mal Aravir"
msgstr "Mal Aravir"

#. [side]: type=Demon Warrior, id=Ka'alarilyn
#. [side]: type=Demon Warrior, gender=female, id=Vyta
#. [side]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:193
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:229
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:159
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:273
msgid "team_name^Lair Hive"
msgstr "Guarida Colmena"

#. [side]: type=Demon Warrior, id=Ka'alarilyn
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:213
msgid "Ka’alarilyn"
msgstr "Ka’alarilyn"

#. [side]: type=Demon Warrior, gender=female, id=Vyta
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:247
msgid "Vyta"
msgstr "Vyta"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:593
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:897
msgid "Find the entrance to the lair of the Chaos Emperor"
msgstr "Encuentra la entrada a la guarida del Emperador del Caos"

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:634
msgid ""
"I didn’t think the demons’ homeland would be such a... cold... place— "
"<b>ATCHOO!!!</b>"
msgstr ""
"No pensé que la tierra natal de los demonios sería un lugar tan... frío... —"
"<b>¡ATCHÚS!</b>"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:639
msgid "I have to say, I never expected Inferno to be such a cold place."
msgstr "Debo decir que nunca esperé que el Infierno fuera un lugar tan frío."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:645
msgid ""
"Yes, there does not appear to be anything but more snow in the distance. Who "
"knew!"
msgstr ""
"Sí, no parece haber nada más que nieve en la distancia. ¡Quién lo diría!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:650
msgid ""
"I assume this is but a small land in a much larger realm. The stories speak "
"of far more varied locations, much like Irdya itself."
msgstr ""
"Asumo que esto es solo una pequeña tierra en un reino mucho más grande. Las "
"historias hablan de lugares mucho más variados, al igual que Irdya."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:655
msgid ""
"Surely the Emperor chose this location in order to have a nigh-on unlimited "
"water supply for his ostentatious capital, then."
msgstr ""
"Seguramente el Emperador eligió este lugar para tener un suministro de agua "
"casi ilimitado para su ostentosa capital."

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:667
msgid ""
"Come to think of it, there <b>is</b> nothing but snow in sight, indeed. Does "
"anyone else find this troubling?"
msgstr ""
"Ahora que lo pienso, en verdad <b>no</b> hay nada más que nieve a la vista. "
"¿Alguien más encuentra esto inquietante?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:672
msgid "You are right, the solitude of this place doesn’t bode well."
msgstr "Tienes razón, la soledad de este lugar no augura nada bueno."

#. [message]: speaker=Erathan
#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:698
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:703
msgid "I spot a few foes over there."
msgstr "Veo a algunos enemigos allí."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:742
msgid "Welcome! Welcome all to my lair, foolish creatures!"
msgstr "¡Bienvenidos! ¡Bienvenidos todos a mi guarida, criaturas insensatas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:749
msgid ""
"It’s that infuriating laugh again! Oh, I swear, the moment I get my hands on "
"that pretentious bastard..."
msgstr ""
"¡Es esa risa irritante otra vez! Oh, lo juro, en cuanto ponga mis manos "
"sobre ese bastardo pretencioso..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:831
msgid ""
"The protection enchantment shielding this gate is far too strong. May I "
"suggest searching for another way to open it?"
msgstr ""
"El encantamiento de protección que resguarda esta puerta es demasiado "
"fuerte. ¿Puedo sugerir buscar otra forma de abrirla?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:836
msgid "Union?"
msgstr "¿Unión?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:841
msgid ""
"I would rather avoid unnecessary use of it while we are in this place... I "
"hope you can understand why."
msgstr ""
"Preferiría evitar un uso innecesario de ella mientras estemos en este "
"lugar... Espero que puedas entender por qué."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:848
msgid ""
"... Yes... I <i>think</i> I see where this is going. Very well, then. Let us "
"do things your way."
msgstr ""
"... Sí... <i>creo</i> que veo a dónde va esto. Muy bien, entonces. Hagámoslo "
"a tu manera."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:873
msgid ""
"Hey, what do we have here... Cockatrices! There are cockatrices roaming "
"about this place!"
msgstr ""
"Eh, ¿qué tenemos aquí...? ¡Basiliscos! ¡Hay basiliscos merodeando por este "
"lugar!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:883
msgid ""
"Bird-like creatures which are said to have the ability to turn any living "
"thing to stone with a single glance. They are not natural denizens of our "
"world, being instead the product of forbidden sorcery."
msgstr ""
"Criaturas parecidas a aves que, según se dice, tienen la capacidad de "
"convertir en piedra a cualquier ser vivo con una sola mirada. No son "
"habitantes naturales de nuestro mundo, sino el producto de una hechicería "
"prohibida."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:888
msgid ""
"Yes, yes — all right, attention everyone! Avoid direct eye contact with "
"these pests or you <i>will</i> regret it!"
msgstr ""
"Sí, sí — ¡de acuerdo, atención todos! Eviten el contacto visual directo con "
"esas alimañas o lo <i>lamentarán</i>."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:893
msgid ""
"I believe I can remove the effects of their magic with a spell. However, "
"should any victim come to harm while petrified..."
msgstr ""
"Creo que puedo eliminar los efectos de su magia con un hechizo. Sin embargo, "
"si alguna víctima sufre daños mientras está petrificada..."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:899
msgid "Elynia is petrified by an enemy unit"
msgstr "Elynia está petrificada por una unidad enemiga"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:909
msgid ""
"Elynia can revert the effects of petrification on adjacent player units at "
"the start of each turn"
msgstr ""
"Elynia puede revertir los efectos de la petrificación en las unidades "
"aliadas adyacentes al comienzo de cada turno"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:928
msgid "I can’t... help you... now..."
msgstr "No puedo... ayudarlos... ahora..."

#. [unit]: type=Chimera, id=Knidaril
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:983
msgid "Knidaril"
msgstr "Knidaril"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:1035
msgid "This is quite obviously an invitation into a trap. Shall we heed it?"
msgstr ""
"Esto es, claramente, una invitación a una trampa. ¿Deberíamos aceptarla?"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:1040
msgid ""
"This whole place feels like a trap to me. On the other hand, if we don’t "
"come to him..."
msgstr ""
"Todo este lugar me parece una trampa. Por otro lado, si no vamos hacia él..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:1045
msgid "... he will come to us."
msgstr "... él vendrá a nosotros."

#. [scenario]: type=Cockatrice}
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:1097
msgid ""
"The glyph’s contents seem to be in a language you have never read nor heard "
"before."
msgstr ""
"El contenido del glifo parece estar en un idioma que nunca has leído ni oído "
"antes."

#. [scenario]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:12
msgid "Until Death"
msgstr "Hasta la muerte"

#. [side]: type=Hell Overlord, id=Yivril
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:149
msgid "Yivril"
msgstr "Yivril"

#. [side]: type=Chaos Lorekeeper, id=Mal Myaramor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:206
msgid "Mal Myaramor"
msgstr "Mal Myaramor"

#. [side]: type=Shadow Courier, id=An-Laila
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:262
msgid "An-Laila"
msgstr "An-Laila"

#. [scenario]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:489
msgid "Argan, the Master of Darkness"
msgstr "Argan, el Amo de la Oscuridad"

#. [scenario]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:489
msgid "Voice of Uria"
msgstr "Voz de Uria"

#. [unit]: type=Master of Darkness, id=Chaos Emperor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:532
msgid "Chaos Emperor"
msgstr "Emperador del caos"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:548
msgid ""
"There he is. There doesn’t appear to be anyone else around. Would it be "
"possible for you two, perhaps, to strike him down from afar while he has his "
"back turned?"
msgstr ""
"Aquí está. No parece haber nadie más cerca. ¿Sería posible que ustedes dos, "
"quizás, lo derribaran desde lejos mientras tiene la espalda vuelta?"

#. [message]: speaker=Chaos Emperor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:553
msgid ""
"I was certain that you would not fail your word, Galas. At long last you and "
"your loyal companions have made it to my lair, overcoming every obstacle in "
"your way. Well done."
msgstr ""
"Estaba seguro de que no romperías tu palabra, Galas. Por fin tú y tus leales "
"compañeros han llegado a mi guarida, superando cada obstáculo en su camino. "
"Bien hecho."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:568
msgid "So we have. Now it’s down to you and us."
msgstr "Así es. Ahora todo depende de ustedes y nosotros."

#. [message]: speaker=Chaos Emperor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:573
msgid "Not exactly. You allow yourselves to be deceived by appearances."
msgstr "No exactamente. Se permiten ser engañados por las apariencias."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:615
msgid ""
"Who are you in truth? Reveal your identity, scum! We should at least be "
"allowed to know the name of the wretched creature hiding behind that mask!"
msgstr ""
"¿Quién eres en verdad? ¡Revela tu identidad, escoria! ¡Al menos deberíamos "
"tener derecho a conocer el nombre de la miserable criatura que se oculta "
"detrás de esa máscara!"

#. [message]: speaker=An-Laila
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:620
msgid "Hehehehehehehehehe..."
msgstr "Jejejejejejejejeje..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Myaramor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:625
msgid "<b>AH HA HA HA HA HA HA HA HA!</b>"
msgstr "<b>¡JA JA JA JA JA JA JA JA JA!</b>"

#. [message]: speaker=Chaos Emperor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:630
msgid ""
"Have you not told them yet, Elynia? What do you expect to accomplish by "
"withholding the truth from your allies?"
msgstr ""
"¿Aún no se lo has contado, Elynia? ¿Qué esperas lograr ocultando la verdad a "
"tus aliados?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:640
msgid "Told us what, exactly?"
msgstr "¿Nos dijiste qué, exactamente?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:657
msgid ""
"Oh, Galas. I am so sorry. All this time, I wanted to believe otherwise... I "
"wanted..."
msgstr ""
"Oh, Galas. Lo siento tanto. Todo este tiempo quise creer otra cosa... Yo "
"quería..."

#. [message]: speaker=Chaos Emperor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:662
msgid "To escape the truth is what you wanted."
msgstr "Lo que querías era escapar de la verdad."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:682
msgid ""
"Once he had pronounced those words, the Chaos Emperor reached for his "
"facemask and disconnected the wires that held it in place, one by one. The "
"Lady of Light just stood there, trembling ever so slightly, her eyes "
"concealed by her right hand. Completely ignorant of the thoughts and "
"feelings raging inside her, Galas could only watch as the dark truth "
"unraveled before his eyes."
msgstr ""
"Tras pronunciar esas palabras, el Emperador del Caos alcanzó su máscara y "
"desconectó los cables que la mantenían en su lugar, uno a uno. La Dama de La "
"Luz simplemente permaneció ahí, temblando apenas, con los ojos ocultos por "
"su mano derecha. Ignorando por completo los pensamientos y sentimientos que "
"la consumían por dentro, Galas sólo pudo observar cómo la oscura verdad se "
"desplegaba ante sus ojos."

#. [modify_side]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:720
msgid "team_name^Argan"
msgstr "Argan"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:739
msgid ""
"And although he quite obviously would have never recognized the distorted "
"visage of the monster otherwise, the silence that followed allowed him to "
"clearly hear Elynia’s faint voice uttering his name."
msgstr ""
"Y aunque evidentemente nunca habría reconocido el rostro distorsionado del "
"monstruo de otro modo, el silencio que siguió le permitió escuchar "
"claramente la débil voz de Elynia pronunciando su nombre."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:753
msgid "Why... did this happen... When... Why could I never find you...?"
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué... sucedió esto... Cuándo... Por qué nunca pude encontrarte...?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:758
msgid ""
"I cannot... believe this. So my suspicions were true. And you... Elynia... "
"you knew this! You led us here when you knew his identity and never saw fit "
"to reveal it! Why?"
msgstr ""
"No puedo... creer esto. Entonces mis sospechas eran ciertas. Y tú... "
"Elynia... ¡lo sabías! Nos llevaste aquí sabiendo quién era y nunca creíste "
"conveniente revelarlo. ¿Por qué?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:763
msgid ""
"Having heard about Yechnagoth, I tried my hardest to believe that the power "
"that enshrouded the lands of Uria was not his doing, and— and perhaps..."
msgstr ""
"Habiendo oído sobre Yechnagoth, hice todo lo posible por creer que el poder "
"que envolvía las tierras de Uria no era obra suya, y— y quizás..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:770
msgid ""
"You are but a foul impostor created by Uria to lead our Lady astray! There "
"is no chance I will ever accept that the Master of Darkness who once "
"protected Irdya has turned to evil! You shall pay for each and every one of "
"your misdeeds!"
msgstr ""
"Eres un vil impostor creado por Uria para engañar a nuestra Dama. ¡Nunca "
"aceptaré que el Maestro de la Oscuridad que una vez protegió Irdya haya "
"cambiado al mal! ¡Pagarás por cada una de tus fechorías!"

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:775
msgid ""
"Oh, but I am very real. While I cannot deny that she made me who I am now, "
"you are deeply mistaken if you think I am not the true Master of Darkness. "
"Even now in these dark times, I continue to look out for Irdya; but instead "
"of wandering the earth as an aimless soul, I follow the path that was laid "
"before us by the Guardian of Life herself. I am her Voice, and I carry out "
"her will for the sake of our future."
msgstr ""
"Oh, pero soy muy real. Aunque no puedo negar que ella me hizo quien soy "
"ahora, estás profundamente equivocado si crees que no soy el verdadero "
"Maestro de la Oscuridad. Incluso ahora, en estos tiempos oscuros, continúo "
"velando por Irdya; pero en lugar de vagar por la tierra como un alma sin "
"rumbo, sigo el camino que nos fue trazado por la Guardiana de la Vida misma. "
"Soy su Voz, y llevo a cabo su voluntad por el bien de nuestro futuro."

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:780
msgid ""
"Elynia, have you not wondered yourself countless times whether it was "
"destiny or a true coincidence that made our paths cross on Irdya? Did you "
"not ask me once why we, mere mortals, had been blessed with an ultimate "
"power beyond our comprehension? Why, even now that you have witnessed how by "
"Uria’s grace I overcame the limits of my frail vessel, you continue to "
"renounce her will? We were born to be together, to fight together, to save "
"this doomed reality together! What should I do to persuade you to embrace "
"our glorious destiny under her command?"
msgstr ""
"Elynia, ¿no te has preguntado tú misma innumerables veces si fue el destino "
"o una verdadera coincidencia lo que hizo que nuestros caminos se cruzaran en "
"Irdya? ¿No me preguntaste alguna vez por qué nosotros, simples mortales, "
"fuimos bendecidos con un poder supremo más allá de nuestra comprensión? ¿Por "
"qué, incluso ahora que has visto cómo por la gracia de Uria superé los "
"límites de mi frágil cuerpo, continúas rechazando su voluntad? ¡Nacimos para "
"estar juntos, para luchar juntos, para salvar esta realidad condenada "
"juntos! ¿Qué debo hacer para persuadirte a que abraces nuestro glorioso "
"destino bajo su mando?"

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:789
msgid "Or perhaps, you truly believe I am an impostor like this elf claims."
msgstr "O quizás, realmente crees que soy un impostor, como dice ese elfo."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:798
msgid ""
"No, Argan. I believe you. I have always believed you. I believe you even "
"now, at the end. I loved you, and I still love you."
msgstr ""
"No, Argan. Te creo. Siempre te he creído. Te creo incluso ahora, al final. "
"Te amé, y todavía te amo."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:807
msgid "Which is why I must put an end to your suffering."
msgstr "Por eso debo poner fin a tu sufrimiento."

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:814
msgid ""
"I see. If there is nothing I can do to make you accept the truth, then you "
"will have to die as well. As much as it pains me to even consider the "
"possibility... Uria’s will reigns supreme."
msgstr ""
"Ya veo. Si no hay nada que pueda hacer para que aceptes la verdad, entonces "
"tú también tendrás que morir. Por más doloroso que sea siquiera considerar "
"esa posibilidad... la voluntad de Uria reina suprema."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Myaramor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:819
msgid "One last chance to retract your words, unbelievers!"
msgstr "¡Última oportunidad para retractarse de sus palabras, incrédulos!"

#. [message]: speaker=An-Laila
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:828
msgid ""
"O Voice that speaks the will of the Mother of Urvatha, what is your command?"
msgstr ""
"Oh Voz que habla la voluntad de la Madre de Urvatha, ¿cuál es tu mandato?"

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:833
msgid "Kill them."
msgstr "Mátenlos."

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:838
msgid "Kill them all."
msgstr "Mátenlos a todos."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:869
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1704
msgid ""
"Kill Argan, the Master of Darkness, and put an end to his sinister rule over "
"Irdya"
msgstr ""
"Mata a Argan, el Maestro de la Oscuridad, y pon fin a su siniestro dominio "
"sobre Irdya."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:880
msgid ""
"Mal Keshar’s presence should allow you to recruit undead once again if you "
"can capture an enemy keep"
msgstr ""
"La presencia de Mal Keshar debería permitirte reclutar no-muertos una vez "
"más si logras capturar una fortaleza enemiga."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Myaramor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:896
msgid "Thus you have sealed your fate! Ack—"
msgstr "¡Así has sellado tu destino! ¡Ack—"

#. [message]: speaker=An-Laila
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:908
msgid ""
"Go on, destroy the container of my soul if you must. As long as Uria exists, "
"I can be brought back..."
msgstr ""
"Sigue, destruye el contenedor de mi alma si es necesario. Mientras Uria "
"exista, puedo ser traído de vuelta..."

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:923
msgid ""
"Why did it have to come to this, my beloved Elynia? Why must we face each "
"other as enemies now, after spending so many thousands of years apart?"
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué tuvo que llegar a esto, mi amada Elynia? ¿Por qué debemos "
"enfrentarnos ahora como enemigos, después de pasar tantos miles de años "
"separados?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:928
msgid ""
"Oh, right! Are you saying I shouldn’t take all the attempts on my life by "
"your subjects as a sign of hostility? Or that I should allow you to continue "
"this new pitiful existence of yours?"
msgstr ""
"¡Ah, claro! ¿Me estás diciendo que no debería tomar todos los intentos "
"contra mi vida por parte de tus súbditos como una señal de hostilidad? ¿O "
"que debería permitirte continuar con esta nueva existencia lamentable que "
"tienes?"

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:933
msgid ""
"You say that as though you have not let that mediocre necromancer become an "
"ally and friend of yours. Is his existence in undeath not far more pitiful "
"than mine? My body was not just rebuilt, but also improved! I can understand "
"your distrust of this new form of technology, but no-one will force you to "
"change your beautiful body if you don’t wish to transcend its limitations — "
"as long as you devote your life and soul to our one true goddess."
msgstr ""
"Lo dices como si no hubieras permitido que ese mediocre nigromante se "
"convirtiera en tu aliado y amigo. ¿No es acaso su existencia en la no-muerte "
"mucho más lamentable que la mía? ¡Mi cuerpo no solo fue reconstruido, sino "
"también mejorado! Puedo entender tu desconfianza hacia esta nueva forma de "
"tecnología, pero nadie te obligará a cambiar tu hermoso cuerpo si no deseas "
"trascender sus limitaciones — siempre y cuando dediques tu vida y alma a "
"nuestra única verdadera diosa."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:938
msgid "Exactly who are you calling mediocre, you miserable piece of—"
msgstr "¿A quién llamas mediocre, pedazo miserable de—"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:943
msgid ""
"If this goddess of yours truly cared for all life on Irdya, she would not be "
"using you to destroy it! Are you not the Chaos Emperor? Did you not command "
"your legions to raze and desecrate the earth?! How can you... how can you "
"speak as if all this destruction were for the greater good!?"
msgstr ""
"Si esta diosa tuya realmente se preocupara por toda la vida en Irdya, no te "
"estaría usando para destruirla. ¿No eres tú el Emperador del Caos? ¿No "
"ordenaste a tus legiones arrasar y profanar la tierra? ¿Cómo puedes... cómo "
"puedes hablar como si toda esta destrucción fuera para un bien mayor?"

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#. He's calling Elynia "my love", in case it's not obvious.
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:949
msgid ""
"If only you could understand the ineffable designs of our goddess, my love. "
"If only you allowed me to show you the way..."
msgstr ""
"Si tan solo pudieras entender los inescrutables designios de nuestra diosa, "
"mi amor. Si tan solo me permitieras mostrarte el camino..."

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:958
msgid "Every day and every night without you has been a nightmare..."
msgstr "Cada día y cada noche sin ti ha sido una pesadilla..."

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:967
msgid ""
"I hoped that the nightmare would end tonight. But no, you had to choose the "
"path of the infidels. And on top of that, you had to choose <i>him</i>, of "
"all creatures — a lowly mundane elf of the forest with no remarkable "
"qualities whatsoever."
msgstr ""
"Esperaba que la pesadilla terminara esta noche. Pero no, tuviste que elegir "
"el camino de los infieles. Y encima, tuviste que elegir <i>a él</i>, de "
"todas las criaturas — un simple elfo común del bosque sin cualidades "
"destacables."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:972
msgid ""
"How dare <i>you</i>, of all people, appeal to jealousy now after all we’ve "
"been through?! And in any case, he is nothing but my friend!"
msgstr ""
"¿Cómo te <i>atreves</i>, de entre todas las personas, a apelar a los celos "
"ahora después de todo lo que hemos pasado? ¡Y de todos modos, él no es más "
"que mi amigo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1067
msgid ""
"Your ploy to draw power from me and into the lich to gain control of the "
"Union was quite ingenious. I would have never expected any less from you, my "
"love. Still, I fear that I must revoke your magic privileges before anyone "
"else gets hurt."
msgstr ""
"Tu estrategia para absorber mi poder y traspasarlo al lich para controlar la "
"Unión fue bastante ingeniosa. Nunca habría esperado menos de ti, mi amor. "
"Aún así, temo que debo revocar tus privilegios mágicos antes de que alguien "
"más salga herido."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1078
msgid "ARGH! He’s reaching into my mind!"
msgstr "¡ARGH! ¡Está entrando en mi mente!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1083
msgid "Malin!"
msgstr "¡Malin!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1116
msgid "I cannot... control my body..."
msgstr "No puedo... controlar mi cuerpo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1122
msgid "You people surely would not murder your own allies, right?"
msgstr "Seguramente ustedes no asesinarían a sus propios aliados, ¿verdad?"

#. [message]: speaker=Erathan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1134
msgid "Argh!!! Get out of... my head!!!"
msgstr "¡Argh!!! ¡Sal de... mi cabeza!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1146
msgid "Elynia! He... he’s doing it again... NO!!!"
msgstr "¡Elynia! Él... lo está haciendo otra vez... ¡NO!!!"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1169
msgid "Galas! It cannot end like this — you must fight back!"
msgstr "¡Galas! No puede terminar así — ¡debes resistir!"

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1177
msgid ""
"I really do not want to do this to you, Elynia, and I am sure you would be "
"unable to live with yourself if your friends were to perish because of one "
"single misguided choice. I offer you one more chance to accept Uria as our "
"true protector—"
msgstr ""
"Realmente no quiero hacerte esto, Elynia, y estoy seguro de que no podrías "
"vivir contigo misma si tus amigos perecieran por una sola elección "
"equivocada. Te ofrezco una última oportunidad de aceptar a Uria como nuestra "
"verdadera protectora—"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1182
msgid ""
"Never! Do you really believe I would choose two people over the fate of "
"Irdya? Who do you take me for?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Nunca! ¿Realmente crees que elegiría a dos personas por encima del destino "
"de Irdya? ¿Por quién me tomas?!"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1186
msgid "Use Elynia to destroy Mal Keshar"
msgstr "Usa a Elynia para destruir a Mal Keshar."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1190
msgid "Death of Mal Keshar at the hands of any other unit"
msgstr "Muerte de Mal Keshar a manos de cualquier otra unidad"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1227
msgid "I... ugh—"
msgstr "Yo... ugh—"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1262
msgid "— I <b>don’t</b> have time for <b>THIS!</b>"
msgstr "— ¡<b>No</b> tengo tiempo para <b>ESTO!</b>"

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1267
msgid ""
"Oh... Oh. You learned to block their spell. That is such a pity — I had "
"hoped Uria would at least allow me to keep you as a garden ornament."
msgstr ""
"Oh... Oh. Aprendiste a bloquear su hechizo. Qué lástima — esperaba que Uria "
"al menos me permitiera conservarte como adorno para el jardín."

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1355
msgid ""
"Perhaps you will learn to not regard the undead as companions now that you "
"realize how easy it is to turn them against their masters."
msgstr ""
"Quizás ahora aprenderás a no considerar a los no-muertos como compañeros, al "
"darte cuenta de lo fácil que es volverlos contra sus amos."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1380
msgid "No, Galas!"
msgstr "No, Galas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1457
msgid ""
"Our foolishness allowed the Warlord to take one of our friends away from us. "
"But I will not let you take advantage of us again, Argan. Not today!"
msgstr ""
"Nuestra necedad permitió al Señor de la Guerra arrebatarnos a uno de "
"nuestros amigos. ¡Pero no dejaré que te aproveches de nosotros otra vez, "
"Argan! ¡No hoy!"

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1484
msgid "No! This light... I cannot—"
msgstr "¡No! Esta luz... no puedo—"

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1507
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1544
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1676
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:2075
msgid "caption^Argan?"
msgstr "Argan?"

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#. Every Argan line with the female^ prefix is actually spoken
#. by Uria herself. The prefix is a hint for translations were
#. gendered speaker syntax is required (e.g. personal pronouns).
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1511
msgid "female^<span color='#fd5' weight='bold'>STOP HER!</span>"
msgstr "<span color='#fd5' weight='bold'>¡DETÉNGANLA!</span>"

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1545
msgid "female^No... more... fooling around."
msgstr "No... más... juegos."

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1550
msgid "I... I recognize that voice..."
msgstr "Yo... reconozco esa voz..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1580
msgid "Elynia... You saved me again..."
msgstr "Elynia... Me salvaste otra vez..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1585
msgid ""
"I’m sorry it took me so long, Galas, but with Mal Keshar under his control..."
msgstr ""
"Lamento haber tardado tanto, Galas, pero con Mal Keshar bajo su control..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1592
msgid "Mal Keshar! Is he... gone?"
msgstr "¡Mal Keshar! ¿Está... destruido?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1597
msgid ""
"If he truly is as powerful as he likes to make himself out to be, there "
"might be a chance his soul is still intact, but whether it will return to "
"this body..."
msgstr ""
"Si en verdad es tan poderoso como le gusta aparentar, puede que haya una "
"posibilidad de que su alma siga intacta... pero que regrese a este cuerpo es "
"otra cuestión..."

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1666
msgid ""
"You made a fatal mistake in coming to Inferno, Elynia. As long as you are in "
"the same realm as I, I too can use the Union against you."
msgstr ""
"Cometiste un error fatal al venir a Ínferno, Elynia. Mientras estés en el "
"mismo reino que yo, también puedo usar la Unión contra ti."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1671
msgid "(<i>defiant</i>) Then one of us must die first."
msgstr "(<i>desafiante</i>) Entonces, uno de los dos debe morir primero."

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1677
msgid ""
"female^Truly, it is a magnificent power. It is a shame that you will not "
"surrender it to me willingly, Lady of Light."
msgstr ""
"En verdad, es un poder magnífico. Es una lástima que no lo entregues "
"voluntariamente, Dama de la Luz."

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1717
msgid ""
"Elynia is able to use the Union without Mal Keshar if she is adjacent to "
"Argan, although doing so puts her at risk"
msgstr ""
"Elynia puede usar la Unión sin Mal Keshar si está adyacente a Argan, aunque "
"al hacerlo se expone a un gran riesgo"

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1953
msgid "You are... hurting me..."
msgstr "Tú... me estás lastimando..."

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1962
msgid "Elynia... Why do you do this?"
msgstr "Elynia... ¿Por qué haces esto?"

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1972
msgid ""
"We were meant to be together... for the rest of eternity... Do you not love "
"me anymore, Elynia?"
msgstr ""
"Estábamos destinados a estar juntos... por toda la eternidad... ¿Acaso ya no "
"me amas, Elynia?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:1977
msgid ""
"You... You’ve become a monster! An abomination! Do you really not realize "
"what you’ve done, what... what Uria has done to you?"
msgstr ""
"¡Tú... te has convertido en un monstruo! ¡Una abominación! ¿De verdad no te "
"das cuenta de lo que has hecho, de lo que... lo que Uria te ha hecho?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:2058
msgid ""
"Excuse me, did I miss anything? ... Oh! I guess you haven’t managed to "
"strike down that pompous fool yet. Good, good."
msgstr ""
"Perdón, ¿me he perdido de algo? ... ¡Oh! Supongo que aún no han logrado "
"derribar a ese necio pomposo. Bien, bien."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:2063
msgid ""
"Mal Keshar! Thank the Lords of Light — I thought I would never hear you "
"speak again. Do you think you can still help us somehow?"
msgstr ""
"¡Mal Keshar! Gracias a los Señores de la Luz — pensé que jamás volvería a "
"escucharte hablar. ¿Crees que aún puedes ayudarnos de alguna forma?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:2068
msgid ""
"Help you? HA! Of course I can help you! It will take much more than some "
"unfathomable ancient power to put me out of commission, boy."
msgstr ""
"¿Ayudarlos? ¡JA! ¡Por supuesto que puedo ayudarlos! Se necesitaría mucho más "
"que un poder antiguo e insondable para dejarme fuera de combate, muchacho."

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:2076
msgid "female^Put an end... to this... <b>NOW!</b>"
msgstr "Pongan fin... a esto... <b>¡AHORA!</b>"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:2251
msgid "Look out! Those creatures emerge from his body with each hit!"
msgstr "¡Cuidado! ¡Esas criaturas emergen de su cuerpo con cada golpe!"

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:2271
msgid "Energy... Yes... Feed me more energy..."
msgstr "Energía... Sí... Denme más energía..."

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:2309
msgid "No... Noooooo!!! My power... falters..."
msgstr "No... ¡Noooooo! Mi poder... flaquea..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:2330
msgid "It’s— it’s tearing me apart—"
msgstr "Me está— me está destrozando—"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:2485
msgid "What just happened?"
msgstr "¿Qué acaba de pasar?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23B_Until_Death.cfg:2494
msgid "The prophecy... has been broken."
msgstr "La profecía... ha sido rota."

#. [scenario]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:4
msgid "Do Us Part"
msgstr "Hasta que la muerte nos separe"

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:116
msgid "Elynia..."
msgstr "Elynia…"

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:140
msgid "... you betrayed... me..."
msgstr "...me… traicionaste…"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:145
msgid ""
"No, Argan. You are the one who betrayed me... me and the peoples of Irdya as "
"well — those we swore to defend until the end of time. You betrayed "
"everything we stood for..."
msgstr ""
"No, Argan. Tú eres quien me traicionó... a mí y también a los pueblos de "
"Irdya — aquellos que juramos defender hasta el fin de los tiempos. "
"Traicionaste todo por lo que luchábamos..."

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:150
msgid ""
"I did nothing but choose the right path for your sake. And this is how you "
"repay me... Then again, I guess I had this coming ever since... then..."
msgstr ""
"Yo no hice más que elegir el camino correcto por ti. Y así es como me lo "
"pagas… Aunque supongo que esto lo tenía merecido desde… entonces…"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:155
msgid ""
"No, you never deserved any of this. If... None of this... none of this would "
"have happened if I..."
msgstr ""
"No, nunca mereciste nada de esto. Si… Nada de esto… nada de esto habría "
"ocurrido si yo…"

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:163
msgid "In the end... it is not your fault..."
msgstr "Al final… no es tu culpa…"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:168
msgid ""
"You said that Uria turned you into this. What does she really want? What’s "
"her goal in enslaving and desecrating Irdya?"
msgstr ""
"Dijiste que Uria te convirtió en esto. ¿Qué es lo que realmente quiere? "
"¿Cuál es su objetivo al esclavizar y profanar Irdya?"

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:173
msgid ""
"Well... she will... she will avenge me... that is for sure. And now without "
"the Union, you cannot— (<i>cough</i>) you cannot defeat... her... Even if "
"you manage to find her... in the heart of... Urvatha... it would be "
"suicide..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno… ella… ella me vengará… de eso puedes estar seguro. Y ahora sin la "
"Unión, no podr— (<i>tose</i>) no podran derrotarla… Incluso si lograran "
"encontrarla… en el corazón de… Urvatha… sería un suicidio…"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:183
msgid ""
"Just as he said those words, Argan’s broken body suddenly convulsed, "
"releasing a steaming mixture of blood and a thick yellow ooze from his mouth "
"and chest, and splashing everything around him. The bright yellow glow that "
"constantly lit his eyes until moments before began to vanish, little by "
"little, until there was nothing to see but tears."
msgstr ""
"Justo cuando pronunció esas palabras, el cuerpo destrozado de Argan "
"convulsionó de repente, expulsando una mezcla humeante de sangre y un espeso "
"líquido amarillo por la boca y el pecho, salpicando todo a su alrededor. El "
"intenso brillo amarillo que iluminaba constantemente sus ojos hasta "
"instantes antes comenzó a desvanecerse poco a poco, hasta que no quedó nada "
"más que lágrimas."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:191
msgid ""
"... And once Elynia moved closer within his grasp, he violently clenched at "
"her arm. And with hurried breath, he asked:"
msgstr ""
"…Y cuando Elynia se acercó dentro de su alcance, él le agarró el brazo con "
"fuerza. Y con respiración entrecortada, preguntó:"

#. [message]: speaker=Argan
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:196
msgid ""
"Elynia... I beg of you... please forgive me. I allowed this to happen. I "
"allowed her... to become who she is now... and control me... Promise me that "
"you will never... you will never... become..."
msgstr ""
"Elynia… te lo ruego… por favor, perdóname. Yo permití que esto sucediera. "
"Permití que ella… se convirtiera en lo que es ahora… y me controlara… "
"Prométeme que nunca… que tú nunca… te convertirás…"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:205
msgid "Become... become what? Argan?"
msgstr "¿Convertirme… en qué? ¿Argan?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:214
msgid "Argan? What do you mean? What am I supposed to do? Argan?!"
msgstr "¿Argan? ¿Qué quieres decir? ¿Qué se supone que debo hacer? ¡¿Argan?!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:219
msgid ""
"Argan! No, no, this can’t be happening, you can’t be doing this, I am trying "
"to heal you, don’t you see? I..."
msgstr ""
"¡Argan! No, no, esto no puede estar pasando, no puedes estar haciendo esto, "
"estoy intentando sanarte, ¿no lo ves? Yo…"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:230
msgid "Why don’t you say anything? Argan!"
msgstr "¿Por qué no dices nada? ¡Argan!"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:239
msgid "Mal Keshar, don’t you just stand there and watch, help me! Help him!"
msgstr "¡Mal Keshar, no te quedes ahí parado mirando, ayúdame! ¡Ayúdalo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:244
msgid ""
"There is nothing I can do. His spirit left us too quickly, and to pull him "
"back into the physical realm after that... You do remember why that is the "
"greatest taboo of all, right?"
msgstr ""
"No hay nada que pueda hacer. Su espíritu nos abandonó demasiado rápido, y "
"devolverlo al reino físico después de eso… Recuerdas por qué es el mayor "
"tabú de todos, ¿verdad?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:253
msgid "At least he may finally rest now."
msgstr "Al menos ahora podrá descansar al fin."

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:357
msgid ""
"Argan’s journal — it was hidden beneath his robes. Elynia, my lady, if you "
"allow me to speak my opinion: we should keep it, it may contain information "
"that could prove useful later."
msgstr ""
"El diario de Argan… estaba oculto bajo sus ropajes. Elynia, mi señora, si me "
"permite opinar: deberíamos conservarlo, podría contener información que "
"resulte útil más adelante."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:366
msgid "Very well... But..."
msgstr "Muy bien… pero…"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:375
msgid "... I should be the one to carry this with me, no-one else."
msgstr "… Debo ser yo quien lleve esto conmigo, nadie más."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:483
msgid "The stronghold is crumbling down! We must leave immediately!"
msgstr "¡La fortaleza se está derrumbando! ¡Debemos irnos de inmediato!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Bx_Do_Us_Part.cfg:488
msgid "At least the Master of Darkness will have a proper burial."
msgstr "Al menos el Maestro de la Oscuridad tendrá un entierro digno."

#. [scenario]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:4
msgid "Broken Heart"
msgstr "Corazón roto"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:226
msgid ""
"Find an exit from the Heart fortress and move Galas, Elynia, or Mal Keshar "
"to it"
msgstr ""
"Encuentra una salida de la fortaleza del Corazón y mueve a Galas, Elynia o "
"Mal Keshar hacia ella"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:256
msgid "We must not waste any more time, unless we want to be buried alive!"
msgstr ""
"¡No debemos perder más tiempo, a menos que queramos ser enterrados vivos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:266
msgid ""
"Elynia, it’s over now. There is nothing more for us to do here. We must "
"focus on surviving."
msgstr ""
"Elynia, ya terminó. No queda nada más por hacer aquí. Debemos concentrarnos "
"en sobrevivir."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:279
msgid "... I know."
msgstr "... Lo sé."

#. [print]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:313
msgid "Checkpoint cleared"
msgstr "Punto de control superado"

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:500
msgid "Lava! These tunnels are flooding with lava!"
msgstr "¡Lava! ¡Estos túneles se están llenando de lava!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:505
msgid ""
"It’s troubling that I am actually considering the possibility of returning "
"to Inferno to escape this insanity."
msgstr ""
"Es preocupante que realmente esté considerando la posibilidad de regresar al "
"Infierno para escapar de esta locura."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:510
msgid ""
"Nonsense! We just must make haste and get to the surface! There ought to be "
"an exit through the hive itself."
msgstr ""
"¡Tonterías! Solo debemos apresurarnos y salir a la superficie. Debería haber "
"una salida a través de la colmena misma."

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:515
msgid "May I ask if anyone else heard that creature?"
msgstr "¿Puedo preguntar si alguien más escuchó a esa criatura?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:520
msgid "What creature? Where?"
msgstr "¿Qué criatura? ¿Dónde?"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:525
msgid ""
"On the way to this section, in the snow-covered area... It may have been "
"just my imagination, but I believe I heard somebody scream furiously from "
"above."
msgstr ""
"De camino a esta sección, en la zona cubierta de nieve... Puede que haya "
"sido solo mi imaginación, pero creo haber escuchado a alguien gritar "
"furiosamente desde arriba."

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:577
msgid ""
"Ugh... This is no place for an elder like me. I feel ill. Perhaps it would "
"be best for you if—"
msgstr ""
"Ugh... Este no es lugar para un anciano como yo. Me siento mal. Quizás sería "
"mejor para ustedes si—"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:582
msgid ""
"<b>NO!</b> ... I mean... I apologize for that, my lord, but I must beg of "
"you to keep going. I don’t want to lose anyone else after all we have been "
"through."
msgstr ""
"<b>¡NO!</b> ... Quiero decir... Me disculpo por eso, mi señor, pero debo "
"rogarle que siga adelante. No quiero perder a nadie más después de todo lo "
"que hemos pasado."

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:587
msgid "... Fair enough. (<i>coughs</i>)"
msgstr "... Está bien. (<i>tose</i>)"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:601
msgid "Is something the matter, old elf?"
msgstr "¿Sucede algo, viejo elfo?"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:606
msgid ""
"It’s only getting worse... it feels as if something wanted to burst out of "
"my head. I pray to the Lords of Light that I may survive this ordeal..."
msgstr ""
"Solo empeora... siento como si algo quisiera estallar de mi cabeza. Rezo a "
"los Señores de la Luz para que sobreviva a esta prueba..."

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:619
msgid "I can’t... continue... Galas, please go on without me..."
msgstr "No puedo... continuar... Galas, por favor sigue sin mí..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:624
msgid "I refuse, my lord. I—"
msgstr "Me niego, mi señor. Yo—"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:629
msgid "<b>ARGH!</b> Galas, please— I— I remember that voice now—"
msgstr "<b>¡ARGH!</b> Galas, por favor— Yo— Ahora recuerdo esa voz—"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:634
msgid "Her voice... She is—"
msgstr "Su voz... Ella es—"

#. [unit]: type=Shadow Courier, id=Corrupted Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:650
msgid "Lédinor?"
msgstr "¿Lédinor?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:696
msgid "Ehhhhh... yuck. I thought it was only a figure of speech."
msgstr "Ehhhhh... qué asco. Pensé que era solo una expresión."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:701
msgid "What are you?! What did you— What did you do to Lord Léd—"
msgstr "¿Qué eres tú?! ¿Qué— Qué le hiciste al señor Léd—"

#. [message]: speaker=Corrupted Lédinor
#. Corrupted Lédinor is actually Uria remote-possessing his
#. body, so "his" grammatical first person is feminine.
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:709
msgid ""
"female^You may have escaped to Irdya, but I will <b>not</b> allow you to "
"march away without due punishment for murdering my precious, most loyal "
"vassal!"
msgstr ""
"Puede que hayas escapado a Irdya, pero <b>no</b> te permitiré marcharte sin "
"el debido castigo por asesinar a mi precioso y más leal vasallo."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:715
msgid "Your vassal? Are you... No... It can’t be..."
msgstr "¿Tu vasallo? ¿Eres tú... No... No puede ser..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:720
msgid ""
"Galas... I fear that no matter what we try, we may never get Lédinor back. "
"Uria must have infected his body in some way before we found him. This is—"
msgstr ""
"Galas... Temo que no importa lo que intentemos, puede que nunca recuperemos "
"a Lédinor. Uria debió haber infectado su cuerpo de alguna manera antes de "
"que lo encontráramos. Esto es—"

#. [event]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:723
msgid "Captive Steward of Telchior’s Hold"
msgstr "Mayordomo Cautivo de la Fortaleza de Telchior"

#. [message]: speaker=Corrupted Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:739
msgid ""
"This is only the beginning, Lady of Light. The beginning of your downfall. "
"Everything and everyone you hold dear shall perish in time. I—"
msgstr ""
"Esto es solo el comienzo, Dama de la Luz. El comienzo de tu caída. Todo y "
"todos los que amas perecerán con el tiempo. Yo—"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:744
msgid "Take your words to the grave, spawn of Uria!"
msgstr "¡Lleva tus palabras a la tumba, engendro de Uria!"

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:756
msgid "That was terrifying... I fear now to think of who’ll be next..."
msgstr "Eso fue aterrador... Ahora temo pensar quién será el siguiente..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:761
msgid ""
"He said he remembered her, Uria... She must have done this to him. It’s the "
"only explanation... the only logical explanation..."
msgstr ""
"Dijo que la recordaba, Uria... Ella debe haberle hecho esto. Es la única "
"explicación... la única explicación lógica..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:766
msgid ""
"We... really ought to make haste and get out of this dreadful place... lest "
"we find out the exact method Uria uses to possess people like this."
msgstr ""
"Nosotros... realmente debemos apresurarnos y salir de este lugar "
"espantoso... no sea que descubramos el método exacto que Uria usa para "
"poseer a personas como esta."

#. [scenario]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:816
msgid "Your journey has just begun."
msgstr "Tu viaje apenas ha comenzado."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:832
msgid "No! The tunnel is collapsing on us! We weren’t fast enough—"
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡El túnel se está derrumbando sobre nosotros! No fuimos lo "
"suficientemente rápidos—"

#. [unit]: type=Death Knight, id=Lord Azghiel
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:860
msgid "Lord Azghiel"
msgstr "Lord Azghiel"

#. [unit]: type=Death Squire, id=Darius
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:873
msgid "Darius"
msgstr "Darius"

#. [unit]: type=Death Squire, id=Durstrag
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:885
msgid "Durstrag"
msgstr "Durstrag"

#. [message]: speaker=Lord Azghiel
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:912
msgid ""
"There they are, the heathens! The Iron Council wants their heads. Get to it!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ahí están, los paganos! El Consejo de Hierro quiere sus cabezas. ¡Manos a "
"la obra!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:917
msgid "(<i>shakes head</i>) Not again..."
msgstr "(<i>niega con la cabeza</i>) No otra vez..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:922
msgid ""
"Your emperor has fallen and this fortress is crumbling with him. Flee and "
"get out of our way or we will have to destroy you!"
msgstr ""
"Tu emperador ha caído y esta fortaleza se está derrumbando con él. ¡Huyan y "
"quítense de nuestro camino o tendremos que destruirlos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:931
msgid "Keep moving!"
msgstr "¡Sigan avanzando!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:971
msgid "We can’t leave Lord Lédinor behind! We must—"
msgstr "¡No podemos dejar atrás al Lord Lédinor! Debemos—"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:976
msgid "It’s hopeless, Galas... Please, you must understand..."
msgstr "Es inútil, Galas... Por favor, debes entender..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:981
msgid ""
"Come on, boy, you ought to know better than this by now, after seeing what "
"became of the Master of Darkness."
msgstr ""
"Vamos, chico, ya deberías saber más que esto después de ver qué le pasó al "
"Maestro de la Oscuridad."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:990
msgid "I am sorry, my lord. I am so sorry..."
msgstr "Lo siento, mi señor. Lo siento mucho..."

#. [scenario]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23Cx_Finale.cfg:4
msgid "Cutscene"
msgstr "Cinemática"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:120
msgid ""
"I understand that you wish to travel with me, Mal Keshar. But, what about "
"you Galas? What will become of the elves who followed you to the Northlands?"
msgstr ""
"Entiendo que deseas viajar conmigo, Mal Keshar. Pero, ¿y tú, Galas? ¿Qué "
"será de los elfos que te siguieron a las Tierras del Norte?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:125
msgid ""
"I have served my people long enough, I would say. To be honest, once Lord "
"Inodien and Lady Unarye became more involved, my presence in our councils "
"became somewhat redundant. And without Anlindë to guide my decisions "
"anymore... Regardless, I was appointed by Lord Lédinor; now that my own "
"appointed successors lead our people and the Chaos Emperor is no more, I "
"feel I have fulfilled my duty."
msgstr ""
"He servido a mi pueblo lo suficiente, diría yo. Para ser honesto, una vez "
"que el Lord Inodien y la Lady Unarye se involucraron más, mi presencia en "
"nuestros consejos se volvió algo redundante. Y sin Anlindë para guiar mis "
"decisiones ya... De todos modos, fui nombrado por Lord Lédinor; ahora que "
"mis propios sucesores designados lideran a nuestro pueblo y el Emperador del "
"Caos ya no está, siento que he cumplido con mi deber."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:140
msgid "So..."
msgstr "Entonces..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:145
msgid ""
"For the first time in ages, I feel free and able to make my own choices "
"again without the weight of an entire civilization resting on my shoulders. "
"So, I must ask you... Would it be all right if I accompanied you on your "
"next journey, Elynia? Because I suspect you are not planning on sitting here "
"idly."
msgstr ""
"Por primera vez en siglos, me siento libre y capaz de tomar mis propias "
"decisiones otra vez, sin el peso de toda una civilización sobre mis hombros. "
"Así que debo preguntarte... ¿Estaría bien si te acompañara en tu próximo "
"viaje, Elynia? Porque sospecho que no planeas quedarte aquí sin hacer nada."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:150
msgid "... If that is what you want."
msgstr "… Si eso es lo que quieres."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:165
msgid ""
"There is a place I would like to visit... That island Althurin mentioned, "
"Zocthanol."
msgstr ""
"Hay un lugar que me gustaría visitar... Esa isla que mencionó Althurin, "
"Zocthanol."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:170
msgid ""
"I fear that the collapse of the Heart fortress may have erased much "
"information about the origins of Uria and Yechnagoth that could have helped "
"us otherwise. However, the Quenoth elves did establish their new home on "
"that island after destroying Yechnagoth; it is possible that they may have "
"found out more about the nature of our enemies since then. I want to meet "
"Quetor’el’s lore-keepers and see what else they might know that could help "
"us."
msgstr ""
"Temo que el colapso de la fortaleza del Corazón haya borrado mucha "
"información sobre los orígenes de Uria y Yechnagoth que podría habernos "
"ayudado de otra forma. Sin embargo, los elfos Quenoth establecieron su nuevo "
"hogar en esa isla tras destruir a Yechnagoth; es posible que hayan "
"descubierto más sobre la naturaleza de nuestros enemigos desde entonces. "
"Quiero encontrar a los guardianes del saber de Quetor’el y ver qué más "
"podrían saber que nos ayude."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:175
msgid "That seems fair enough. But, how are we going to get there?"
msgstr "Me parece justo. Pero, ¿cómo vamos a llegar hasta allá?"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:182
msgid ""
"Uh, we’ll sail across the ocean, of course. Surely our northern friends "
"won’t mind if we borrow a ship or two."
msgstr ""
"Eh, cruzaremos el océano en barco, por supuesto. Seguramente a nuestros "
"amigos del norte no les importará si les pedimos prestado uno o dos barcos."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:187
msgid ""
"There is something unsettling about all this, though. Even though we set "
"Argan free from his suffering, and the destruction of his capital severed "
"the connection Irdya had with Inferno, the demons of Uria continue to roam "
"our world in large numbers, just as before. Is she still able to influence "
"our world? Are there other gateways to Inferno still intact elsewhere? And "
"we never really saw the Chaos Warlord again. If she somehow survived—"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, hay algo inquietante en todo esto. Aunque liberamos a Argan de "
"su sufrimiento, y la destrucción de su capital cortó la conexión que tenía "
"Irdya con el Infierno, los demonios de Uria siguen deambulando por nuestro "
"mundo en grandes cantidades, como antes. ¿Todavía puede influenciar nuestro "
"mundo? ¿Habrá otras puertas al Infierno intactas en algún otro lugar? Y "
"nunca volvimos a ver al Señor de la Guerra del Caos. Si de alguna manera "
"sobrevivió—"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:192
msgid "Then we’ll have to deal with her again, eventually. I know..."
msgstr ""
"Entonces tendremos que lidiar con ella otra vez, eventualmente. Lo sé..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:201
msgid ""
"And then there is that Mal Hekuba and the Iron Council. I don’t suspect they "
"will give up easily, and we <i>are</i> still in enemy territory."
msgstr ""
"Y luego está ese Mal Hekuba y el Consejo de Hierro. No creo que se rindan "
"con facilidad, y <i>todavía</i> estamos en territorio enemigo."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:206
msgid ""
"Between the ongoing war and the loss of their capital, my hope is that they "
"will be too preoccupied struggling against the Alliance in the north to hunt "
"us down. (<i>sighs</i>)"
msgstr ""
"Entre la guerra continua y la pérdida de su capital, espero que estén "
"demasiado ocupados luchando contra la Alianza en el norte para perseguirnos. "
"(<i>suspira</i>)"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:217
msgid ""
"I understand your concern, but there is hardly anything we can do with the "
"scarce information we possess regarding Uria and her followers right now."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo tu preocupación, pero casi no hay nada que podamos hacer con la "
"escasa información que poseemos sobre Uria y sus seguidores ahora mismo."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:223
msgid "What about you, Igor? What will you do next?"
msgstr "¿Y tú, Igor? ¿Qué harás ahora?"

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:228
msgid ""
"Well... I actually wonder how I survived all that... I feel like a legend "
"now, heh. But... perhaps it’s time I find a nice place to settle in and live "
"the rest of my days in peace, you know? Obviously not here, not in these "
"lands with those wicked men everywhere. Could I follow you on a journey a "
"last time? If that’s all right with you, that is."
msgstr ""
"Bueno... en realidad me pregunto cómo sobreviví a todo eso... ahora me "
"siento como una leyenda, je. Pero... quizás es hora de encontrar un buen "
"lugar para establecerme y vivir el resto de mis días en paz, ¿sabes? "
"Obviamente no aquí, no en estas tierras con esos hombres malvados por todas "
"partes. ¿Podría acompañarlos en un viaje una última vez? Si te parece bien, "
"claro."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:233
msgid ""
"Oh, of course it is. I would not even think of abandoning you and your "
"trusty steed now that we have been reduced to such a small band of "
"fugitives. (<i>turns menacingly</i>) I do need to raise a new army to "
"protect us, after all."
msgstr ""
"Oh, claro que sí. Ni pensaría en abandonarte a ti y a tu fiel corcel ahora "
"que hemos quedado reducidos a una banda tan pequeña de fugitivos. (<i>se "
"vuelve amenazante</i>) Después de todo, necesito levantar un nuevo ejército "
"para protegernos."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:240
msgid "(<i>glaring</i>) Don’t you dare."
msgstr "(<i>mirando fijamente</i>) Ni se te ocurra."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:245
msgid ""
"You always ruin everything for me. Why do I even tolerate this, I wonder..."
msgstr "Siempre me arruinas todo. Me pregunto por qué siquiera tolero esto..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:250
msgid "It is fine, Igor. We will miss you when we finally part ways."
msgstr "Está bien, Igor. Te extrañaremos cuando finalmente nos separemos."

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:255
msgid "Oh, I’ll miss you too, friends. (<i>sniffles</i>)"
msgstr "Oh, yo también los extrañaré, amigos. (<i>solloza</i>)"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:264
msgid ""
"It’s a shame we lost that fancy ring we found back there. I wonder what "
"became of it?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:277
msgid ""
"I... uh... wellllll... while we were escaping the fortress... I kinda..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:282
msgid "Oh, you little—"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:287
msgid ""
"Listen, everything was shaking! I couldn’t help it! I tripped! I think "
"that’s the last time I saw it, at least"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:292
msgid ""
"I should turn you into a— I mean— PAH! It doesn’t matter anymore. I was "
"curious to find out exactly how it works. Alas!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:299
msgid ""
"I have the ring right here, but somehow it’s completely inert now. I fear "
"that exposing it to the Union may have stripped it of its magic. It might "
"not even work again in a thousand years."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:304
msgid ""
"Figures it would break when exposed to such power. Pah, I was curious to "
"find out exactly how it worked. Alas!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:311
msgid ""
"I fear I must’ve dropped it when we were escaping the crumbling fortress. I "
"don’t know exactly when I lost it, but it was already gone by the time we "
"reached the surface."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:316
msgid ""
"Oh well, who needs a stupid resurrection ring when you have necromancy, "
"anyway... Although, I have to admit I really wanted to find out exactly how "
"it works. Alas!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:325
msgid ""
"Let us return to the Far North, then. I would like to pay a visit to our "
"people as well."
msgstr ""
"Entonces volvamos al Lejano Norte. También me gustaría visitar a nuestra "
"gente."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:330
msgid "Hah! So you do miss being in a position of power after all!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ja! ¡Así que sí extrañas estar en una posición de poder después de todo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/24_Epilogue.cfg:335
msgid ""
"No, no, it’s nothing like that. I just want to speak to my comrades again — "
"it has been far too long since I last saw their faces."
msgstr ""
"No, no, no es nada de eso. Solo quiero hablar con mis camaradas otra vez — "
"ha pasado demasiado tiempo desde la última vez que vi sus rostros."

#. [unit_type]: id=Prong Bug, race=verlissh
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/alien-verlissh/Prong_Bug.cfg:5
msgid "Prong Bug"
msgstr "Insecto vara"

#. [unit_type]: id=Prong Bug, race=verlissh
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/alien-verlissh/Prong_Bug.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Amongst the Verlissh attack forces, some people have spotted strange "
"creatures that resemble beetles, except for being larger than a wolf. "
"Fortunately enough, these creatures’ performance in battle is nothing to "
"fear, and their only apparent purpose seems to be scouting."
msgstr ""
"Entre las fuerzas de ataque Verlissh, algunas personas han visto criaturas "
"extrañas que se parecen a escarabajos, salvo por ser más grandes que un "
"lobo. Afortunadamente, su desempeño en batalla no es motivo de temor, y su "
"único propósito aparente parece ser el reconocimiento."

#. [unit_type]: id=Shadow Courier, race=demon
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/demons/Shadow_Courier.cfg:5
msgid "Shadow Courier"
msgstr "Mensajero sombrío"

#. [unit_type]: id=Shadow Courier, race=demon
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/demons/Shadow_Courier.cfg:23
msgid ""
"A few chosen ones from the ranks of the Chaos Lorekeepers are given "
"knowledge and abilities that are forbidden to the common followers; they are "
"the closest to the Emperor that anyone has ever been, and serve him as his "
"right-hands. Although physically weak and slow after turning into demons, "
"their magic skills more than compensate for such lack, making them opponents "
"that should never be fought directly if possible."
msgstr ""
"A unos pocos elegidos entre las filas de los Guardianes del Conocimiento del "
"Caos se les otorgan conocimientos y habilidades prohibidas a los seguidores "
"comunes; son los más cercanos al Emperador que nadie jamás ha sido, y le "
"sirven como su mano derecha. Aunque físicamente débiles y lentos tras "
"convertirse en demonios, sus habilidades mágicas compensan con creces tales "
"carencias, convirtiéndolos en oponentes que nunca deberían ser enfrentados "
"directamente."

#. [attack]: type=cold
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/demons/Shadow_Courier.cfg:40
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/shaxthal/Boss_Master_of_Darkness.cfg:53
msgid "infernal chill"
msgstr "Frío infernal"

#. [attack]: type=arcane
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/demons/Shadow_Courier.cfg:52
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/shaxthal/Boss_Master_of_Darkness.cfg:65
msgid "noctum"
msgstr "noctum"

#. [unit_type]: id=Dwarvish Flamethrower, race=dwarf
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/dwarves/Flamethrower.cfg:5
msgid "Dwarvish Flamethrower"
msgstr "Lanzallamas enano"

#. [unit_type]: id=Dwarvish Flamethrower, race=dwarf
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/dwarves/Flamethrower.cfg:19
msgid ""
"It is said that the Dwarven Flamethrowers have strange staves of wood and "
"iron, similar to those of the Thunderguards; but instead of making a "
"thunderous noise and shooting a projectile, their weapon generates a "
"continuous tongue of flame."
msgstr ""
"Se dice que los lanzallamas enanos poseen extraños bastones de madera y "
"hierro, similares a los de los Guardias del Trueno; pero en lugar de "
"producir un ruido atronador y disparar un proyectil, su arma genera una "
"lengua continua de fuego."

#. [attack]: type=fire
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/dwarves/Flamethrower.cfg:34
msgid "firestick"
msgstr "lanzallamas"

#. [unit_type]: id=Dwarvish Steamwheel, race=dwarf
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/dwarves/Steamwheel.cfg:5
msgid "Steamwheel"
msgstr "Vapormóvil"

#. [unit_type]: id=Dwarvish Steamwheel, race=dwarf
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/dwarves/Steamwheel.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Some Dwarves use strange vehicles that can move fast without a horse. It is "
"said that these great wheeled vehicles are powered by invisible steam "
"genies, and thus they are called ‘Steamwheels’."
msgstr ""
"Algunos enanos usan extraños vehículos que pueden moverse rápido sin "
"caballos. Se dice que estos grandes vehículos con ruedas están impulsados "
"por genios de vapor invisibles, y por eso se los llama ‘Vapormóviles’."

#. [unit_type]: id=Dwarvish Thunderwheel, race=dwarf
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/dwarves/Thunderwheel.cfg:5
msgid "Thunderwheel"
msgstr "Truenomóvil"

#. [unit_type]: id=Dwarvish Thunderwheel, race=dwarf
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/dwarves/Thunderwheel.cfg:19
msgid ""
"With the help of one more steam genies, these noisy vehicles are able to "
"move faster than horses."
msgstr ""
"Con la ayuda de uno o más genios de vapor, estos ruidosos vehículos pueden "
"moverse más rápido que los caballos."

#. [unit_type]: id=Dwarvish Warwheel, race=dwarf
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/dwarves/Warwheel.cfg:5
msgid "Warwheel"
msgstr "Rueda de guerra"

#. [unit_type]: id=Dwarvish Warwheel, race=dwarf
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/dwarves/Warwheel.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Warwheels are faster and more heavily armored than Steamwheels, and can "
"breach enemy lines with their fearsome charge."
msgstr ""
"Las ruedas de guerra son más rápidas y están más blindadas que las ruedas de "
"vapor, y pueden romper las líneas enemigas con su temible carga."

#. [unit_type]: id=Anlinde Elvish Ascetic, race=elf, gender=female
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/elves-wood/Anlinde_Ascetic.cfg:5
msgid "female^Elvish Ascetic"
msgstr "Asceta Elfa"

#. [unit_type]: id=Anlinde Elvish Ascetic, race=elf, gender=female
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/elves-wood/Anlinde_Ascetic.cfg:22
msgid ""
"Some elves have studied varieties of magic better suited for offensive "
"purposes. Whence their knowledge and mastery of such arts came is not known, "
"and they do not reveal their secrets. All that is known of their training is "
"that they may spend a long time alone in the wilderness, not to appear for "
"years, or in extreme cases, centuries.\n"
"\n"
"For these ascetics, knowledge may be a curse at times, as their people tend "
"to expect from them more that what they can offer without violating their "
"own principles. Nonetheless, they may use their mastery of magic to lend a "
"hand to fate--or to twist it. They possess good knowledge of both offensive "
"and defensive spells. They often also have basic notions of medicine and can "
"cure other creatures from the effects of poison."
msgstr ""
"Algunos elfos han estudiado variedades de magia más adecuadas para fines "
"ofensivos. De dónde viene su conocimiento y maestría de tales artes no se "
"sabe, y no revelan sus secretos. Todo lo que se sabe de su entrenamiento es "
"que pueden pasar mucho tiempo solos en la naturaleza, sin aparecer durante "
"años o, en casos extremos, siglos.\n"
"\n"
"Para estas ascetas, el conocimiento puede ser una maldición a veces, porque "
"su pueblo suele esperar de ellas más de lo que pueden ofrecer sin violar sus "
"propios principios. Aun así, pueden usar su maestría de la magia para echar "
"una mano al destino… o para torcerlo. Poseen buen conocimiento tanto de "
"hechizos ofensivos como defensivos. A menudo también tienen nociones básicas "
"de medicina y pueden curar a otras criaturas de los efectos del veneno."

#. [attack]: type=arcane
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/elves-wood/Anlinde_Ascetic.cfg:53
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/elves-wood/Anlinde_Mystic.cfg:53
msgid "ethereal zephyr"
msgstr "corriente etérea"

#. [unit_type]: id=Anlinde Elvish Avatar, race=elf, gender=female
#. [unit_type]: id=Anlinde Dead, race=elf, gender=female, description=GO AWAY
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/elves-wood/Anlinde_Avatar.cfg:5
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/elves-wood/Dead_Anlinde.cfg:15
msgid "female^Elvish Avatar"
msgstr "Avatar elfa"

#. [unit_type]: id=Anlinde Elvish Avatar, race=elf, gender=female
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/elves-wood/Anlinde_Avatar.cfg:25
msgid ""
"The great power attained by some mystics is often dreaded by the enemies of "
"elvenkind. After a long path of learning — often lasting their entire "
"lifetime — these avatars of wind and storm master the natural elements, and "
"are capable of commanding them at their will.\n"
"\n"
"Needless to say, these skills could be used to destroy the elvish "
"civilization. Avatars are thus highly respected, often feared sages of their "
"people. Power is both a gift and a curse — understanding and bearing this "
"great responsibility is perhaps one of the last challenges that must be "
"mastered by these mystics."
msgstr ""
"El gran poder alcanzado por algunas místicas suele ser temido por los "
"enemigos de los elfos. Tras un largo camino de aprendizaje —a menudo durante "
"toda su vida— estas avatares del viento y la tormenta dominan los elementos "
"naturales y pueden mandarlos a su voluntad.\n"
"\n"
"No hace falta decir que estas habilidades podrían usarse para destruir la "
"civilización élfica. Por eso los avatares son sabios muy respetados y a "
"menudo temidos por su pueblo. El poder es tanto un don como una maldición —"
"comprender y asumir esta gran responsabilidad es quizá uno de los últimos "
"desafíos que deben superar estas místicas."

#. [attack]: type=arcane
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/elves-wood/Anlinde_Avatar.cfg:60
msgid "ethereal storm"
msgstr "tormenta etérea"

#. [unit_type]: id=Anlinde Elvish Mystic, race=elf, gender=female
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/elves-wood/Anlinde_Mystic.cfg:5
msgid "female^Elvish Mystic"
msgstr "Mística elfa"

#. [unit_type]: id=Anlinde Elvish Mystic, race=elf, gender=female
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/elves-wood/Anlinde_Mystic.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Experienced mystics are of great value in the new Elvish society. Their "
"great knowledge of history and magic, tolerance and fair judgement is what "
"is sought for in a leader or advisor. In times of need, they are in charge "
"of assisting their lords with worthy advice or even support on the "
"battlefield. But they have not finished learning yet, and still wander about "
"the world, seeking new questions to answer."
msgstr ""
"Las místicas experimentadas son de gran valor en la nueva sociedad élfica. "
"Su gran conocimiento de la historia y la magia, su tolerancia y justo juicio "
"son cualidades buscadas en un líder o consejera. En tiempos de necesidad, se "
"encargan de asistir a sus señores con consejos valiosos o incluso apoyo en "
"el campo de batalla. Pero aún no han terminado de aprender y siguen vagando "
"por el mundo, buscando nuevas preguntas para responder."

#. [unit_type]: id=Elvish Civilian, race=elf, gender=male,female
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/elves-wood/Civilian.cfg:5
msgid "Elvish Civilian"
msgstr "Civil elfo"

#. [unit_type]: id=Elvish Civilian, race=elf, gender=male,female
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/elves-wood/Civilian.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Despite not being of a particularly warlike nature, most elves are taught at "
"very early age the basics of swordplay and archery. This enables them to "
"defend themselves and form a militia to guard their homes in times of need."
msgstr ""
"Aunque no son especialmente belicosos, a la mayoría de los elfos se les "
"enseña desde muy temprana edad los fundamentos de la esgrima y la arquería. "
"Esto les permite defenderse y formar una milicia para proteger sus hogares "
"en tiempos de necesidad."

#. [female]: gender=female
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/elves-wood/Civilian.cfg:142
msgid "female^Elvish Civilian"
msgstr "Civil elfa"

#. [unit_type]: id=Lady of Light, race=faerie, gender=female
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/faeries/Lady_of_Light.cfg:5
msgid "female^Lady of Light"
msgstr "Dama de la luz"

#. [unit_type]: id=Lady of Light, race=faerie, gender=female
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/faeries/Lady_of_Light.cfg:37
msgid ""
"While it is not exactly rare for elves to attain a faerie-like affinity with "
"nature, none in recorded history can claim to have done so to the same "
"degree as the legendary Lady of Light. Elynia’s divine heritage allows her "
"to channel the power of the Lords of Light and cast a glow in even the "
"darkest depths of Irdya, wielding it against all those who oppose the "
"natural order.\n"
"\n"
"Very little is known of her ultimate power, the Union of Light and Darkness "
"once invoked by her and the Master of Darkness against the powerful Demon "
"Lord Zhangor. And now that the Union has been fractured by a cruel twist of "
"fate, it is doubtful that the mystery will ever be elucidated. Nevertheless, "
"the essence of Light continues to radiate from her very skin and provide her "
"with the strength to assist her people in their hour of need."
msgstr ""
"Aunque no es del todo raro que los elfos alcancen una afinidad feérica con "
"la naturaleza, ninguno en la historia registrada puede afirmar haberlo hecho "
"en el mismo grado que la legendaria Dama de la Luz. La herencia divina de "
"Elynia le permite canalizar el poder de los Señores de la Luz y proyectar un "
"resplandor incluso en las profundidades más oscuras de Irdya, usándolo "
"contra todos aquellos que se opongan al orden natural.\n"
"\n"
"Se sabe muy poco de su poder supremo, la Unión de la Luz y la Oscuridad, "
"invocada una vez por ella y el Maestro de la Oscuridad contra el poderoso "
"Señor Demonio Zhangor. Y ahora que la Unión ha sido fracturada por un cruel "
"giro del destino, es dudoso que el misterio se resuelva alguna vez. No "
"obstante, la esencia de la Luz sigue irradiando desde su propia piel y le "
"proporciona la fuerza para asistir a su pueblo en su hora de necesidad."

#. [unit_type]: id=Sylvan Warden, race=faerie, gender=female
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/faeries/Sylvan_Warden.cfg:5
msgid "female^Sylvan Warden"
msgstr "Guardiana silvana"

#. [unit_type]: id=Sylvan Warden, race=faerie, gender=female
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/faeries/Sylvan_Warden.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Elynia’s mastery of faerie magic remains unrivaled on Irdya, even without "
"the legendary power of the Union of Light and Darkness. Always dutiful as "
"the sworn protector of elvenkind and the forests of Irdya, she will do "
"anything to stop those who may threaten her people or upset the delicate "
"balance of nature."
msgstr ""
"El dominio de Elynia sobre la magia feérica sigue siendo insuperable en "
"Irdya, incluso sin el poder legendario de la Unión de la Luz y la Oscuridad. "
"Siempre leal como protectora jurada de los elfos y los bosques de Irdya, "
"hará todo lo necesario para detener a quienes amenacen a su pueblo o alteren "
"el delicado equilibrio de la naturaleza."

#. [attack]: type=fire
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/faeries/Sylvan_Warden.cfg:63
msgid "mystic fire"
msgstr "fuego místico"

#. [unit_type]: id=Sentry Tower, race=mechanical
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/mechanical/Sentry_Tower.cfg:5
msgid "Sentry Tower"
msgstr "Torre de vigilancia"

#. [unit_type]: id=Sentry Tower, race=mechanical
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/mechanical/Sentry_Tower.cfg:26
msgid ""
"These immovable defensive structures stand tall and fast against any foes "
"foolish enough to attempt to strike them down."
msgstr ""
"Estas estructuras defensivas inmóviles se alzan altas y firmes contra "
"cualquier enemigo lo suficientemente necio como para intentar derribarlas."

#. [unit_type]: id=Chimera, race=monster
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/monsters/Chimera.cfg:5
msgid "Chimera"
msgstr "Quimera"

#. [unit_type]: id=Chimera, race=monster
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/monsters/Chimera.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Only a wicked evil wizard could have taken the characteristics of various "
"monsters and have put them together in a single weapon of their cause. With "
"three tails, a pair of feathery wings, the body of a gigantic bird and the "
"eyes of a fearsome Cockatrice, this Chimera is not a foe to play with. Its "
"ability to turn its opponents to stone is probably the major threat it "
"imposes over its victims. Use extreme caution, and never look directly to "
"its eyes."
msgstr ""
"Solo un malvado y perverso hechicero podría haber tomado las características "
"de varios monstruos y combinarlas en un solo arma para su causa. Con tres "
"colas, un par de alas emplumadas, el cuerpo de un ave gigantesca y los ojos "
"de un temible basilisco, esta Quimera no es un enemigo con el que se pueda "
"jugar. Su habilidad para convertir a sus oponentes en piedra es "
"probablemente la mayor amenaza que impone sobre sus víctimas. Usa extrema "
"precaución y nunca la mires directamente a los ojos."

#. [attack]: type=cold
#. [attack]: type=arcane
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/monsters/Chimera.cfg:46
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/monsters/Cockatrice.cfg:37
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/monsters/Eyestalk.cfg:64
msgid "gaze"
msgstr "mirada"

#. [unit_type]: id=Cockatrice, race=monster
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/monsters/Cockatrice.cfg:5
msgid "Cockatrice"
msgstr "Cocatriz"

#. [unit_type]: id=Cockatrice, race=monster
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/monsters/Cockatrice.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Sometimes known as ‘basilisks’, these mystical creatures are said to be able "
"to turn the living to stone. Needless to say, this makes them extremely "
"dangerous."
msgstr ""
"A veces conocidas como «basiliscos», se dice que estas criaturas místicas "
"pueden convertir a los vivos en piedra. Innecesario es decirlo: esto las "
"hace extremadamente peligrosas."

#. [unit_type]: id=Eyestalk, race=monster
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/monsters/Eyestalk.cfg:6
msgid "Eyestalk"
msgstr "Tallo ocular"

#. [unit_type]: id=Eyestalk, race=monster
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/monsters/Eyestalk.cfg:46
msgid ""
"Named ‘Eyestalks’ for obvious reasons, these plant-like creatures can focus "
"their gaze onto an unsuspecting victim to draw life energy straight out of "
"them to replenish their own. While almost defenseless against melee attacks, "
"its deadly gaze from afar is not to be underestimated."
msgstr ""
"Llamados ‘Tallos oculares’ por razones obvias, estas criaturas con forma de "
"planta pueden enfocar su mirada en una víctima desprevenida para extraerle "
"la energía vital y reponer la suya. Aunque son casi indefensos contra "
"ataques cuerpo a cuerpo, su mirada letal a distancia no debe subestimarse."

#. [attack]: type=impact
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/monsters/Eyestalk.cfg:53
msgid "smash"
msgstr "golpe"

#. [unit_type]: id=Brain Drainer, race=monster
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/monsters/Leech_Brain_Drainer.cfg:5
msgid "Brain Drainer"
msgstr "Drena-cerebros"

#. [unit_type]: id=Brain Drainer, race=monster
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/monsters/Leech_Brain_Drainer.cfg:22
msgid ""
"Any expert can readily tell that ‘giant leech’ is a complete misnomer, as "
"these creatures bear absolutely no relation to real leeches found in water "
"bodies on the surface. Most people who have had close encounters with them "
"have either managed to evade detection and flee, or suffered a swift and "
"grisly demise — because of this, knowledge about their biology and behavior "
"is extremely limited.\n"
"\n"
"With that said, thanks to the involuntary efforts of a number of hapless "
"explorers it is now known that the preferred feeding method of larger "
"individuals of this species involves grabbing prey by the head with their "
"sucker and swiftly grinding it to bits. Owing to this gruesome habit, some "
"have taken to calling them ‘brain drainers’."
msgstr ""
"Cualquier experto puede decir fácilmente que «sanguijuela gigante» es un "
"nombre completamente equivocado, ya que estas criaturas no tienen ninguna "
"relación con las verdaderas sanguijuelas que se encuentran en cuerpos de "
"agua en la superficie. La mayoría de las personas que han tenido encuentros "
"cercanos con ellas o lograron evadir la detección y huir, o sufrieron una "
"muerte rápida y espantosa — por esto, el conocimiento sobre su biología y "
"comportamiento es extremadamente limitado.\n"
"\n"
"Dicho esto, gracias a los esfuerzos involuntarios de varios desafortunados "
"exploradores, ahora se sabe que el método de alimentación preferido de los "
"individuos más grandes de esta especie consiste en agarrar a la presa por la "
"cabeza con su ventosa y triturarla rápidamente en pedazos. Debido a este "
"hábito macabro, algunos han comenzado a llamarlas «drenadores de cerebros»."

#. [attack]: type=pierce
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/monsters/Leech_Brain_Drainer.cfg:34
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/monsters/Leech_Giant.cfg:32
msgid "sucker"
msgstr "ventosa"

#. [unit_type]: id=Giant Leech, race=monster
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/monsters/Leech_Giant.cfg:5
msgid "Giant Leech"
msgstr "Sanguijuela gigante"

#. [unit_type]: id=Giant Leech, race=monster
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/monsters/Leech_Giant.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Down in the deepest reaches of Irdya, it is highly common for cave systems "
"to be shrouded in eternal darkness, except in any sections where they "
"intersect volcanic formations. In such environments, eyesight is not only "
"unnecessary but can even prove to be a hindrance due to the fragile "
"structure of the responsible organs. Thus it comes as no surprise that many "
"creatures have forgone visual interaction with their surroundings and "
"instead rely exclusively on their senses of smell and hearing.\n"
"\n"
"Naturally, for surface dwellers the sole idea of large eyeless creatures "
"roaming in the dark is unnerving in its own right. If one were to add a "
"lamprey-like mouth and a primal thirst for blood, the grim resulting picture "
"would cause many a prospective spelunker to quit on the spot. Fortunately, "
"things like that are only ever described in stories told by old retired "
"dwarvish adventurers at dingy taverns — surely, they are merely fabrications "
"of booze-addled minds looking for attention."
msgstr ""
"En las profundidades más remotas de Irdya, es muy común que los sistemas de "
"cuevas estén envueltos en una oscuridad eterna, excepto en las secciones "
"donde intersectan formaciones volcánicas. En tales entornos, la vista no "
"solo es innecesaria, sino que incluso puede resultar un estorbo debido a la "
"frágil estructura de los órganos responsables. Por eso no sorprende que "
"muchas criaturas hayan renunciado a la interacción visual con su entorno y "
"dependan exclusivamente de sus sentidos del olfato y el oído.\n"
"\n"
"Naturalmente, para los habitantes de la superficie, la sola idea de grandes "
"criaturas sin ojos merodeando en la oscuridad ya es inquietante por sí "
"misma. Si a eso se le suma una boca similar a la de una lamprea y una sed "
"primitiva de sangre, la imagen resultante sería suficiente para hacer que "
"muchos aspirantes a espeleólogos abandonen en el acto. Afortunadamente, "
"cosas como esas solo se describen en historias contadas por viejos "
"aventureros enanos retirados en tabernas lúgubres — seguramente no son más "
"que invenciones de mentes embriagadas buscando atención."

#. [unit_type]: id=Rabbit, race=monster
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/monsters/NPC_Rabbit.cfg:5
msgid "Rabbit"
msgstr "Conejo"

#. [unit_type]: id=Rabbit, race=monster
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/monsters/NPC_Rabbit.cfg:20
msgid ""
"It is easy for people who have never lived in the countryside to "
"underestimate the menace that these small and innocent-looking creatures "
"pose to civilization. Their staggeringly high breeding rate and powerful "
"incisors allow them to make short work of any plantation in a matter of "
"days, depriving hard-working farmers from their only source of income and "
"wreaking havoc on a kingdom’s economy. Luckily for most, the rabbit "
"population is usually kept under control by their many predators, including "
"humans who have realized their culinary applications."
msgstr ""
"Es fácil para quienes nunca han vivido en el campo subestimar la amenaza que "
"estas pequeñas criaturas de apariencia inocente suponen para la "
"civilización. Su asombrosa tasa de reproducción y sus poderosos incisivos "
"les permiten arrasar cualquier plantación en cuestión de días, privando a "
"los agricultores de su única fuente de ingresos y causando estragos en la "
"economía de un reino. Por suerte para la mayoría, la población de conejos "
"suele mantenerse bajo control gracias a sus muchos depredadores, incluidos "
"los humanos que han descubierto sus aplicaciones culinarias."

#. [attack]: type=pierce
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/monsters/NPC_Rabbit.cfg:25
msgid "incisors"
msgstr "incisivos"

#. [unit_type]: id=Master of Darkness, race=shaxthal
#. [unit_type]: id=Dead Shadow Master, race=shaxthal, description=
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/shaxthal/Boss_Master_of_Darkness.cfg:5
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/shaxthal/Dead_Shadow_Master.cfg:5
msgid "Master of Darkness"
msgstr "Amo de la oscuridad"

#. [unit_type]: id=Master of Darkness, race=shaxthal
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/shaxthal/Boss_Master_of_Darkness.cfg:30
msgid ""
"Argan’s unfaltering faith in the Mother of Inferno has turned him into a "
"messianic figure revered by the Chaos Empire’s subjects, an antithesis to "
"the Master of Darkness of old. His grotesque new body is anything but an "
"impediment to his fabled mastery of the essence of Darkness. Feared by "
"allies and foes alike, he rules Uria’s sacred domain on Irdya with an iron "
"fist, and delivers her command directly to the Chaos Warlord and the Iron "
"Triad. And to those foolish few who may disobey his authority, the bleakest "
"of fates awaits — to be stripped of their will and turned into mindless "
"biomechanical creatures bound to serve their master unquestioningly for the "
"rest of their lives.\n"
"\n"
"Needless to say, absolutely no creature born from Irdya has ever confronted "
"this man in battle and survived to tell the tale."
msgstr ""
"La inquebrantable fe de Argan en la Madre del Infierno lo ha convertido en "
"una figura mesiánica reverenciada por los súbditos del Imperio del Caos, una "
"antítesis del Amo de la Oscuridad de antaño. Su grotesco nuevo cuerpo dista "
"mucho de ser un impedimento para su legendaria maestría sobre la esencia de "
"la Oscuridad. Temido tanto por aliados como por enemigos, gobierna el "
"dominio sagrado de Uria en Irdya con mano de hierro y transmite sus órdenes "
"directamente a la Señora de la Guerra del Caos y a la Tríada de Hierro. "
"Aquellos pocos insensatos que se atrevan a desobedecer su autoridad afrontan "
"el más terrible de los destinos: ser despojados de su voluntad y "
"transformados en criaturas biomecánicas sin mente, condenadas a servir a su "
"amo sin cuestionamientos por el resto de sus vidas.\n"
"\n"
"Innecesario es decirlo: absolutamente ninguna criatura nacida en Irdya ha "
"confrontado a este hombre en batalla y sobrevivido para contarlo."

#. [attack]: type=arcane
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/shaxthal/Boss_Master_of_Darkness.cfg:41
msgid "soul ripper"
msgstr "desgarrador de almas"

#. [unit_type]: id=Chaos Warlord, race=shaxthal, gender=female
#. Keep the unit type name gender ambiguous if your language allows it.
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/shaxthal/Boss_Warlord.cfg:6
msgid "female^Chaos Warlord"
msgstr "Señora de la Guerra del Caos"

#. [unit_type]: id=Chaos Warlord, race=shaxthal, gender=female
#. Keep gender ambiguous if your language allows, since this text is
#. available before the Warlord’s gender is formally revealed.
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/shaxthal/Boss_Warlord.cfg:36
msgid ""
"Not since the fall of Mal-Ravanal had Irdya seen an entity able to seize the "
"entirety of the Great Continent by force — until, that is, the rise of the "
"Chaos Empire. It is said the humble man who founded it would not have "
"compared to the legendary lich in power or stature, but the Mother of "
"Inferno herself lent him her guidance and blessing. In time, the Empire’s "
"reach would extend far beyond even Ravanal’s petty conquest, its leaders far "
"more powerful than the Founder could ever have hoped to be.\n"
"\n"
"Today the Chaos Lorekeepers function at the behest of the Empire’s main "
"governing body, the Iron Council. In turn, the Council answers to the Chaos "
"Emperor, though for the most part it is his second, the Chaos Warlord, who "
"figures prominently in the Empire’s politics and decision-making.\n"
"\n"
"Beyond being a key figure of authority, the Chaos Warlord occasionally takes "
"active part in the Empire’s military campaigns, commanding its forces "
"wherever Uria’s plans require surgical precision and absolute efficacy. It "
"is rumored that, despite centuries of continual assaults, the Warlord has to "
"yet fall short of an objective. If so, this creature is personally "
"responsible for the deaths of countless millions over the years. That even "
"the most hardened of demon warriors quake with fear at the prospect of "
"attracting the Warlord’s attentions should be cautionary hint enough for "
"anyone foolish enough to ponder blocking the Warlord’s way."
msgstr ""
"No desde la caída de Mal-Ravanal había visto Irdya una entidad capaz de "
"apoderarse por la fuerza de todo el Gran Continente… hasta el ascenso del "
"Imperio del Caos. Se dice que el humilde hombre que lo fundó no habría "
"podido compararse con el legendario liche en poder o estatura, pero la Madre "
"del Infierno en persona le otorgó su guía y bendición. Con el tiempo, el "
"alcance del Imperio se extendería mucho más allá de la mezquina conquista de "
"Ravanal, y sus líderes serían mucho más poderosos de lo que el Fundador "
"jamás habría podido soñar.\n"
"\n"
"Hoy, los Guardianes del Conocimiento del Caos funcionan por orden del "
"principal órgano gubernamental del Imperio, el Consejo de Hierro. A su vez, "
"el Consejo responde al Emperador del Caos, aunque en su mayor parte es su "
"segundo al mando, la Señora de la Guerra del Caos, quien figura de manera "
"destacada en la política y la toma de decisiones del Imperio.\n"
"\n"
"Más allá de ser una figura clave de autoridad, la Señora de la Guerra del "
"Caos participa ocasionalmente en las campañas militares del Imperio, "
"dirigiendo sus fuerzas allí donde los planes de Uria exigen precisión "
"quirúrgica y eficacia absoluta. Se rumorea que, a pesar de siglos de asaltos "
"continuos, la Señora de la Guerra aún no ha fallado en ninguno de sus "
"objetivos. Si esto es cierto, esta criatura es personalmente responsable de "
"la muerte de incontables millones a lo largo de los años. Que incluso los "
"más curtidos guerreros demoníacos tiemblen de miedo ante la mera posibilidad "
"de llamar su atención debería ser advertencia suficiente para cualquiera lo "
"bastante insensato como para pensar en interponerse en su camino."

#. [attack]: type=arcane
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/shaxthal/Boss_Warlord.cfg:57
msgid "ethereal blast"
msgstr "corriente etérea"

#. [attack]: type=fire
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/shaxthal/Boss_Warlord.cfg:69
msgid "burning inferno"
msgstr "infierno ardiente"

#. [variation]
#. You can use her correct gender for this version of her description.
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/shaxthal/Boss_Warlord.cfg:274
msgid ""
"Nobody knows for sure what path led her to become what she is now: a "
"creature neither human nor machine. The Chaos Warlord’s human visage and "
"emaciated body belie the fearsome strength and sharpness of mind she has "
"displayed in battle over the centuries. To Uria’s servants — humans or "
"otherwise — her unnatural abilities and great power have earned her a "
"reputation as a demoness, along with the fear and respect normally reserved "
"for a demon lord.\n"
"\n"
"The fate of anyone facing her in combat is already set, and the most they "
"can hope for is a swift and painless death."
msgstr ""
"Nadie sabe con certeza qué camino la llevó a convertirse en lo que es ahora: "
"una criatura que no es ni humana ni máquina. El rostro humano y el cuerpo "
"demacrado de la Señora de la Guerra del Caos ocultan la temible fuerza y la "
"agudeza mental que ha demostrado en combate durante siglos. Para los siervos "
"de Uria —humanos o no— sus habilidades antinaturales y su gran poder le han "
"ganado la reputación de ser una demonio, junto con el miedo y respeto que "
"normalmente se reserva a un señor demoníaco.\n"
"\n"
"El destino de cualquiera que se enfrente a ella en combate ya está sellado, "
"y lo mejor que puede esperar es una muerte rápida e indolora."

#. [race]: id=elvish_spirits
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/undead.cfg:5
msgid "race^Elvish Spirit"
msgstr "Espíritu élfico"

#. [race]: id=elvish_spirits
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/undead.cfg:6
msgid "race+female^Elvish Spirit"
msgstr "Espíritu élfica"

#. [race]: id=elvish_spirits
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/undead.cfg:7
msgid "race^Elvish Spirits"
msgstr "Espíritus élficos"

#. [race]: id=elvish_spirits
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/undead.cfg:8
msgid ""
"Many mighty elven warriors of ancient have died in such a way that their "
"desire of fighting for a last time is not fulfilled. Thus, their souls "
"cannot rest in peace forever, and seek to return to this world for getting "
"their thirst quenched with a last glorious confrontation.\n"
"\n"
"However, they usually cannot do so without help of necromancy. Since elves "
"have always been opposed to allowing necromancy and their practitioners "
"amongst their people, their ancestors have not had the opportunity to return "
"to assist their kind, till now."
msgstr ""
"Muchos poderosos guerreros élficos de antaño murieron sin haber satisfecho "
"su deseo de luchar una última vez. Por eso sus almas no pueden descansar en "
"paz y buscan regresar a este mundo para saciar su sed con una última "
"confrontación gloriosa.\n"
"\n"
"Sin embargo, no pueden hacerlo sin ayuda de la necromancia. Como los elfos "
"siempre se han opuesto a permitir la necromancia y a sus practicantes entre "
"su pueblo, sus antepasados no habían tenido oportunidad de regresar para "
"ayudar a los suyos… hasta ahora."

#. [unit_type]: id=Elvish Ancestor, race=elvish_spirits
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/undead/Elvish_Spirit_Ancestor.cfg:5
msgid "Ancestor"
msgstr "Ancestro"

#. [unit_type]: id=Elvish Ancestor, race=elvish_spirits
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/undead/Elvish_Spirit_Ancestor.cfg:28
msgid ""
"Revered warriors of old roam through the elven forests, visible only by the "
"light of their shining silver blades, their wounds having closed as if they "
"had never existed. Though they are only partially present in the mortal "
"realm, their voices can whisper words in the wind that chill the hearts of "
"their enemies, words that show the true meaning of fear."
msgstr ""
"Reverenciados guerreros de antaño recorren los bosques élficos, visibles "
"solo por la luz de sus brillantes espadas de plata, con sus heridas cerradas "
"como si nunca hubieran existido. Aunque solo están parcialmente presentes en "
"el reino mortal, sus voces pueden susurrar palabras en el viento que hielan "
"los corazones de sus enemigos, palabras que muestran el verdadero "
"significado del miedo."

#. [attack]: type=arcane
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/undead/Elvish_Spirit_Ancestor.cfg:32
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/undead/Elvish_Spirit_Forefather.cfg:33
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/undead/Elvish_Spirit_Warrior.cfg:32
msgid "ancient blade"
msgstr "hoja ancestral"

#. [attack]: type=cold
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/undead/Elvish_Spirit_Ancestor.cfg:44
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/undead/Elvish_Spirit_Forefather.cfg:45
msgid "requiem"
msgstr "réquiem"

#. [unit_type]: id=Elvish Forefather, race=elvish_spirits
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/undead/Elvish_Spirit_Forefather.cfg:5
msgid "Forefather"
msgstr "Antepasado"

#. [unit_type]: id=Elvish Forefather, race=elvish_spirits
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/undead/Elvish_Spirit_Forefather.cfg:29
msgid ""
"The ancient elvish lords may come back to this world in times of great need, "
"to lead their people to glory once again. When attacking, they sing a "
"chilling chant of death, one which can paralyze their opponents with shear "
"fear. This has been known to have changed the course of many a battle in "
"favor of the elven forces, even when defeat was so close at hand."
msgstr ""
"Los antiguos señores élficos pueden volver a este mundo en tiempos de gran "
"necesidad, para guiar a su pueblo hacia la gloria una vez más. Al atacar, "
"entonan un canto de muerte escalofriante, capaz de paralizar a sus oponentes "
"con un miedo puro. Se sabe que esto ha cambiado el curso de muchas batallas "
"a favor de las fuerzas élficas, incluso cuando la derrota estaba tan cerca."

#. [unit_type]: id=Elvish Warrior Spirit, race=elvish_spirits
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/undead/Elvish_Spirit_Warrior.cfg:5
msgid "Warrior Spirit"
msgstr "Espíritu guerrero"

#. [unit_type]: id=Elvish Warrior Spirit, race=elvish_spirits
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/undead/Elvish_Spirit_Warrior.cfg:28
msgid ""
"The greatest elvish warriors of times past are not completely gone, for they "
"consider even death no obstacle to them. They will roam the forests which "
"formerly served as their homes, wandering through both their memories and "
"the mortal plane of which they inhabit. Their recollections of glorious "
"battles and wars, conquests and defeats, cause them to eternally seek a "
"chance to perform those same feats once again. Indeed, this is not "
"difficult, for they can strike the utmost terror into their foes, sometimes "
"even causing death."
msgstr ""
"Los mayores guerreros élficos de tiempos pasados no se han ido del todo, "
"pues consideran que ni siquiera la muerte es un obstáculo para ellos. "
"Vagando por los bosques que antes sirvieron como sus hogares, deambulan "
"entre sus recuerdos y el plano mortal en el que aún habitan. Sus "
"remembranzas de gloriosas batallas y guerras, conquistas y derrotas, los "
"llevan a buscar eternamente la oportunidad de realizar esas mismas hazañas "
"una vez más. De hecho, esto no les resulta difícil, pues pueden infundir un "
"terror absoluto en sus enemigos, a veces incluso causando la muerte."

#. [unit_type]: id=Shadow Minion, race=undead
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/undead/Shadow_Minion.cfg:5
msgid "Shadow Minion"
msgstr "Esbirro sombrío"

#. [unit_type]: id=Shadow Minion, race=undead
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/undead/Shadow_Minion.cfg:30
msgid ""
"These spawns of the night are not to be taken lightly. Although weak beneath "
"the suns’ light, they prove remarkably dangerous under the protection of the "
"darkness, being able to move unseen and strike when least extected."
msgstr ""
"Estas criaturas nacidas de la noche no deben tomarse a la ligera. Aunque son "
"débiles bajo la luz del sol, resultan extremadamente peligrosas bajo la "
"protección de la oscuridad, siendo capaces de moverse sin ser vistas y "
"atacar cuando menos se lo espera."

#. [unit_type]: id=Shadow Spawn, race=undead
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/undead/Shadow_Spawn.cfg:5
msgid "Shadow Spawn"
msgstr "Engendro sombrío"

#. [unit_type]: id=Shadow Spawn, race=undead
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/units/undead/Shadow_Spawn.cfg:19
msgid ""
"These creatures, known to those who encounter them as Shadow Spawns, are an "
"embodiment of the darkest magical arts, and as such, only those highly adept "
"in the arts of necromancy can create them. Like some undead, they possess "
"the necromantic ability to raise the corpses of those they kill to the cruel "
"world of unlife, and are willing to use this to full advantage."
msgstr ""
"Estas criaturas, conocidas por quienes se topan con ellas como Engendros "
"sombríos, son la encarnación de las artes mágicas más oscuras, y como tales, "
"solo aquellos altamente versados en la nigromancia pueden crearlas. Al igual "
"que otros no-muertos, poseen la habilidad nigromántica de alzar los "
"cadáveres de quienes matan hacia el cruel mundo de la no-vida, y están "
"dispuestas a usar esta facultad al máximo."

